title: Sony Xperia M4 Aqua Dual
description: Get more with two powerful cameras, waterproofing and a 2-day battery.This waterproof* camera phone is packed with the best in Sony camera technology. Like Superior Auto, which recognises 52 different scenarios and then configures the optimum settings so you don‰Ûªt have to. The result? Perfect shots every time, even in lowlight.The Xperia M4 Aqua phone features a 5-megapixel, super wide-angle front camera so you can fit even more in the shot ‰ÛÒ you, your companions, and the impressive view.For days that are jam-packed with work or play, you need a smartphone that keeps on going. And going. The Xperia M4 Aqua has a battery that lasts up to 2 days** so you‰Ûªll never have to worry about staying out and about.The Xperia M4 Aqua is as durable as it is beautiful. Its innovative design protects it against water as well as fine dust particles so you‰Ûªll never have to put it away ‰Û÷just in case‰Ûª.*The Xperia M4 Aqua is waterproof and protected against dust as long as you follow a few simple instructions: all attached covers are firmly closed; you can‰Ûªt take the phone deeper than 1.5 m of water and for longer than 30 minutes; and the water should be fresh water. Casual use in chlorinated pools is permitted provided the phone is rinsed in fresh water afterwards. No seawater and no salt water pools. Abuse and improper use of device will invalidate warranty. The phone has an Ingress Protection rating of IP65 and IP68. To see what this means and for more information see www.sonymobile.com/durability. Do note that the Xperia M4 Aqua has a capless USB port to connect and charge your smartphone. The USB port needs to be fully dried up before charging if the phone has been exposed to water.**Battery life has been measured against Sony Mobile Communications AB‰Ûªs smartphone usage profile, defined in September 2014 to represent the typical smartphone user‰Ûªs active condition, including but not limited to a range of usage scenarios (calling, texting, web browsing, social networking, game playing, music listening, picture taking, picture browsing, online video watching, video recording and playback).

title: XOLO X900
description: Intel has stepped into the smartphone market and tied up with Lava mobiles to bring out the Xolo X900 as its initial offering. The device comes in a sleek frame and has a candy bar form. This mid-range smartphone is run on the Android v2.3 (Gingerbread) OS and can be upgraded to the superior v4.0 (Ice Cream Sandwich) OS. The processor on the device is the Intel Atom which churns out an impressive 1.6 GHz of processor speed and is backed up by a substantial 1 GB of RAM which ensures that the apps on the phone are run in a smooth manner. Hyper-Threading Technology on the processor cleverly uses its ability to load apps in minimal time. The phone also contains a micro SIM card slot. The display on the device is an enlarged 4.03-inch TFT LCD Capacitive touchscreen which gives an effective resolution of 1024 x 600 pixels. The high-end features of this device make interaction with the screen a very satisfying experience. The phone also contains a 400 MHz Graphics Engine which enhances the gaming experience of the user. The Xolo X900 comes with an impressive 8 megapixel primary camera which is capable of high quality 1080 x 1920 pixel video recording and is backed up by a single LED flash. The secondary 1.3 megapixel camera allows the user to transmit better video quality when taking a video call. The camera possesses an 8x digital zoom and comes packed with features such as Autofocus, Touch focus, Burst mode and multi-mode. The Burst mode function allows the user to click multiple pictures in a short span of time for objects that are being shot in continuous motion with a single tap of the click button. Additionally, the camera is capable of recording HD or Full HD video. Design The Xolo X900 is a sleek looking rectangular device with slightly curved edges. The phone has a minimal thickness of 10.99 mm and weighs in at a slight 127 g which makes it easy to hold in the palm of the hand. The considerable screen of this device is protected by the almost impenetrable Corning Gorilla Glass. The device comes packed with an Accelerometer which adjusts screen orientation depending on the direction in which it is held. Additionally, the Proximity sensor switches off the display when held close to the ear and the Ambient Light sensor adjusts screen brightness depending on the environment. Storage and Battery The phone comes with an internal memory of 16 GB and its heavy features are powered by a 1460 mAh battery. The battery promises to provide the user with a lengthy 14 hours of talktime on the 2G network and 8 hours of talktime on the 3G network. Connectivity and Features The Xolo X900 is capable of keeping the user connected to the internet at home, work as well as on the move. It features GPRS and EDGE technology to connect to the internet via the 2G network. For a faster browsing experience the device comes loaded with HSDPA and HSUPA technology which allow the phone to transfer data over the 3G network at a faster rate compared to other devices without this feature. The phone comes with WiFi capability to connect to a wireless network and can also be tethered to another device through the USB or WiFi hotspot function. The phone can also act as a navigation aid in the form of Google Maps which uses the device‰Ûªs GPS support. This phone is also capable of exchanging data through the micro USB port or the Bluetooth function. The Xolo X900 will keep the user entertained through the inbuilt music player or the video player on the device. Additionally, the phone comes with features like Dual Speaker, Ambient Noise Cancellation, a micro HDMI port and a Gmail app which combined with the other features, make this phone a worthy buy.

title: LG Optimus GT540
description: The LG GT540 Optimus is the second Android phone from the Korean manufacturer. It is an entry-level touchscreen handset sporting a faux aluminum brushed chassis with metallic trims around the corners. The 3 inch resistive touchscreen supports 320 x 480 pixels and offers dual homescreen, LG's proprietary one and the vanilla themed Android version. The GT540 runs on the Android 1.6 Donut OS, which gives you access to around 30,000 apps from the Android Market. The phone automatically integrates with an array of Google products, including YouTube, Gtalk, Google Maps and Gmail. The handset is preloaded with an Social Networking Client that supports a range of SNS including Facebook, Twitter and Bebo. It comes with a 3.5 mm audio jack, so you can connect it to any standard headphones or car stereo kit. The GT540 recognises popular media formats including MP3, WAV, WMA, eAAC+, MP4, DivX, Xvid, H.264, H.263 & WMV. The device supports automatic account synchronization with all Google mobile services and offers enhanced social networking functions in an enhanced multimedia environment. The Optimus offers impressive imaging capabilities and comes embedded with a 3 megapixel camera with face detection it can also record VGA resolution videos at 17fps. The phone features a highly receptive accelerometer which supports smooth transitions between portrait and landscape modes. As with all Android phones, the Optimus comes pre-installed with a range of Google applications, including Facebook, YouTube and Gmail. Plus there are thousands more free and paid apps available to download from the Android Market store. Other features in the handset include expandable memory of up to 32GB via microSD card and a host of communication options, including SMS, MMS, email, instant messaging and a handy document viewer. The Optimus GT540 supports automatic account synchronization with all Google mobile services and gives one touch access to the Android Market. The phone is powered by a 1500mAh battery and gives up to 5 h 30 min (3G) / up to 7 h 20 min (2G) talktime. It supports GPRS, EDGE, Bluetooth v2.1 with A2DP, Wi-Fi and micro USB connectivity.

title: Moto X (2nd Generation)
description: Pure Style. Pure Performance. Pure Voice. Pure Simplicity. The all-new Moto X is here to captivate you with its aesthetically pleasing design and high-end technical features. Pure Style The all-new Moto X showcases a curved metal frame design that fits easily and comfortably in your hands. The Moto X also comes with a water-resistant coating to protect it from accidental splashes. Pure Performance Enjoy seamless multitasking, faster response rates, and reduced battery drain with the 2.5 GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon quad-core processor and 2 GB RAM of the all-new Moto X. The second generation Moto X runs on Android KitKat which further boosts the performance and battery life of the device. The OS is upgradeable to Android 5.0 Lollipop. Stunning HD Display Enjoy crisp and crystal-clear photos and videos in 1080p on the remarkable 13.21 cm (5.2) HD display of the new Moto X. The Corning Gorilla Glass 3 protects the beautiful OLED display from scratches and damages. Also, the Moto X displays notifications and updates without interrupting your activities. Best Voice Experience Control the all-new Moto X with just your voice. You can create your own voice prompt, post your status on Facebook, send a message through WhatsApp, or just ask questions - your Moto X will obey every command without you having to even touch the phone. Moto Assist Truly a smartphone, the all-new Moto X learns your preferences and adapts to your situations accordingly. Depending on whether you are at the office, or driving, or attending a meeting, your Moto X will adapt its behaviour to your situation and give information accordingly. Moto Actions Use simple gestures to respond to your Moto X - just wave your hand over the Moto X to silence calls or just flick your wrist twice to launch the camera. Intuitive Camera Twist your wrist, launch the Moto X's 13 MP primary camera, and click remarkable pictures with the first ever ring-flash that gives more balanced light and fewer shadows. Your Moto X clicks multiple pictures before and after you touch the screen so that you can choose the best from the lot. 4-Mic Technology Bid goodbye to background noise with the Moto X's exclusive 4-mic technology. Not only does this technology eliminate background noise, it also ensures that you are heard clearly whether you are in a crowded market or stuck in traffic. Battery Enjoy all-day battery life with the powerful 2300 m Ah battery of the all-new Moto X. It boasts battery life of up to 24 hours on mixed usage. Storage The Moto X offers 32 GB of internal storage space for all your music, photos, videos, applications and documents. The Moto X does not feature an SD card slot; hence you cannot expand the storage on this device. Connectivity Enjoy endless connectivity with friends and family via 3G or Wi-Fi on the Moto X. The Moto X lets you transfer data easily to other devices via Bluetooth or USB. Sensors The all-new Moto X comes with a gyroscope, an accelerometer, a compass, and a proximity sensor. These sensors help your Moto X connect better with you and the outside world.

description: The Intex Aqua Speed carries a 4.5-inch IPS LCD multi touch display with qHD resolution (540 x 960 pixels) and a pixel density of 245ppi. description: Pure Style. Pure Performance. Pure Voice. Pure Simplicity. The all-new Moto X is here to captivate you with its aesthetically pleasing design and high-end technical features. Pure Style The all-new Moto X showcases a curved metal frame design that fits easily and comfortably in your hands. The Moto X also comes with a water-resistant coating to protect it from accidental splashes. Pure Performance Enjoy seamless multitasking, faster response rates, and reduced battery drain with the 2.5 GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon quad core processor and 2 GB RAM of the all-new Moto X. Best Voice Experience Control the all-new Moto X with just your voice. Moto Assist Truly a smartphone, the all-new Moto X learns your preferences and adapts to your situations accordingly. Depending on whether you are at the office, or driving, or attending a meeting, your Moto X will adapt its behavior to your situation and give information accordingly. Moto Actions Use simple gestures to respond to your Moto X - just wave your hand over the Moto X to silence calls or just flick your wrist twice to launch the camera. Intuitive Camera Twist your wrist, launch the Moto X's 13 MP primary camera, and click remarkable pictures with the first ever ring-flash that gives more balanced light and less shadows. Your Moto X clicks multiple pictures before and after you touch the screen, so that you can choose the best from the lot. 4-Mic Technology Bid goodbye to background noise with the Moto X's exclusive 4-mic technology. These sensors help your Moto X connect better with you and the outside world.

description: Your search for a budget-friendly Android smartphone ends with Intex‰Ûªs Cloud M6. title: Sony Xperia M4 Aqua Dual
description: Get more with two powerful cameras, waterproofing and a 2-day battery.This waterproof* camera phone is packed with the best in Sony camera technology. Like Superior Auto, which recognises 52 different scenarios and then configures the optimum settings so you don‰Ûªt have to. The result? Perfect shots every time, even in lowlight.The Xperia M4 Aqua phone features a 5-megapixel, super wide-angle front camera so you can fit even more in the shot ‰ÛÒ you, your companions, and the impressive view.For days that are jam-packed with work or play, you need a smartphone that keeps on going. And going. The Xperia M4 Aqua has a battery that lasts up to 2 days** so you‰Ûªll never have to worry about staying out and about.The Xperia M4 Aqua is as durable as it is beautiful. Its innovative design protects it against water as well as fine dust particles so you‰Ûªll never have to put it away ‰Û÷just in case‰Ûª.*The Xperia M4 Aqua is waterproof and protected against dust as long as you follow a few simple instructions: all attached covers are firmly closed; you can‰Ûªt take the phone deeper than 1.5 m of water and for longer than 30 minutes; and the water should be fresh water. Casual use in chlorinated pools is permitted provided the phone is rinsed in fresh water afterwards. No seawater and no salt water pools. Abuse and improper use of device will invalidate warranty. The phone has an Ingress Protection rating of IP65 and IP68. To see what this means and for more information see www.sonymobile.com/durability. Do note that the Xperia M4 Aqua has a capless USB port to connect and charge your smartphone. The USB port needs to be fully dried up before charging if the phone has been exposed to water.**Battery life has been measured against Sony Mobile Communications AB‰Ûªs smartphone usage profile, defined in September 2014 to represent the typical smartphone user‰Ûªs active condition, including but not limited to a range of usage scenarios (calling, texting, web browsing, social networking, game playing, music listening, picture taking, picture browsing, online video watching, video recording and playback).

title: Samsung Galaxy J5
description: Whether you want to read e-books or immerse yourself in photos and videos, the Samsung Galaxy J5 with its HD display, fast performance and a superb camera is an ideal choice. Brilliant Display Whether you love watching videos or playing games, the Galaxy J5 offers an immersive visual experience on its 12.7 cm (5) HD Super AMOLED display. Enjoy sharp and detailed pictures in brilliant clarity and lifelike colors on this device. Fast Performance The 64-bit 1.2 GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon Quad-Core processor and 1.5 GB RAM guarantee a lag-free performance. Apps open quickly, multitasking is smooth and games run without glitches. It runs on Android Lollipop and comes with the Adreno 306 GPU. Camera The 13 MP rear camera with F1.9 aperture captures impressive photos and videos even in low light conditions. The 5 MP front camera with selfie flash lets you click beautiful selfies. It also comes with selfie modes such as palm and wide selfie modes. With FHD support, you can enjoy FHD video calling with this device. Connectivity Thanks to 4G LTE support, you can enjoy seamless connectivity and data speeds up to 150 Mbps. You can also use two SIM cards simultaneously on this device. Long Lasting Battery The 2600 mAh battery lets you browse the web, play games and listen to music through the day without worrying about your phone's battery dying. Storage This Samsung smartphone comes with 8 GB of internal storage. You can add an extra 128 GB using a microSD card.

title: Samsung Galaxy J7
description: The perfect amalgamation of rich features brilliantly packed into a slim body, the Samsung Galaxy J7 is ideal for gaming, browsing and watching videos. Brilliant Display View videos and play games in crystal-clear clarity and without missing out any details on the sharp 13.97 cm (5.5) HD Super AMOLED display of the J7. With brilliant contrast and true-to-life colors, this Samsung device provides an immersive viewing experience. Fast Performance Immerse yourself in flawless gaming. Switch between applications in seconds. Accomplish tasks quickly and smoothly. Thanks to the 64-bit 1.5 GHz Exynos 7580 Octa-Core processor and 1.5 GB RAM, this Samsung Galaxy device handles every task you put across with ease. It runs on Android Lollipop and comes with a Mali-T720 MP2 GPU. Camera Click eye-catching outdoor shots and beautiful selfies with the 13 MP rear camera and 5 MP front camera of the J7. Thanks to the F1.9 aperture and the selfie flash, pictures are clear even in low lighting situations. With palm and wide selfie mode, you can get creative with selfies. This device is also capable of FHD video calling. Connectivity Challenge even the mightiest opponents while multi-player gaming, thanks to 4G LTE that ensures a seamless connectivity and provides fast data speeds up to 150 Mbps. Smart Dual SIM lets you use two SIM cards simultaneously in this device. Long Lasting Battery The powerful 3000 m Ah battery lets you surf the web, play games and listen to music without worrying about your battery running out. In addition, Samsung's Ultra Power Saving Mode lets you extend the device's battery life till you find a power outlet. Storage This Samsung device comes with 16 GB of internal storage which can be expanded up to 128 GB using a microSD card.

title: Micromax Q6
description: The Micromax Q6 is a Dual SIM phone with a slide out full QWERTY keyboard. The slider styled mobile has a 2.4-inch screen with TFT display and 320 x 240 pixels resolution. There is also an alphanumeric keypad just below the screen, which along with the QWERTY keypad give you comfort of two keypads in one phone. The Opera Mini browser is preloaded in the mobile phone. The Q6 is integrated with Facebook and Nimbuzz applications. The QWERTY phone has a 2 megapixel camera with video recording capability. The operating frequency of the device is GSM Dual Band (900 and 1800 MHz). Weighing 130 g, this Micromax handset measures 112.5 x 51 x 15.3 mm. Battery and Storage The battery used in the Micromax Q6 is a standard Li-Ion 950 mAh. The battery serves talk time of 7 hours, while the mobile can be in standby mode up to 216 hours after one full charge. The phone memory allows you to store up to 1000 contacts and 1000 SMSes. The memory can be expanded up to 8 GB using a microSD card. Multimedia This Micromax mobile packs in Stereo FM Radio, Music and Video Player. The phone also comes preloaded with Games. The formats supported by the device are MP3, AMR, MIDI and WAV files. The music playback gets enhanced by the presence of a built-in Yamaha audio amplifier. Connectivity and Features Connectivity wise, this device has Bluetooth, USB, 3.5 mm audio jack and charger connector. Internet access on Micromax Q6 is enabled through GPRS and EDGE. A unique feature of the Q6 is that it sports both kinds of keypads, Alphanumeric and QWERTY, which users can use as per their convenience.

title: Lenovo K3 Note
description: If you love watching movies or gaming on your smartphone, this sleek and powerful Lenovo K3 Note features a mesmerizing 13.97 cm Full HD display and is backed by powerful Octa Core performance. Display Enjoy watching videos, viewing high-resolution photos and gaming on the big 13.97 cm (5.5) Full HD IPS display of the K3 Note. With the 1920 x 1080 resolution, visuals come to life on this bright and vivid screen. Performance Thanks to the 64-bit Octa Core processor, you can multitask effortlessly on this device. Apps, games and videos run smoothly and lag-free. This Lenovo device is powered by the faster and smoother Android Lollipop 5.0. Dual SIM Dual Standby Whether you travel abroad often or you want to separate business from pleasure, the Lenovo K3 Note offers you two SIM slots. GSM, WCDMA and LTE SIM cards are compatible with this device. With Dual Standby, both your SIM cards are active and you'll never miss important calls ever again. Battery Run an extra mile before you plug your Lenovo device into the power outlet. The powerful 2900 m Ah battery packs enough punch for you to enjoy non-stop entertainment for longer. Storage With 16 GB internal storage, you can store more of your favorite photos, music and games worry-free in this Lenovo smartphone. Camera The K3 Note packs a 13 MP primary shooter which lets you capture amazing photos and videos. Sensors This Lenovo smartphone features a proximity sensor, gravity sensor, light sensor, anti gyroscope and an electronic compass. The gravity sensor and anti gyroscope let you enjoy flawless motion-based gaming.

title: Samsung Galaxy Fame
description: The Galaxy is soon to be within the reach or anyone who wants it; at least, in the case of the Fame model by Samsung, it can be true. The phone is the latest in the range of devices that have been released by Samsung for this price range. The phone is a robust little device with 3.5 inches of display. The candy bar design of the phone makes it easy for users to hold and operate the phone with ease. The Samsung S6812 - Galaxy Fame is a Dual SIM enabled GSM phone where both the SIMs are in standby mode. This mode is effective in keeping the battery levels at optimum performance parameters at all times. The capacitive touch screen phone is well designed so that it can be operated in one hand efficiently. The phone runs on the Android V4.1 Jelly Bean OS which is one of the latest OS offerings by Google. The 1 GHz processor is highly efficient for multitasking with the 512 MB of RAM that it possesses. The 5 MP camera in the rear is supplemented by the 0.3 MP front facing camera. The device is capable of video recording at 25 fps. The camera is capable of taking high quality photos with its CMOS sensor, Auto Focus, Multi-scene Mode, Metering and multi-shooting mode. It can also be used for image editing. The 3.5 inch HVGA, 320 x 480 p screen is capable of rendering 262 K colors. The battery used in the Samsung S6812 - Galaxy Fame smartphone has a capacity of 1300 mAh which is more than sufficient to keep the phone operational for almost 300 hrs on standby and 6 hours of talktime. The phone comes with an internal memory of 4 GB which can be ramped up to another 32 GB with the help of microSD cards. The phone supports GPRS, EDGE, 3G and WiFi connectivity options along with a USB and Bluetooth connection adapter. The FM radio also supports recording.

title: Samsung Rex 90
description: Feature phones have been around for a long time now and have not, yet, outlived their usefulness in being the preferred choice of those who firmly refuse to give in to the smartness of a phone. Samsung launches its Rex series to cater to this need, the Rex 90 is a dual GSM SIM bar type phone that runs on Java. The Hybrid Dual SIM gives you uninterrupted data services even when you are on call and the phone also allows you to transfer calls to the other SIM while you are on call. The Samsung Rex 90 S5292 sports a 3.5 inch TFT capacitive HVGA screen with a resolution of 320 x 480 pixels and a color depth of 262k colors. Look at any detail with better detailing with the Rex 90‰Ûªs pinch to zoom feature. The phone comes with the TouchWiz user interface that allows you to add and remove screens and customize the dock as well and is designed to add sharpness to your viewing experience.åÊ Never let that funny signboard or the dimpled smile of a friend pass you by without capturing it for posterity. The full touch Rex 90 packs a 3.2 megapixel camera and is capable of capturing video as well. Forgot to load your music? Be entertained by RJs with the inbuilt FM on the phone that supports recording as well. Music always sounds better with the 3D sound on the Samsung Rex. Design Sturdy with a chrome frame, the Samsung Rex 90 has the volume rocker nestled on the left side while the power button fits snugly into the right side. The phone also comes with 3.5 mm audio jack and responsive keys that make it a breeze to operate the phone even when you are on the move. The rounded body is designed to fit snugly in your palm; the Rex sure is an assertive presence without being obtrusively large.åÊåÊ Storage and Battery The Samsung Rex 90 has an expandable memory which can be extended up to 32 GB with a microSD card to store all your media requirements and comes with Hot Swap support as well which allows you to insert or remove the memory card without having to switch off or restart the device. The Rex 90 from Samsung is powered by a 1000 Li-Ion mAh battery that gives you up to fifteen continuous hours of talk time on a 2G network. title: Samsung Galaxy Young
description: Perfect for upgrading from a simple feature phone, Samsung presents the Galaxy Young to give you the full Android experience right within the budget. Packing a 1 Ghz Cortex A5 processor and 512 MB of RAM, multitasking is made easy on the phone as are app launches and processing as well. Browsing through content is also made easier without any hitches or lag. Easy Mode The Galaxy Young has an Easy Mode that you can put the phone on that allows you to access frequently used functions like contacts, apps, dialer and such on the home screen for ease of use. This is especially useful for those who are still getting used to smartphones. Motion UI Specific to Samsung devices, the Young also comes equipped with the Motion UI that makes use of simple actions to perform certain functions ‰ÛÒ shaking will update the contents, turning the phone over will put it in mute and smart alert bundles all the notifications that you have missed to help you prioritize. It also has ChatON which lets you share media, texts and voice messages with friends with just a phone number. Dual SIM With dual SIM card support, the phone allows you to choose the voice, data and text plans that are most conducive to your usage, thereby allowing you to get the best of two different networks and never running out of connectivity either. Switching between SIM cards also does not require rebooting and you are allowed to use data on one SIM while on call on the other.

title: Honor 6
description: Meet the smartly designed Honor 6 from Huawei featuring an octa-core processor, 3 GB RAM, and the latest Android KitKat operating system. Design A prodigy of modern science and technology, the Huawei Honor 6 features a peacock inspired back cover with a 3D optical glare texture and a diamond pattern. The 2.86 mm ultra thin frame and the 75.7% screen to body ratio makes the Huawei Honor 6 a compact smartphone. The rounded corners of the Huawei Honor 6 ensure that the phone fits comfortably in your hands. Display Enjoy vivid pictures and videos on the 12.7 cm (5)åÊJDI in-cell display of the Honor 6 enriched with smart brightness adjustment and color enhancement technology. The super responsive screen of the Honor 6 is protected with Corning Gorilla Glass 3 and a fingerprint resistant coating to ensure less scratches and less fingerprints. Performance The Huawei Honor 6 packs a 1.7 GHz octa-core which delivers an impressive performance while reducing power consumption. Experience smooth and effortless multitasking with the dual channel 3 GB RAM. The improved high-performance GPU makes the Honor 6 compatible with a variety of games and ensures admirable gaming performance. Battery The powerful 3000 mAh battery is enriched with SmartPower 2.0 which saves up to 30% power with its hardware and software power saving technology and 5 power consumption reduction. The ultra-power saving mode allows you to use 10% battery for an additional 24 hours. Camera The Huawei Honor 6 features a 13 MP rear camera and a back-illuminated 5 MP front camera. Click remarkable low light photos with the 13 MP which comes with Sony's fourth generation stacked BSI sensor, hardware-based HDR, and a dual LED flash. Also, the Honor 6 is capable of taking photos instantly in just 0.6 seconds. User Interface The Honor 6 features the all new EMUI 2.3 which comes with 489 improvements as compared to the previous one. The new UI offers up to 1000 additional optimizations, instant calling with the screen off, and a magazine unlock with weekly poster-quality wallpapers for your lock screen. Storage The Huawei Honor 6 offers 16 GB of on-board storage space for all your photos, videos and documents. The storage is expandable up to 64 GB via an external micro SD card. title: Sony Xperia P
description: Sony has rolled out an effective mid-range mobile with the Sony Experia P. The phone is an impressive smartphone from the Sony Experia stables and similar to its predecessors, comes in the form of a bar. The device is run on the well tested Android v2.3 OS, upgradableåÊto v4.1 Jelly Bean, and can also be upgraded to the much vaunted v4.0 (Ice Cream Sandwich) OS. The Sony Xperia P possesses a 1 GHz U8500, Dual Core processor. These specifications are supported by a 1 GB RAM to assure the smooth running of the multiple apps on this device. The rectangular screen of this Sony phone is a 4-inch TFT capacitive display, which gives a resolution of 960 x 540 pixels. The display also comes with WhiteMagic Technology, which is a feature that allows the user to discern what is displayed on the screen even in the afternoon sun and helps to conserve battery at other times. Additionally, the Mobile Bravia Engine aids the display quality to a fair extent. The User Interface used on this device is Android‰Ûªs very own Timescape. The phone possesses a powerful 8 megapixel camera with an 8x digital zoom which will ensure excellent quality pictures. The secondary 0.3 megapixel camera allows the user to carry out video calls. The camera is accompanied with an LED flash. The camera features Face and Smile detection, Touch Focus, Image Stabilization, Red-eye Reduction and many more features that simplify the photography process. The Full HD recording feature on the device is capable of taking high definition 1080 x 1920 pixel video, at 30 fps, making the video shooting experience quite satisfying. The phone comes loaded with a geo-tagging feature that allows a user to obtain local information using the GPS function on the phone. Design The Sony Experia P has a good weight distribution and is easy to hold in the palm of the hand. The edges are sharp and straight in appearance. The phone weighs in at 120 g and is neither too light nor too heavy when held. The screen is scratch resistant and has a shatter proof sheet over the mineral glass. The display comes with an ambient light sensor which is an intelligent sensor that adjusts the display brightness according to the surrounding environment. Storage and Battery The Sony Experia P comes with a sufficient internal memory of 16 GB. The colossal processor requires an equally efficient battery. The device comes packed with a 1305 mAh, Li-Ion battery which takes care of the power requirements of the device. The battery promises to offer 6 hours of talktime when used on the 2G network and offers an equally adequate 5 hours when used on the 3G spectrum. The device offers up to 80 hours of music playback and 4 hours of video playback to keep you entertained when travelling or when you‰Ûªre sitting in an extremely boring meeting. Headphones are advisable for the latter case. Connectivity and Features This Sony Experia will keep you connected in almost all the possible ways. Over the 2G network you can use GPRS and EDGE technology. For an optimized browsing experience the user can also connect to the internet via the 3G network. The device is capable of higher data transfer rates being HSDPA and HSUPA capable. That means the capacity of the phone to transfer data is enhanced compared to other 3G capable phones without this feature. This Sony phone is also WiFi capable when you are in a wireless network. The user can also transfer files and documents through Bluetooth or through the micro USB port. The device is capable of tethering to other mobiles through the USB and WiFi hotspot. Using the HDMI port on the device the user can connect and transfer audio or video data from this phone. This Sony phone caters to the music lover with 3D Surround Sound and xCLOUD technology for an excellent music experience. Living up to being an all-round entertainment phone, the user can indulge in motion games like Asphalt and Tilt 3D or access the FM radio. The device comes with social networking sites like Facebook and Twitter. Other apps such as Youtube, Google Talk with Video Chat, Google Latitude and the Android Market are bundled into this phone. Business features of the phone include Document Viewer, which allows the user to manage and access documents and presentations and Pushmail, which provides access to the user‰Ûªs Email on the move.

title: Moto G (3rd Generation)
description: Advanced IPX7 water resistance, a 13 MP rear camera and a 5 MP front camera, a long-lasting 2470 mAh battery and Android Lollipop. Meet the beautifully crafted Moto G (3rd Gen), the phone that'll always be there for you. Advanced Water Resistance With the IPX7-rating, the Moto G 3rd Gen is water resistant* enough to handle splashes and accidental drops in water. *Designed to withstand immersion in up to 3 feet of fresh water for up to 30 minutes provided the back cover is properly sealed. Not designed to work while submerged underwater. Do not use while swimming, or subject it to pressurized streams of water. Not dustproof. See Motorola.in for details. Camera The Moto G 3rd Gen features a 13 MP rear camera and a 5 MP front camera. With features such as an ultra-fast f2.0 lens, a color-balancing dual LED flash and HDR, you get perfectly exposed and true-to-life images even in low lighting conditions. Long Lasting Battery The Moto G 3rd Gen comes with a long-lasting 2470 mAh battery* which packs enough juice to last an entire day. Play games, browse the web and listen to music all day without worrying about your phone's battery draining out. *All battery life claims are approximate and based on an average user profile that includes both usage and standby. Actual battery performance will vary and depends on signal strength, network configuration, features selected, and voice, data, operating temperature and other application usage patterns. Performance The Moto G (3rd Gen) boasts a 1.4 GHz Quad-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 410 processor, 2 GB RAM and advanced Adreno graphics. Switch between your favourite apps quickly, enjoy flawless gaming and stream HD videos seamlessly on this Moto smartphone. 4G Stream music, browse the web, play online games and watch videos in a flash, thanks to 4G LTE connectivity. Display A 12.7 cm (5) HD display complements the sleek and stylish design of this Moto smartphone. Immerse yourself in vivid colors and sharp details while viewing photos, watching videos and playing games. Corning Gorilla Glass 3 Corning Gorilla Glass 3 spans your Moto G from nearly end-to-end, protecting your phone from scratches and accidental scrapes. Android OS Enjoy a true Android experience on this smartphone. Moto G runs on the fast and user-friendly Android Lollipop v5.1.1. Dual SIM Juggle between your personal and work life easily by taking advantage of the dual SIM feature of this Moto smartphone. Expandable Storage This phone comes with 16 GB internal storage which can be expanded to an additional 32 GB using a microSD card. Moto Display Preview notifications and updates with Moto Display and decide which ones you want to see. You can even play or pause music* without unlocking your phone. You can also check for new updates on your favourite apps by nudging your phone. *Music controls work with music player apps that use standard Android controls, such as Play Music. Moto Assist Moto Assist keeps track of where you are and what you're doing and adapts accordingly. So if you're in a meeting, it puts your phone in silent mode. åÊ

title: Sony Xperia Tipo Dual
description: Sony‰Ûªs flagship Sony Xperia series comes out with its latest offering, the Sony Xperia Tipo Dual. This Sony Xperia mobile comes in a bar form and is powered by an 800 MHz Scorpion processor. The phone is run on the smart and clever Android v4.0 (Ice Cream Sandwich) OS and also contains 512 MB of RAM to ensure the smooth running of multiple applications on the device. The phone features a 3.2-inch TFT Capacitive Touchscreen which provides an HVGA resolution of 320 x 480 pixels. The phone also comes with the Timescape user interface which serves to enhance the usability of the device. The Sony Xperia Tipo Dual has a dual SIM (GSM + GSM) capability for users who require separate SIM cards for different network providers. Additionally, the phone features an Adreno 200 graphics processing unit which serve to enhance the visual experience for the user. The phone features a 3.2 megapixel camera which is capable of recording video at 640 x 480 pixels as well. The camera features a 4x digital zoom in addition to other useful features like Geo-tagging, send to web and Self Timer. Design The Sony Xperia Tipo Dual is a sleek and smart looking device and comes in dimensions of 57 x 103 x 13 mm. The phone weighs in at a lithe 99.4 g and features useful display features like scratch resistance, handwriting recognition, gesture support and multi touch. The phone also contains an accelerometer sensor, proximity sensor and compass to boost the ease of use of the device. Storage and Battery The Sony Xperia Tipo Dual is powered by an adequate 1500 mAh Li-Ion battery which promises the user a talktime of up to 5 hours when used on the 2G network. On the 3G network, the phone gives a talktime of up to 6 hours. This Sony Xperia mobile possesses an internal memory of 2.5 GB and can be expanded by up to 32 GB using micro SD card, thus giving you enough space to store your music and video collection. Connectivity and Features The phone is capable of keeping the user connected to the internet via the multiple features it possesses. The device comes with GPRS and EDGE technology which will keep you connected via the 2G network. The phone also comes with HSDPA and HSUPA technology to keep you connected to the 3G network at a faster browsing speed. Files and documents can be exchanged using the Bluetooth functionality or the micro USB port in the phone. The WiFi capability of the device allows the user to connect to wireless network in the vicinity. The WiFi hotspot and micro USB port allows the user to tether their phone with another device as well. Additionally, this Sony Xperia phone also acts as a navigation aid in the form of Google maps which uses assisted-GPS technology. The phone is capable of keeping you entertained through the multiple features it comes with. The music player, video player and FM radio features can keep you entertained on the move. Sound enhancements in the form of xLOUD Audio Filter technology and TrackID music recognition make the usability of the multimedia functions highly desirable. Additional features on the phone include predictive text input, 3D gaming, Street view and Latitude. Social networking Apps include Facebook, Twitter and Instant Messaging allow the user to stay in touch with friends and family from anywhere.

description: An extension of the Sony Xperia Neo series, the Xperia Neo L is a mid-range smartphone filled with multiple clever features. The relatively high specifications of this device require an equally capable battery. Connectivity and Features The Sony Xperia Neo L is well equipped to keep you connected at home, work or on the move. It comes packed with GPRS and EDGE technology for data transfer over the 2G network. The device also comes with HSDPA and HSUPA technology for optimized data transfer over the 3G network. This Xperia Neo L is WiFi enabled to let you access the internet from a wireless network. The phone can be tethered to another device using the WiFi hotspot or through the micro USB port. Files and documents may also be transferred using the Bluetooth functionality. The phone promises to keep you entertained with the help of the inbuilt music player. The device comes with bluetooth support and a microUSB port lets you transfer data with your computer as well. Get the best of what is out there with the Micromax Canvas 4 A210.

Dual Sim This smartphone comes with two SIM trays, one of which doubles up as a microSD card slot, eliminating the need to carry two separate phones for business and personal contacts. Connectivity This Galaxy A5 supports 3G networks and has Wi-Fi capability so you can browse the Web in a much faster way. Transfer files and data to other compatible devices via Bluetooth. title: Asus Zenfone 4
description: An amalgamation of technology and style, the Asus Zenfone 4 comes with the Asus ZenUI, PixelMaster for images, SonicMaster for sound, and an impressive Intel processor. Timeless Design The Asus Zenfone 4 flaunts a simple, ergonomic and innovative design which is inspired from the classic ZenBook. The design incorporates the iconic concentric circle finish with a unique fine texture which lends the phone a classic look and feel. Incredible Performance Experience Intel's magic with the 1.2 GHz dual core processor which makes the phone totally responsive and efficient. Switch between multiple apps easily, browse through heavy web pages and run games smoothly on the Asus Zenfone 4. Moreover, the phone comes with 1 GB of RAM which adds to the performance efficiency. Display Enjoy your photos and videos on the 4-inch TFT multi-touch capacitive display which exhibits a resolution of 800 x 480 pixels. With Soda Lime Glass, Asus assures tough protection from damages and better durability without compromising on beauty. Superb Photos Click excellent photos with the 5 MP rear camera infused with Asus's unique PixelMaster technology which combines five brightness-enhancing lenses to achieve perfect photos. Also, the phone comes with a 0.3 MP VGA camera. PixelMaster Technology Combining hardware, software and premium optical design, the PixelMaster technology by Asus is integrated into this Zenfone 4 to produce professional quality photos. The technology delivers images with excellent clarity, contrast, and richness. Unparalleled low-light performance The increased low-light performance of this Asus Zenfone allows you to take clear and sharp photos and videos in poorly lit situations. It adjusts the pixel size and image processing algorithms to boost color contrast and reduce noise. Lens Developed with a five element optical formula, the camera provides distortion-free photos with excellent optical performance. The device has a wide f/2.0 aperture that allows capturing of finer details well. Time Rewind With the Time Rewind feature, the camera automatically begins capturing images two seconds before and one second after pressing the shutter button. Asus ZenUI Simple, intuitive, and extremely functional, the ZenUI is exclusively designed to function based on your needs. Features such as What's Next, Do It Later, Omlet Chat, PixelMaster, Zen Link, and Open Cloud provide smart options to prevent complications and ease out your life. Ultimate Sound Experience A combination of high-quality hardware and software, Asus's SonicMaster technology is designed to deliver an exceptional sound experience. This unique audio optimization technology has been developed by the Asus Golden Ear Team. Dual SIM The Asus Zenfone 4 comes with dual SIM standby support allowing you to maintain just one device for your personal as well as work needs. Operating System The Asus Zenfone 4 comes with Android Jelly Bean 4.3 operating system installed in the device. The OS is upgradeable to the latest Android KitKat on this Asus device. Memory This Asus smartphone offers up to 8 GB of internal memory to store all your multimedia files and important documents. The memory of the device is expandable up to 64 GB via a micro SD card. Along with these memory options, Asus provides 5 GB free lifetime Asus web storage. Connectivity Enjoy endless around-the-clock connectivity with friends and family via 3G or Wi-Fi on your Asus Zenfone 4. Furthermore, the phone lets you transfer data to other devices via Bluetooth or USB connect. Battery Life The Asus Zenfone 4 comes with a strong 1600 m Ah lithium battery which offers up to 12 hours of 3G talk time and 295 hours of 3G standby time.

title: Microsoft Lumia
description: The Microsoft Lumia 430 smartphone packs a 4-inch display with 480 by 800 pixels of resolution, a dual-core Snapdragon 200 SoC running at up to 1.2GHz, 1GB of RAM, and 8GB of expandable storage. The main, fixed-focus camera has 2MP of resolution, while the front-facing cam shoots 640 by 480-pixel images. The dual SIM functionality is welcome as it enables one to use two carriers' services on one device. All in all, a modest hardware configuration, but actually decent given the phone's price point. Windows Phone is known for running well even on low-end devices, and the 1GB of RAM should suffice for all the apps available on the Windows Phone Marketplace.Speaking of software, the Microsoft Lumia 430 ships with Windows Phone 8.1 along with the Denim update.

description: With a 13 MP rear camera andåÊ5MP front camera, the Huawei Honor 4X captures candid moments with its 22mm wide angle lens. It also has a fully laminated black waterfall screen for sharper, vivid images at a pixel resolution of 1280x720. 4G Connectivity Connect to 4G networks and enjoy strong and stable signals with a reduced chance of fallback to 3G. Experience 4G connectivity on two networks as the Honor 4X is capable of utilizing two 4G SIMs. Performance The Honor 4X is equipped with a 64-bit QuadCore CPU, an Adreno 306 GPU processor and a Qualcomm MSM 8916 processor which results in quicker responses, faster gameplay and quicker and stable connectivity to 4G networks. Connectivity The Honor 4X connects to wireless internet networks and can be used as a Wi-Fi hotspot on demand. It also supports 3G networks for high-speed connectivity on-the-go and can connect to Bluetooth-enabled devices for peer-to-peer transfer.

title: BlackBerry Torch 9860
description: The BlackBerry Torch 9860 from Research In Motion (RIM) is a touchscreen phone with an opulent design. This smartphone runs on BlackBerry 7 OS and is loaded with a powerful 1.2 GHz processor. This handset also has 768 MB RAM. This phone has a 3.7-inch TFT capacitive touchscreen with a resolution of 480 x 800 pixels. Liquid Graphics enabled on this BlackBerry smartphone brings your pictures, videos, games and applications to life with intricate details. The Torch 9860 from BlackBerry has a 5 megapixel camera with features like continuous auto-focus, image stabilization and face detection that enriches your photography experience. This camera can capture images at a maximum resolution of 2592 „É 1944 pixels. Geo tagging feature is supported on the BlackBerry 9860 smartphone. HD Video recording at 720p is possible on this handset giving you a complete camera and video experience. Design The Torch 9860 from BlackBerry has a sleek and well finished design. The four tactile Send, Menu, Escape and Power function keys are arranged along the screen's lower edge. A highly responsive trackpad between these keys works efficiently and helps you navigate your pages with ease while surfing the Internet. The multi-touch input method feature enabled on the Torch 9860 makes your experience easy and effective. A proximity sensor for auto turn-off and an accelerometer for auto rotate are also loaded on to this smartphone. Storage and Battery A Li-Ion 1230 mAh battery powers this BlackBerry Torch phone. This battery gives you a talk time of 4 hours on 2G and 6 hours on 3G. The phone also gives you a standby time of 333 hours on 2G and 324 hours on 3G. The Torch 9860 from RIM has an internal memory of 4 GB which is expandable up to 32 GB using microSD, microSDHC cards. Connectivity and Features GPRS, EDGE, 3G, and Wi-Fi are platforms through which you can access the Internet on this BlackBerry smartphone. AGPS on your phone will allow you to find any place and guide you to your destinations. Email and Push Email on this phone along with Document viewer (Word, Excel, and PowerPoint) equips you to meet your office needs. Social networking is enabled on this phone. Facebook and Twitter can be accessed and you can share your thoughts with the world. A unique voice-activated universal search feature with speech-to-text translation lets you look for files, email, contacts, music and even search the web without typing on the BlackBerry Torch 9860.

title: BlackBerry Z30
description: Yet another business phone from the house of Blackberry to woo the world into its seamless, classy countenance with solid performance, the Z30 is a smartphone that will makes its presence felt. Screen Smooth and svelte, the Z30 and its 5-inch Super AMOLED touchscreen make sure that you have a scrolling experience that is as smooth as butter. The largest Blackberry touchscreen as yet, the Advanced Display Technology ensures that everything you see on it is crisp, sharp and colourfully, vividly rich. Browsing the web and reading online content also become so much easier on the large screen, especially with the reader mode that removes all kinds of page clutter with just a touch. The keyboard on the touchscreen has also been tweaked to give you an effortless typing experience that is both smooth and easy to work with especially if you text a lot. The keyboard is also intuitive enough to personalize next-word suggestions according to your common usages making things that much simpler. Usability Always be in touch with the office and be on top of all your reports with MS Office compatibility through the Documents To Go apps which comes with InTact technology that ensures that the formatting does not change when the report you send is opened on another kind of device.åÊ Camera An 8 megapixel primary camera that supports full HD recoding ensures that not a moment of life passes you buy, lost to time ‰ÛÒ capture and relive those moments with great clarity. With the secondary camera of 2 megapixels, the phone ensures that the clarity of your video chats is not compromised either.åÊ Blackberry OS Running the Blackberry v10.2 operating system that is super-intuitive, the phone understands the way you use your phone and the Priority Hub collects content in one place allowing you to see all important messages in one place making it so much easier for you to focus on what is truly important. Processor With a 1.7 GHz Qualcomm MSM8960T Pro Dual Core Processor, the Z30 ensures that you flick and swipe your way through your phone with incomparable ease. Power, Storage and Connectivity Ample storage space in the form of capacity that can be extended up to 64 GB along with Wi-Fi support ensures that your Z30 has great connectivity and space enough for all your apps. Also, you can connect the phone with a micro HDMI cable or stream content via Miracast onto a large screen ‰ÛÒ making that career-making presentation in the next board meeting is as easy as a click. Providing an amazing duration of battery life, the Blackberry Z30 will never ever die on you when you really need it. And with the Balance technology, the phone allows you to create more than one profile to keep the different aspects of your life like family and friends separate without any hassles or mess-ups.

title: Lenovo X2-AP
description: The Lenovo Vibe X2 is the benchmark for smartphones in this modern market. With Mediatek 4G LTE True8Core, you can connect to 4G networks for seamless internet browsing. Mediatek 4G LTE Experience 4G speeds with Mediatek's advanced 4G LTE True8Core processor. It not only allows for the industry's fastest internet speeds but it also has power saving features that gives you more hours of usage. Supported by 2GB of RAM, this processor will ensure that you have a smooth and responsive smartphone experience. Brilliant Camera This smartphone boasts an incredible 13 mega pixel primary camera and 5 mega pixel secondary which results in stunning photos and selfies. With an easy-to-use interface and multiple shooting modes at your side, taking pictures on your phone will never be the same again. The phone also comes with voice and gesture control. Long-Lasting Battery The Vibe X2 has a 2300 m Ah Lithium-ion battery which gives you up to 17 and 19 hours of talk time on 2G networks and 3G networks respectively. With Vibe Xtension click on layers, you can fuel your phone for up to 75% more battery life. Dual SIM Connectivity Enjoy the flexibility two phone numbers on one phone. You can now separate your business contacts from your personal contacts wherever you go. This phone is also WiFi enabled, allowing you to connect to wireless internet networks. This phone also has Bluetooth v4.0 for peer-t-peer transfer. Incredible Display The Vibe X2 boasts a large 12.7 cm (5) Full HD IPS display which is protected by Gorilla Glass 3. This results in an incredible pixel resolution of 1920x1080. Operating System This phone comes with the latest Android operating system - KitKat 4.4.2. This unique operating system comes with new features which personalizeåÊyour phone to suit your lifestyle. Sensors The Vibe X2 comes with a number of helpful sensors. This includes an eCompass which helps you find your way using GPS applications such as Google maps, a Proximity Sensor to detect nearby objects and a light sensor to adjust the brightness of your screen to the environment's natural light for optimal viewing. Storage Space This phone has an internal memory of 32GB, allowing you to store more movies, videos and music on to your Vibe X2.

title: BlackBerry Z10
description: A Blackberry that is customized to make work more effective and your social life more happening, the Z10 puts together an easy interface with a good processor and customized apps to give you a comprehensive smartphone experience. Blackberry Flow Seamlessly integrating all the apps with the UI, Blackberry Flow on the Z10 ensures that it remembers your behavior and replicates it on a regular basis to allow for a more intelligent user experience. Blackberry Hub Blackberry Hub brings all the notifications you have in one place which you can switch to from any app that you're on to ensure ease of maintaining multiple tasks at once. Blackberry Keyboard The device comes with a keyboard on the touch screen that identifies your style and suggests words based on that which makes it faster to type on and ensures that you make lesser mistakes. Display The 4.2-inch screen comes with 1280 x 768 pixels and 356 ppi to present visuals which are sharp and clear. Every image is detailed and crisp and the touch screen is highly responsive and has gesture support as well. Camera The phone comes with an 8 MP primary camera and a 2 MP secondary camera for video chats. Capable of full HD recording, the primary sensor has a Time Shift mode that captures frames before and after you photo, allowing you to get the perfect picture. The device also comes with crop, enhance features and filters. BBM Video The device allows you to have face to face conversations and share screens as well, making it easier for you to keep in touch with friends and loved ones from around the world. This is done through the camera's primary and secondary cameras. Blackberry Remember The Z10 allows you to group items together pertaining to a single project like lists, photos, messages and links to allow you to be more organized. The feature is also linked with the calendar and supports spreadsheets, documents and presentations. Blackberry Balance The smartphone can be set such that your work and personal content remain separate from each other and switching between the profiles is easy with a simple gesture. Intelligent Calendar The Calendar app manages your schedules and tasks intelligently, right from suggesting who to invite bases on past events to showing social updates of friends to allow you to keep in touch better. Connectivity The device comes with Blackberry Browser which is an in-built browser, 3G and Wi-fi support, where it is connects to the internet quickly. It also has Bluetooth and USB. You can also connect the phone to the TV via HDMI and watch videos and media on a big screen. The Z10 comes with DLNA support and is 4G ready as well. Content Security With Blackberry Protect, all the data you have on the phone remain private to your eyes and in case the device gets stolen, it is programmed to lock or wipe the data. Voice Control The phone is capable of performing tasking by recognizing your speed patterns - you can dictate a document, compose an email, open an app, update a status and even BBM with voice commands.

title: Lenovo A6000
description: The Lenovo A6000 is a smartphone designed for multimedia and music lovers on a budget. It features a 5" wide-view HD display that offers good resolution. It also has a Snapdragon quad core processor that delivers responsive system performance. 4G LTE Data Speeds This phone allows for fast you to enjoy data transfer speeds for streaming videos and music, or multiplayer gaming. This phone has LTE Cat 4 speeds of up to 150Mbps download and up to 50Mbps upload. Twin Dolby Speakers This Lenovo phone comes with Twin Dolby speakers which offer enhanced volume and crisp sound. Listen to your favorite tracks with clear, rich sound on this smartphone. Snapdragon Processor This smartphone is equipped with Snapdragon 64-bit quad-core processor which gives you a responsive system performance. It is supported with 1 GB of RAM for seamless multitasking capabilities. Design & Display A polycarbonate body makes this phone light and easy to carry, weighing only 128 grams, The phone has a slim, 8.2mm profile. Watch your favorite videos on this phone's 12.7 cm (5) wide-HD display. Camera Take incredible photos on the Lenovo A6000's 8 MP primary camera with flash. It's 2 MP fixed-focus, secondary camera is also great for fun selfies. Operating System This smartphone comes with Android's 4.4 KitKat operating system. This takes the system performance to an all-time high by optimizing memory and improving the touchscreen so that it responds better. Long Battery Life This phone comes with a 2300 mAh lithium-ion battery to give you hours of entertainment and connectivity throughout the day. This battery is replaceable. Connectivity Utilize the connectivity of two SIM cards this phone's Dual SIM feature. This phone is Wi-Fi enabled, allowing you to connect to wireless internet networks. Transfer media files to and from other devices via Bluetooth v4.0. The phone also has FM Radio capabilities to connect to local radio stations. Sensors This phone comes with a proximity sensor which detects nearby objects. It also has a gravitation sensor which controls the phone's orientation and a light sensor which adjusts the display's background to improve user viewability and increase power savings. Storage Store up to 8 GB of data on this phone‰Ûªs internal storage space. You can expand the storage up to 32 GB to store more apps, games and photos.

title: LG Optimus Black P970
description: The LG Optimus Black is a smartphone running Android 2.2 Froyo OS with a WVGA display. The Optimus Black P970 is powered by a 1 GHz Cortex-A8 processor with a PowerVR SGX530 GPU for handling graphic intensive apps. The LG Optimus Black features a Nova IPS Display which LG claims it to be the best ever display they have fitted on a smartphone. The screen packs the same 800 x 480 pixels as that on the LG Optimus 2X, albeit with enhanced brightness, richer contrast ratios and improved sunlight legibility. The 5 megapixel camera on the Optimus P970 is complimented by a LED flash and can record 720p HD video. There is a front facing 2 megapixel camera for video calls. The phone features LG's Optimus 2.0 UI and brings new features like missed calls or new message alerts on your lockscreen. The intelligent lockscreen also takes you to the relevant section as soon as you unlock the screen. Apart from that, the LG Black packs the usual Froyo 2.2 goodies like flash supported browser, Wi-Fi tethering support and wireless control from the notification bar. Design The Optimus Black wears a sleek, minimalistic chassis and conveys a sense of understated sophistication with its continuous lines. Weighing a frugal 109 g and measuring 9.2 mm in thickness, the Optimus Black is one of the slimmest and most portable mid-high end Android phones in the market. The phone comes with a accelerometer for auto UI orientation, a proximity sensor for auto turn-off and a ambient light sensor for auto brightness adjust. LG has introduced a G button in the Optimus Black P970, once pressed, it allows you to control the phone with various preset motion gestures. The button utilizes the handset's accelerometer to understand the gestures and allows various functions like panning around a web page, changing homescreens or accepting calls without unlocking the screen. Battery and Storage LG has slimmed down the 1500 mAh battery to fit it into the thin chassis of the Optimus Black. The Lithium Ion cell gives 16 hrs of talk time and 455 hrs of standby. The P970 comes with 1 GB of internal memory and supports up to 32 GB microSD cards. Connectivity and Features The Optimus Black can connect to the Internet via 3G, Wi-Fi and GPRS networks. The phone is preloaded with Android Webkit browser with pinch-to-zoom and kinetic scrolling support. LG has preloaded the Optimus Black with custom versions of Facebook and Twitter apps, with contact integration and sharing support. The SmartShare app detects songs/videos in your computer and offers to play it on your TV via DLNA connectivity. The media player on the Optimus Black supports Dolby Mobile effect which gives a discernible acoustic improvement when you connect your headphones. The Wi-Fi Direct feature on the LG Optimus Black P970 facilitates quick and easy wireless transfers between compatible devices. The best part about the technology is that it does not require a wireless access point (Router) and works similar to Bluetooth transfers. The Optimus Black features A-GPS connectivity with Digital Compass and syncs with Google Maps. Other features in the P970 include Document Viewer, Push Mail support, Voice commands and Organizer.

title: Sony Xperia C3
description: Never miss out on a selfie moment with the Sony Xperia C3. This smartphone features a 5MP front-facing camera with a super wide-angle lens and soft LED flash that allows you to incredible photos with minimum effort. Camera The Sony Xperia C3 comes with 8 MP rear-facing camera and a powerful 5MP front camera. With a unique soft LED flash, superior auto mode and a 25mm wide-angle view, you can expect nothing less than high definition. The camera also features Sony's Exmor RS technology takes highly detailed shots with low noise - even in low-lit conditions. Camera Apps Make your photos and selfies even more attractive with a number of camera apps that you can download from the phone's online store. These apps allow you to add a number of effects, colors and filters which enhances the photo's overall value. Display The Sony Xperia C3 features a massive 14 cm (5.5), 720p HD Display that boasts Sony's TV technologies. The phone has an IPS feature which gives you perfect viewing from any angle. It also has a pixel resolution of 1280x720. Sleek Design At 7.6 mm, the Sony Experia C3 is a slim, sleek smartphone that can fit almost anywhere. The phone also weighs 150 g, making it easier for you to carry it around. Lightning Performance The Sony Xperia C3 comes with a Qualcomm MSM8926 Quad Core Processor which allows you to run multiple apps simultaneously with ease. This processor has a clock speed of 1.2 GHz to give maximum performance without draining of battery. Long Lasting Battery With Sony's Battery Stamina Mode, you are able to enjoy more hours of fun with your Xperia C3. This mode extends your phone's standby time up to 4 times. The phone will automatically switch off the display, apps and other functions that are idle for a long time. Connectivity The Sony Xperia C3 comes with Near Field Communication which gives you a quick way to wirelessly connect to any nearby electronic devices. You can even connect your phone to a Wi-Fi enabled TV via DLNA or Wi-Fi Miracast. Dual SIM The Sony Xperia C3 comes with a Dual SIM feature that allows you to use up to twoåÊSIM cards at the same time. Separate your work from pleasure, all on one phone.

title: Samsung Galaxy Note 4
description: The Samsung Galaxy Note 4 is a sleek, modern mobile phone that matches the lifestyle of contemporary customers. Think of the Note 4 as a collection of your most precious wisdom and thoughts which can be easily accessed wherever you go. Quad HD Super AMOLED Display The Samsung Galaxy Note 4 boasts an incredible 5.7" Quad HD Super AMOLED Display that can produce vivid colors at an astonishing resolution of 2560x1440 pixels. It has a pixel density of 500 pixels per inch which delivers better clarity. You can even change your lock screen every hour for constant freshness throughout the day. Incredible Photography Whether it's bright or dark, the Note 4's 16 Mega Pixel Smart OIS (Optical Image Stabilization) primary camera will always give you incredible results. Take clear selfies with this phone's powerful secondary 3.7 Mega Pixel camera with a 120 degree wide angle feature that allows you to capture more in your picture. Say, 'Cheese' You can now trigger your secondary camera by placing your finger over the phone's heartbeat sensors and removing it using voice commands such as 'cheese or 'smile'. Smart Select The Note 4 comes with the S Pen which you can use to copy text and images from different apps using 'Smart Select'. It also has an improved touch and feel experience, where the writing speed, pressure and angle of your pen affects the way you write. You can even take a picture and convert it into an editable format. Multitask Quicker The Note 4 has a multi-window feature which allows you to gain flexibility when using multiple applications simultaneously. There are four modes in which you can view your phone - full-view, split-view, pop-up view and mini icon. Stunning Battery This phone has a 3220 mAh fast charging battery with a shortened recharge feature that helps the battery go from 0-50% charge in around 30 minutes. If you need to conserve battery, this phone has an ultra power saving mode that closes unused applications and processes for you to get more battery out of your phone. Performance The Galaxy Note 4 has up to 3GB of RAM, which allows you to handle multiple tasks simultaneously. The phone comes with 32 GB built-in and it can be expanded up to 64GB. Sensors This phone has been designed to house multiple sensors such as Hall Sensor, Geo-magnetic, Proximity Sensor, Accelerometer, RGB Ambient Light Sensor, Gesture Sensor, Gyroscope and Barometer. Connectivity This phone is WiFi enabled, has Bluetooth v4.1 and supports 3G networks.

title: Gionee Elife S5.1
description: Sleek and powerful, the Gionee Elife S5.1 is the perfect combination of aesthetic beauty and performance. Design The sleek Elife S5.1 re-defines the meaning of slim with its 5.1 mm thin profile and 1.8 mm bezel. This Gionee phone boasts a complete metal and glass finish. Display Watching YouTube videos or playing games is a delight on the 12.19 cm (4.8) HD display of this Gionee smartphone. The Corning Gorilla glass protects the display from scratches and accidental scrapes. Performance This sleek and stylish smartphone performs like a charm, thanks to the 1.7 GHz Octa Core processor and 1 GB RAM. Play games lag-free, stream HD videos smoothly and multitask seamlessly on this Gionee device. It runs on Amigo 2.0 OS based on Android KitKat v4.4. Camera Click beautiful photos and selfies with the 8 MP rear camera and the 5 MP front camera. The camera is also equipped with a variety of features such as auto-exposure, auto-focus, charm camera, horizontal panorama, touch focus, gesture shot and smile shot to further enhance your photos. Battery This smartphone is powered by a 2050 mAh Li-Ion battery that boasts a 3G talk time of up to 10 hours and up to five days of standby time. Storage This Gionee device offers up to 16 GB of internal storage space to save your favourite apps, photos and music.

title: Asus Zenfone 2
description: Beautifully crafted, the Asus Zenfone 2 ZE551ML delivers a truly remarkable performance and gets you through the day without fail. This dual SIM smartphone runs on Android Lollipop and offers up to 32 GB internal storage. Beautifully Crafted Indeed a marvel of design and ergonomics, this Asus smartphone is crafted with ultra-thin edges and flaunts the iconic Asus concentric circle design. The 3.9 mm thin edges make it comfortable to hold this device with one hand. Ergonomic Arc Design Besides making it extremely comfortable to hold this device, the ergonomic arc design with the intuitive rear controls make it easy to adjust the volume, snap selfies or retrace your steps. Display Enjoy crystal-clear picture clarity on the razor-sharp 13.97 cm (5.5) IPS display of the Asus Zenfone 2. It comes with a resolution of 1920 x 1080 Full HD and offers 178-degree viewing angles. In addition, Asus TruVivid technology ensures that colors appear natural and lifelike. Performance Apps open quickly, games run smoothly and web browsing is effortless on this Asus phone. Thanks to the 1.8 GHz 64-bit Intel Atom Super Quad-core processor which enhances everyday performance up to three times better and gaming performance up to seven times faster. Graphics Performance Whether you are watching an HD flick or playing Mortal Kombat X, get a smooth and immersive experience with the PowerVR-G6430 GPU built into this Asus handset. 4 GB RAM The Asus Zenfone 2 boasts of being the world's first smartphone with up to 4 GB RAM. This large RAM capacity and the dual channel technology makes your Zenfone multitask seamlessly and gives up to two times data transfer speed as compared to other similar devices. Touch Experience With a quick response time of 60 ms, experience impressive touch responsiveness on this Asus smartphone. A crystal-clear anti-fingerprint coating is applied on the screen to reduce scratches and smudges. Sound Experience Developed by the Asus Golden Ear Team, the SonicMaster technology has been designed to deliver rich and detailed audio whether you are on speakers or headphones. Amazing Camera Click amazing pictures with the 13 MP primary shooter. The 5 MP front camera comes with an 85-degree wide-angle lens that lets you take exceptional selfies or enjoy clear video calls. Super HDR Mode The Super HDR Mode helps to improve the light balance, so that the pictures you click are similar to what your eyes see. Low Light Mode With 4x increased light sensitivity, reduced noise, and 4x enhanced color contrast, the Low Light Mode lets you capture clear and sharp images in low light conditions. Dual-LED Real Tone Flash Ideal for indoor shots, the dual-LED real tone flash creates natural illumination and captures the real tones of subjects in every photo. Zero Shutter Lag Capture moments in real time, even the fast fleeting ones, with the zero shutter lag capability of this Asus PixelMaster camera. Selfie Panorama This amazing Asus phone gives you the ability to take 140-degree panoramic selfies, so you can capture your entire gang of friends and even the background. Zen UI Experience The new interface design delivers a smart and intuitive user experience. Also, the Zen UI lets you customize your Asus phone the way you want. This UI comes with a variety of new features such as ZenMotion, SnapView, Trend Micro Security and ZenUI Instant Updates. Battery For long lasting usage, this Asus device packs a powerful 3000 mAh battery that keeps it alive through the day. In addition, it comes with the Asus BoostMaster Technology which charges the battery at double the normal speed. With 39 minutes of charging, your battery gets fueled up to 60%. Connectivity This Asus device comes with 4G LTE, 3G, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, and NFC.
