Low Light Mode With 4x increased light sensitivity, reduced noise, and 4x enhanced color contrast, the Low Light Mode lets you capture clear and sharp images in low light conditions. Dual-LED Real Tone Flash Ideal for indoor shots, the dual-LED real tone flash creates natural illumination and captures the real tones of subjects in every photo. Zero Shutter Lag Capture moments in real time, even the fast fleeting ones, with the zero shutter lag capability of this Asus PixelMaster camera. Selfie Panorama This amazing Asus phone gives you the ability to take 140-degree panoramic selfies, so you can capture your entire gang of friends and even the background. Zen UI Experience The new interface design delivers a smart and intuitive user experience. Also, the Zen UI lets you customize your Asus phone the way you want. This UI comes with a variety of new features such as ZenMotion, SnapView, Trend Micro Security and ZenUI Instant Updates. Battery For long lasting usage, this Asus device packs a powerful 3000 mAh battery that keeps it alive through the day. In addition, it comes with the Asus BoostMaster Technology which charges the battery at double the normal speed. With 39 minutes of charging, your battery gets fueled up to 60%. Connectivity This Asus device comes with 4G LTE, 3G, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth and NFC.

title: Gionee Elife E3
description: Turn your smartphone into a super-phone with our choicest array of mobile accessories. These accessories are specially designed to boost the performance of your phone, along with giving you the option of customizing it to your own liking.

title: Sony Xperia C4 Dual
description: Are you a selfie fan? If yes, then grab this exceptional Sony Xperia C4 Dual smartphone which has been designed to click the best PROselfies. Apart from an amazing front and rear camera, this Full HD smartphone offers maximum performance and speed. Front CameraåÊ- For PROselfies For all selfie lovers, the 5 MP front camera of this Sony device is equipped with a soft LED flash, 25 mm wide-angle lens and other features to click the best PROselfies. Exmor R sensor ensures sharp pictures with low noise. HDR balances bright background lights for clearer results. SteadyShot lets you shoot amazing selfie videos. Unique Soft LED Flash The unique soft LED flash automatically adjusts according to the lighting conditions, illuminates the scene and gives you the perfect shot. Whether there is a bright backlight or you are taking photos at night, the Superior Auto feature ensures that your selfies and group selfies are of professional quality. 25 mm Wide View Thanks to the 25 mm wide-angle lens with an 80-degree field of view, you can fit in more of your friends or more of the view in a single shot. Main Camera This Sony Xperia smartphone is equipped with a 13 MP primary shooter. Exmor RS For Mobile This image sensor technology assures sharp photos and videos with fine detailing, amazing picture clarity and rich colors, even while shooting in challenging light conditions. Superior Auto The Superior Auto feature recognises up to 52 different scenarios such as illuminated night shots and close-up macros. This intelligent feature adjusts the settings according to the scene, so you get noteworthy photos always. HDR For Photo & Video HDR mode shoots the same image multiple times under different exposures and layers them, so that you get clear and bright photos and videos. This feature is extremely useful while capturing photos or videos in strong backlight or high-contrast situations. SteadyShot Thanks to SteadyShot, every video you shoot with this Xperia smartphone is smooth, steady and perfect. Sound Photo Relive you favourite moments with sound and visuals. Capture up to 10 seconds of audio with your photos using Sound Photo app and share it via PlayMemories Online. AR Mask Replace your own face or other people's faces with a different face using the AR Mask app. You can choose from the pre-loaded faces or create your own collection. Style Portrait This app lets you select from different styles to enhance your photos or add fun effects to them. These effects can be applied in real-time or after taking the photo or video. Download More Apps Apart from the pre-installed apps, you can download more camera apps directly from the camera interface of this Xperia smartphone. Display The large 13.97 cm (5.5) Full HD display and Mobile Bravia Engine 2 make the Xperia C4 an ideal device for watching movies and playing games. The IPS technology allows excellent viewing from all angles, so you and your friends can enjoy a movie on this device while chilling out in the college cafeteria. åÊ Sound Equipped with a speaker capable of up to 97 decibels and ClearAudio+ technologies for crystal clear audio, you can pump up your home get-togethers with loud music. This Xperia device delivers rich bass, thanks to the xLoud loudness enhancement engine. Design Despite the large screen size, the Xperia C4 is sleek, lightweight and easily slides into your jeans pocket or wallet. The device is 7.9 mm thin and weighs just 147 grams. Processor Play games lag-free, run multiple apps simultaneously, surf the web seamlessly and stream HD videos without glitches. The competent 1.7 GHz Octa Core processor and 2 GB RAM offers maximum performance in everything you do on your Xperia smartphone. The phone also comes with a built-in LTE/4G modem for extremely fast internet connectivity. Battery An incredibly powerful yet efficient 2600 mAh battery powers this Xperia phone. To further extend the already long battery life, this device offers four power management modes - Battery STAMINA mode, Extended standby mode, Extended usage mode and Ultra STAMINA mode.

title: Intex Aqua Dream
description: Intex Aqua Dream Smartphone is Powered By Android v4.4 (Kitkat) Operating System.These Smartphone is Gives Better Picture Quality with 13 MP Rear Camera and 5.0 MP Front Camera.Its Gives 2300 mAh (Li-Ion) Battery Backup.

title: Intex Aqua Star II HD
description: Aqua Star II HD Experience Life In True HD.Android Kitkat 4.4.2 Welcome to the world pf AQUA STAR II HD, Preloaded with the Super Smooth Android Operation System That Give you an unmatched multi-tasking experience.Power Packed Performance High Definition High Processing. Aqua Star II HD is powered with advanced processor and chipset that gives optimum Quality output without slowing you down.1.2GHz Quadcore Processor, 1 GB RAM, SC7731 Chipset.High Definition 5 Inch Display of Aqua Star II HD.

title: Intex Aqua Xtreme II
description: Display and ConfigurationThe Intex Aqua Xtreme 2 has a slim and stylish design along with a brushed back panel. It sports a 5.0-inch HD IPS LCD display with a screen resolution of 720 x 1,280 pixels along with a pixel density of 294 ppi. The display provides rich and vivid graphics to the user. It is powered by a strong 1.4GHz octa-core Cortex A7 processor with 2GB RAM which enables multi-tasking and saves the woes of application lags. It comes loaded with Android v4.4 (KitKat) Operating System.Camera and MemoryThe Intex Aqua Xtreme 2 is equipped with a 13.0MP rear camera with LED flash and auto focus and a front camera of 5.0MP for online video chatting. The cameras have features like live photo mode, face beauty mode, panorama, smile shot, HDR and selfie by Bluetooth and earphone. It also has a front camera of 5.0MP for online video chatting and clicking selfies. The device has ample internal memory of 16GB and allows users to extend the memory of up to 32GB with a microSD-card to store all necessary data. Connectivity and BatteryThe Intex Aqua Xtreme 2 It is a dual SIM phone and offers a wide range of connectivity options like 3G, GPRS, EDGE and Wi-Fi to connect it to the internet. And Bluetooth and USB as well. The phone is backed by a powerful 2000mAh Li-ion battery which gives a talk time of up to 8 hours and a standby time of up to 300 hours.VerdictThe Intex Aqua Xtreme 2 is packed with powerful features, and is an apt solution if you are looking for a powerful smartphone with gaming and multitasking capabilities within a budget. Moreover, the device is slim, lightweight and poses an attractive design.

title: Nokia Lumia 620
description: Nokia has added yet another feather to its cap with the Nokia Lumia 620, a smartphone that is powered by windows and is well within your budget without cutting any corners. Cinemagraph A unique app that crosses the worlds between still photos and videos, the Cinemagraph allows you to add motion to images ‰ÛÒ you have to just pick the points you want animated in a picture that you click with the 5 megapixel primary camera.åÊ City Lens Hold up the HERE City lens app to show all the businesses, shops, restaurants around you along with detailed information to help you make decisions like reviews, directions and links ‰ÛÒ the Lumia 620 is handy like that.åÊ Smart Shoot With the feature, you can take the best parts and expressions from a series of photos to create one perfect group photo to make memories that everyone looks great in. MS Office With Outlook, Excel, Word and PowerPoint integration, the Lumia 620 allows you to keep in sync with the office and work wherever you are. Make reports, crunch numbers and even do a quick presentation on your phone, it is that easy.åÊ Nokia Music With the MixRadio feature on the Lumia 620, you can stream music from a wide variety of channels and listen to them offline as well. While there are presents to choose from, you can also create your own custom playlists as well for a musical experience that is truly you.

title: Nokia Lumia 625
description: Taking the Lumia legacy to the next level is the 625, typically Nokia, sturdy, stylish and powerful. Big-screen experience, Super sensitive touch View the action on the centre stage with the 4.7 inch touchscreen on the Lumia 625 ‰ÛÒ everything looks so much better on the large screen as entertainment gets a new high. The capacitive touch ensures that you have a smooth as silk scrolling experience that works even when you are wearing gloves or using your fingernails. High Quality Video The 5 megapixel camera on the phone comes with full HD recording capabilities; the Lumia 625 ensures that the sweet moments of life that you want to relive over and over again are captured in full detail, with a clarity that brings the moment back to life, whenever you want, wherever you want. Unique semi-transparent shell design The smartphone is designed with gentle curves and a shell design that is semi-transparent. In hep colors, the phone is one that you will love whipping out every chance you get. HERE Maps A boon for the geographically challenged, HERE maps from the house of Nokia makes is simple for you to navigate, be it right at homeground or when you are travelling. You can even download sections and store them offline to assist on a daily basis without you having to use up precious data.

title: Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge
description: Crafted from glass and metal, the Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge is a revolutionary smartphone that comes with a Quad HD Super AMOLED display, 16 MP camera and lightning-fast 64-bit, octa-core processor. Its curved design lets you access notifications and control different functions easily. Beautiful Display Watch your favorite movie or play your favorite game on this smartphone as it is equipped with a 13 cm (5.1) Quad HD Super AMOLED display, which produces a pixel resolution of 2560 x 1440 and has a pixel density of 577 ppi. The edge of the phone gives you quick access to your notifications and other functions. Incredible Camera Capture every moment with the Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge as it comes with an auto real-time HDR, fast f/1.9 aperture and smart optical image stabilization, which guarantees crisp photos in any light environment. It comes with a 5 MP front camera and a 16 MP rear camera. Wireless Charging Charge your phone without any wires as the Samsung Galaxy S6 features built-in wireless charging capabilities. Its 2600 mAh battery lets you browse the net, play games and take calls for hours on end. On Ultra Power Saving mode, you can text and make calls even with 10% battery. Performance Get lightning performance on your Samsung Galaxy S6 as it comes with a 64-bit, Octa-Core processor, and 3 GB RAM, which ensures ultra-quick multitasking capabilities. It is also powered by an Android Lollipop v5.0 operating system. Finger Scan Keep your phone secure at all times with the Galaxy S6 Edge's finger scanning feature, which recognizes your unique ID and keeps unwanted users from accessing your personal information. Connectivity This smartphone is Bluetooth-enabled, which means you can transfer files, music and documents with other Bluetooth devices without any wires. The phone also connects to wireless internet networks which allow you to browse the web at a moment's notice. This phone can also connect to 4G LTE networks which results in super-fast web browsing wherever you go. Sensors This smartphone comes with a number of useful sensors such as an Accelerometer, Geo-magnetic, Gyroscope, RGB ambient light sensor, Proximity sensor, Barometer, Hall sensor, Finger Scanner and Heart Rate Monitor.

title: Micromax Canvas Nitro 2
description: Watch a trending 9GAG video in HD while you check your text messages, or take breathtaking snaps of passing scenery from your car with this impressive smartphone. Powerful Octa-core Processor Applications like WhatsApp and Facebook will seamlessly operate in the background while you're playing Temple Run on this smartphone as it has a 1.4 GHz octa-core processor, 2 GB of DDR3 RAM and an MTK6592 chipset which ensure a powerful performance. Mesmerising HD IPS Screen Watch enchanting fantasy flicks in high quality on the 12.7 cm (5) HD IPS screen of this smartphone which has a resolution of 1280x720 pixels and a colour depth of 16.7 million. The screen is durable too as it is encased in Corning Gorilla Glass 3. Brilliant 13-MP Camera Thanks to a Sony IMX135 CMOS sensor and the Largan 5P lens, the 13-MP rear camera of this smartphone can capture marvelous, high-quality photos. The auto-focus and flash features bring greater clarity to images. Boasting a OV05648-G04A sensor, the 5MP FF front camera (F2.2 aperture) can take wide-angled (84-degree viewing scope) selfies. Style The 7.5-mm sleek form factor of this mobile adds a trending elegance to it. Android KitKat OS You can seamlessly operate and navigate through the applications of this smartphone as it has the Android KitKat 4.4.2 OS. Search for information on Google with voice commands by using the "Okay, Google" feature, and customize your contact list the way you see fit. Use the Hangouts app to stay in touch with friends. Smart Gestures Gesture unlock, upside speaker, upside silent, gesture dial phone, gesture answer phone, gesture camera snap, proximity incoming call and gesture browse gallery are the various smart gesture options that are available on this phone for you to simplify the way you use it. Video Pinning Pin the video of your choice on the screen of this smartphone and watch it as your reply to text messages or while you use another application. Connectivity The 3G, Wi-Fi and Bluetooth features can be used to stream online videos or transfer files to another phone. Free Pre-Loaded Apps Newshunt, Paytm, Quikr, Snapdeal, Swiftkey, Dr. Saftey, Hotstar, MAD, App center, ASKME, Chaatz, Clean master, Opera Mini, Saavn, Truecaller Giga Jump and Marbles are the various applications that this phone comes pre-loaded with.

title: Lenovo S90 Or Sisley S90
description: At times, a smartphone becomes your saviour. In this day and age, a smartphone helps you stay in touch with your family and friends even while on business trips. The Lenovo Sisley S90 gives you that freedom and more. The Super AMOLED Experience With a 127 mm screen size, the S90‰Ûªs Super AMOLED screen packs an HD multimedia experience that‰Ûªll rock your socks off. You can watch movies while you commute to work, and share videos with friends and family. Smile! You‰Ûªre on Camera! Featuring a 13 MP primary camera with auto-focus and LED flash, and an 8 MP secondary camera, this mobile phone enables you to take awesome shots and selfies. Backpacking across the country side? Take awe-inspiring panorama shots and share online. Post selfies of yourself with some camels if your friends don‰Ûªt believe you. Empowering You With a Qualcommå¨ Snapdragon‰ã¢ MSM8916 64-bit 1.2GHz Quad Core processor, 2 GB RAM and 32 GB of inbuilt storage space, this phone makes playing around with a wide selection of apps as easy as pie. Connected to the World With dual micro SIM slots, connect to 2G or 3G networks with ease. A-GPS allows you to broadcast your location and let your pals know where you are for a quick meet up. Multimedia At Your Fingertips Easily connect your headphones to this mobile using the 3.5 mm jack and start listening to your complete music collection on the go. If you prefer wireless, buy a pair of bluetooth headphones and pair them with this phone to use them at the gym or anywhere else. Android KitKat With Android v4.4, the experience of using a smartphone becomes as easy as stealing candy from a baby.

title: Sony Xperia M4 Aqua Dual
description: The Sony Xperia M4 Aqua Dual is a mid-range waterproof Sony smartphone that packs a decent processor and screen, noteworthy camera and excellent battery life. Waterproof With a high IP rating of IP65/68, this Sony smartphone has been designed to resist fine dust particles and water as long as all the ports and attached covers are firmly closed. It can be submerged up to 1.5 meters in fresh water for up to 30 minutes. Primary Camera Capture your favorite moments in crystal-clear clarity with the 13 MP primary camera which is equipped with an EXMOR RS sensor and HDR. Superior Auto Whether you are clicking a night view or taking a close-up shot, the Superior Auto feature has been tuned to recognize up to 52 scenarios. This feature automatically adjusts the settings, so that you get the perfect shots in any situation. HDR The HDR mode captures the same image in different exposures and layers them so that you get clear photos and videos. This is an essential feature while capturing photos and videos against a strong backlight or in high contrast situations. Exmor RS Get detailed shots with rich colors, exceptional clarity and minimal noise under any lighting conditions, thanks to the Exmor RS image sensor technology. Front Camera Take amazing selfies or group selfies with the 5 MP front camera that comes with a super wide-angle lens. Auto Scene Recognition Thanks to Auto Scene Recognition, you get to capture great selfies irrespective of the lighting condition or scenario. 22 mm Wide View Fit in more of the view or all of your friends in one shot, thanks to the 22 mm wide-angle lens with an 88-degree field. Movie Creator This app lets you create blockbusters using your photos and videos, and share them with your friends and family. AR Fun Scribble messages or draw fun animations and objects before you take the photo with this AR Fun app. Portrait Retouch For beautiful selfies, the Portrait Retouch app offers 10 different beauty styles, make-up effects, and decorative frames. Sound Photo Add up to 10 seconds of audio with your photos via the Sound Photo app. Share these sound photos with your friends through PlayMemories Online. Download More Apps Apart from the pre-installed apps, this Xperia smartphone offers you a wide variety of camera apps that can be downloaded easily. Battery Life The powerful 2400 m Ah battery offers up to two days of battery life, so you can click lots of photos while out on a trip without worrying about your phone running out of battery. Besides, you can activate Battery STAMINA Mode to make your battery last longer. Battery Modes The Extended Standby Mode lets standby mode last 4x times longer. Extended usage mode increases usage time up to 14%. Ultra STAMINA mode squeezes out every bit of battery charge by limiting your phone's functions to calls and messages only. Display This Sony smartphone comes with a stunningly bright 12.7 cm (5) HD display, so you can enjoy watching your favourite videos or playing games in excellent visual clarity. The IPS technology ensures a clear view from any angle and accurate color reproduction from edge to edge. Design Thanks to Sony's OmniBalance design, this phone is comfortable to hold and use. It features a subtle metallic frame, matte finish on the back and Sony's distinctive aluminium power button. Speed The 64-bit octa-core processor (Qualcomm Snapdragon 615) streams videos lag-free, ensures faster web browsing and allows efficient multitasking. It comes with a built-in LTE/4G modem which enables extremely fast internet connections with up to 150 Mbit/s download and 50 Mbit/s upload speeds.

title: Samsung Galaxy S Duos 3
description: Stay connected with the chit-chat on Facebook or Twitter by seamlessly surfing the net on this smartphone. You can also play a host of games while on the move. This pocket-friendly smartphone has been finely crafted and operates on Android's KitKat interface. Operating System Featuring Android KitKat 4.4.2, this smartphone allows you to seamlessly browse through its applications without glitches. This OS is quite intuitive as it comes with the updated version of TouchWiz Essence UX. With 14 different regional languages for you to message with, this smartphone is truly versatile and competent. Design A glimmer of elegance lies in this phone's chrome-finish edges, and the premium, textured-finish of the backcover gives your hand the certainty of a firm grip. Advanced Camera Foster the professional photographer in you by taking photos of inspirational scenery, ancient relics or cloudy skies with this smartphone's 5 MP primary camera. A host of camera modes allow you to give images added effect and depth. Videos are recorded at 30 FPS on this phone, so they are very clear. Display Play Temple Run or watch awe-inspiring movies on the 10.16-cm display screen of this smartphone which produces clear and crisp images. Performance The 1.2 GHz dual-core processor and 512 MB RAM of this smartphone allow you to run many apps seamlessly at the same time. Connectivity Separate your work from your personal life by using two different SIMs at the same time with this phone. 3G, Wi-Fi and Bluetooth allow you to stay connected to your friends on Facebook or hooked to a conversation on WhatsApp no matter where you go. Storage This phone offers a storage space of 4 GB, so you can store loads of tracks, video clips and more on it.

title: Sony Xperia E4 Dual Sim
description: The Sony Xperia E4 Dual is a long-lasting smartphone which comes with a 5" screen, fun apps and a two-day battery that lets you enjoy the phone's exciting features for hours at a stretch. Battery The Xperia E4 Dual comes with a 2300 mAh battery which gives you up to 2 days of battery life on a single charge. With such a battery, you can get up to 6.5 hours of video playback and up to 48 hours of audio playback. Extended Standby Mode This phone comes with an Extended Standby Mode which gives it a standby time that lasts up to four times as long. This mode switches off your apps and functions when you're not using the display. You will still be able to receive calls, alarms, texts and other notifications which you can choose in the settings menu. Extended Usage Mode If you are low on battery and still have a lot to do on your phone, simply switch it to the extended usage mode to boost your usage time by up to 14%. Ultra Standby Mode This mode limits your phone to core functions - such as SMS and calls - which squeezes out every drop of your battery. Design This smartphone is a true example of craftsmanship, as its round shape and textured surface makes it easy to hold in your hands. Display The Xperia E4 dual is fitted with a bright 12.7 cm (5)åÊqHD display which brings your favorite games, apps and videos to life. It also uses an IPS technology which offers an improved viewing angle, sharp images, and accurate colors. Camera This smartphone is equipped with a 5 MP primary camera and comes with Sony's innovative auto scene recognition feature and HDR, which results in beautiful, vivid photos. It also has a 2 MP secondary camera which lets you take fun 'selfies'. Auto Scene Recognition The Xperia E4 Dual has an auto scene recognition feature which recognizes up to 52 scenarios and automatically adjusts the settings to get incredible photos wherever you go. HDR HDR (High Dynamic Range) is a technology which is used to capture clear photos against strong backlight. This feature captures the image at different exposure levels to create an optimized photo which you can share with your friends and family. Camera Apps The Xperia E4 takes your entertainment experience to a whole new level with fun-filled apps that will make good times with your friends more memorable. AR Fun This app allows you to draw on top of your picture to create fun photos that you and your friends will remember for a long time. Portrait Retouch With Portrait Retouch, you can choose from 10 different beauty styles, make-up effects, and decorative frames to better your selfies. Live On YouTube Broadcast every moment as it happens with Live on YouTube. You can get your friends' responses on the screen, allowing you to keep the conversation going in real time. Sound Photo You can capture up to 10 seconds of audio with the photos and share it with your friends through PlayMemories Online. Sound This smartphone is equipped with an xLOUD enhancement engine which delivers your music with richer sound and powerful bass performance. It comes with Clear Audio technologies which minimize distortion and restores balance and clarity to your music tracks. This phone automatically selects the right settings for your songs. Performance Browse through web pages, play fun games and listen to your favorite songs simultaneously as the Sony Xperia E4 dual comes with a 1.3 GHz quad-core processor which gives you high performance without draining the battery. It has 1 GB of RAM and 8 GB of internal memory to store your videos, photos, and songs. Switch to Sony With Xperia Transfer, you can move all your important stuff on to the phone easily, making it the perfect phone to switch over to. Connectivity Enjoy switching between calls as this phone comes with Dual SIM feature which lets youåÊput conversations on hold, while you attend another call, without it going to voicemail. This phone comes with both Wi-Fi and Wi-Fi hotspot to connect to wireless internet networks. It can also transfer files with other devices via Bluetooth 4.1.

title: Sony Xperia C3
description: Never miss out on a selfie moment with the Sony Xperia C3. This smartphone features a 5 MP front-facing camera with a super wide-angle lens and soft LED flash that allows you to incredible photos with minimum effort. Camera The Sony Xperia C3 comes with 8 MP rear-facing camera and a powerful 5 MP front camera. With a unique soft LED flash, superior auto mode and a 25 mm wide-angle view, you can expect nothing less than high definition. The camera also features Sony's Exmor RS technology takes highly detailed shots with low noise - even in low-lit conditions. Camera Apps Make your photos and selfies even more attractive with a number of camera apps that you can download from the phone's online store. These apps allow you to add a number of effects, colors and filters which enhances the photo's overall value. Display The Sony Xperia C3 features a massive 14 cm, 720 p HD Display that boasts Sony's TV technologies. The phone has an IPS feature which gives you perfect viewing from any angle. It also has a pixel resolution of 1280x720. Sleek Design At 7.6mm, the Sony Experia C3 is a slim, sleek smartphone that can fit almost anywhere. The phone also weighs 150 g, making it easier for you to carry it around. Lightning Performance The Sony Xperia C3 comes with a Qualcomm Snapdragon 400 Quad-Core Processor which allows you to run multiple apps simultaneously with ease. This processor has a clock speed of 1.2GHz and gives you maximum performance without draining of battery. Long Lasting Battery With Sony's Battery Stamina Mode, you are able to enjoy more hours of fun with your Xperia C3. This mode extends your phone's standby time up to 4 times. The phone will automatically switch off the display, apps and other functions that are idle for a long time. Connectivity The Sony Xperia C3 comes with Near Field Communication which gives you a quick way to wirelessly connect to any nearby electronic devices. You can even connect your phone to a WiFi enabled TV via DLNA or WiFi Miracast. Dual SIM The Sony Xperia C3 comes with a Dual SIM feature that allows you to use up to 2 SIM cards at the same time. Separate your work from pleasure, all on one phone.

title: Sony Xperia M4 Aqua Dual
description: The Sony Xperia M4 Aqua Dual is a mid-range waterproof Sony smartphone that packs a decent processor and screen, noteworthy camera and excellent battery life. Waterproof Phone With a high IP rating of IP65/68, this Sony smartphone has been designed to resist fine dust particles and water as long as all the ports and attached covers are firmly closed. The IPS technology ensures a clear view from any angle and accurate color reproduction from edge to edge. Design Thanks to Sony's OmniBalance design, this phone is comfortable to hold and use. It features a subtle metallic frame, matte finish on the back and Sony's distinctive aluminium power button. Speed The 64-bit Octa-core processor (Qualcomm Snapdragon 615) streams videos lag-free, ensures faster web browsing and allows efficient multitasking. title: Apple iPhone 6 Plus
description: The iPhone 6 Plus is not only bigger, it's better in every way. The iPhone 6 Plus boasts a large Retina Display on a slim, smooth metal surface. It is the perfect combination of hardware and software functions and it can be in your pocket right now. Sleek Design The best part of the iPhone 6 Plus is its innovative design. The cover glass curves around the sides to join the anodized aluminum enclosure in a modest design with no distinct edges or gaps. It's a seamless fusion of metal and glass that feels incredible in your hands. Bigger and Better Display The iPhone 6 Plus comes with a 5.5-inch Retina HD display that can produce a pixel resolution of 1920x1080 at 401 Pixels per inch. The Multi-touch Display comes with full sRGB color standards, white balance and brightness. The phone also uses UV light to rightly position the display's liquid crystals, resulting in a better viewing experience. State-of-the-Art Technology The iPhone 6 Plus comes with Apple's latest microchip - the all-new A8 Chip. This microchip's graphics and CPU performance are faster than iPhone 5's A7 chipåÊwhile managing a larger display and other features. It uses an advanced 20-nanometer process that results in incredibly quick performances. M8 Coprocessor Technology and Sensors This phone comes with an M8 coprocessor that measures data from its sensors such as the accelerometer, compass and gyroscope, allowing you to measure your steps and distance. It even measures changes in elevation. Stunning Photography The iPhone 6 Plus comes with an iSight camera that makes it easier to take pictures. With large 1.5-micron pixels and f/2.2 aperture, it is arguably the most popular camera that captures 1080 p HD videos at 60 frames per second. You can also take slow motion videos in 720 p resolution at 240 frames per second. Faster Connectivity The iPhone 6 comes with an ultra-fast wireless technology that allows you to connect to high-speed wireless networks wherever you go. With 802.11ac WiFi, you can connect to wireless networks up to 3 times faster than 802.11n networks. It also has Bluetooth 4.0. Touch ID Enjoy security at your fingertips thanks to the iPhone 6 Plus' fingerprint password that allows you to protect your phone from other users. It not only unlocks your phone, it can also be used to approve purchases on the App Store or iTunes. iOS 8 The iPhone 6 Plus comes with the latest operating system from Apple - iOS 8. This operating system comes with a number of incredible features that streamline your workflow wherever you go. The iPhone 6 Plus also comes with a bunch of new apps that make everyday lively, exciting and organized.

Incredibly light, the beautifully crafted iPhone 6 feels great in your hands. Thanks to its innovative design, the iPhone 6 provides an intuitive experience and is extremely easy to use. The iPhone 6's 8 MP iSight camera gets new features such as a new sensor with Focus Pixels, improved face detection and exposure control. Also, now you can take amazing 1080p HD videos with the world's most popular camera. Security Make life easier with the iPhone 6's breakthrough Touch ID technology. Now you can securely access your phone with your fingerprint - no more worries about forgetting your pass code ever again. Moreover, the iPhone 6 lets you use your fingerprint to securely make purchases on iTunes or the App Store. Operating System The iPhone 6 comes with the biggest iOS release ever - the iOS 8. Featuring new capabilities and features, the world's advanced mobile operating system - the iOS 8 - gives you an incredible experience on your iPhone 6. Connectivity Thanks to the advanced Wi-Fi support with fast wireless performance, you can keep up with the world around you easily. Moreover, the iPhone 6 comes with Bluetooth and 3G support. With a 12.7 cm (5) 720p black waterfall fully laminated IPS screen, the Honor 4C is perfect for watching videos or playing games. It also comes with a quad-core Mali-450 image processor which improves GPU performance, ensuring that your images and videos are crisp and clear. Strong Signal Reception This phone has a higher signal reception by 3dB when compared to other phones in its range. This results in clear conversations even when the signal is weak, such as underground garages or other marginal coverage areas. It has a macro mode at the centimeter level for close up shots and a 27 mm wide angle lens for landscape shots. You can expect up to 80 hours of light usage and up to 50 hours of moderate usage with this phone.

Processor This phone comes loaded with powerful Qualcommå¨ Snapdragon‰ã¢ S4 Pro processor, a dual core processor that is ideal for an HD smartphone. This processor provides efficient multitasking without draining the battery, mainly because it asynchronous, that is, each core is independently powered, implying that you get the precise amount of power that you need. Battery Put the phone on STAMINA mode and save keep your battery from running out. On STAMINA mode, the Wi-Fi and data traffic are disabled during standby. This is mode can be customized so that you can choose which notifications you want to receive and which you wish to ignore, so as to keep the power from draining.

title: Apple iPhone 5S
description: A smartphone that is created to surpass the boundaries of technology, the iPhone 5S from Apple becomes an indispensible part of your life. A fine blend of powerful hardware with software designed to help the hardware reach its true potential, 5S is all set to change the way smartphones work. Touch ID A smartphone locking system that is first of its kind, the iPhone 5S comes with Touch ID, a fingerprint identity sensor that recognizes your fingerprint on the Home button to unlock the phone, dispensing off with tedious passcodes and pattern locks. A7-chip Processor One step faster than fast itself, the iPhone 5S is a 64-bit smartphone that holds the A7-chip to give you twice the performance. The iPhone 5S also captures full HD videos which you can take in slow motion or zoom in during the shoot itself to customize, to capture and to hold precious memories close. The 1.2 megapixel secondary camera for FaceTime comes with better illumination sensors and larger pixels to ensures that your video chats are in HD quality as well.åÊ iOS 7 An operating system that has been designed with the iPhone 5S in mind, the 4-inch retina display screen brings icons alive. Connectivity and Storage With 13 LTE bands, the 5S ensures that you connect to the net to browse and download faster than ever. It also comes with a 32 GB storage capacity to make space for all the apps, media, music and files that you need.

title: Moto X (2nd Generation)
description: Pure Style. Pure Performance. Pure Voice. Pure Simplicity. The all-new Moto X is here to captivate you with its aesthetically pleasing design and high-end technical features. Pure Style The all-new Moto X showcases a curved metal frame design that fits easily and comfortably in your hands. The Moto X also comes with a water-resistant coating to protect it from accidental splashes. Pure Performance Enjoy seamless multitasking, faster response rates, and reduced battery drain with the 2.5 GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon quad-core processor and 2 GB RAM of the all-new Moto X. The second generation Moto X runs on Android KitKat which further boosts the performance and battery life of the device. The OS is upgradeable to Android 5.0 Lollipop. Stunning HD Display Enjoy crisp and crystal-clear photos and videos in 1080 p on the remarkable 5.2 inch HD display of the new Moto X. The Corning Gorilla Glass 3 protects the beautiful OLED display from scratches and damages. Also, the Moto X displays notifications and updates without interrupting your activities. Best Voice Experience Control the all-new Moto X with just your voice. You can create your own voice prompt, post your status on Facebook, send a message through WhatsApp, or just ask questions - your Moto X will obey every command without you having to even touch the phone. Moto Assist Truly a smartphone, the all-new Moto X learns your preferences and adapts to your situations accordingly. Depending on whether you are at the office, or driving, or attending a meeting, your Moto X will adapt its behaviour to your situation and give information accordingly. Moto Actions Use simple gestures to respond to your Moto X - just wave your hand over the Moto X to silence calls or just flick your wrist twice to launch the camera. Intuitive Camera Twist your wrist, launch the Moto X's 13 MP primary camera, and click remarkable pictures with the first ever ring-flash that gives more balanced light and less shadows. Your Moto X clicks multiple pictures before and after you touch the screenåÊso that you can choose the best from the lot. 4-Mic Technology Bid goodbye to background noise with the Moto X's exclusive 4-mic technology. Not only does this technology eliminate background noise, it also ensures that you are heard clearly whether you are in a crowded market or stuck in traffic. Battery Enjoy all-day battery life with the powerful 2300 mAh battery of the all-new Moto X. It boasts battery life of up to 24 hours on mixed usage. Storage The Moto X offers 32 GB of internal storage space for all your music, photos, videos, applications and documents. The Moto X does not feature an SD card slot; hence you cannot expand the storage on this device. Connectivity Enjoy endless connectivity with friends and family via 3G or Wi-Fi on the Moto X. The Moto X lets you transfer data easily to other devices via Bluetooth or USB. Sensors The all-new Moto X comes with a gyroscope, an accelerometer, a compass, and a proximity sensor. These sensors help your Moto X connect better with you and the outside world.

title: Karbonn Titanium S4
description: Karbonn puts together the best of power, performance and pleasant looks to present the Titanium S4 that is a cut above the rest in its class. Life. Large. Beautiful. A beautifully large 4.7 inch AMOLED touchscreen catches your eye ‰ÛÒ the Titanium S4 spares no pixel with its HD resolution screen that comes with capacitive multitouch support to amplify the colors, brightness, sharpness and contrast of anything that you view on it with better viewability in sunlight and great viewing angles. Biting Off Jelly Bean The Titanium S4 is armed with the Jelly Bean (v.4.2) operating system that is designed to be fast, fluid and smooth with graphics and memory working together in a smart manner to give you better efficiency with great battery management. The Android OS makes the phone more responsive while bringing together all your notifications to one place that you can take action on immediately or later, whichever suits your style. With Google Now integration for information at the fingertips and gesture typing support to shoot off messages in a jiffy, the UI is more intuitive than ever, simplifying your day to day tasks. Pumping Power A quad core processor clocked at 1.2 GHz supported by 1 GB of RAM allows the smartphone to process in a jiffy handling all actions that you perform without any lag or hitch. What‰Ûªs more, multitasking and switching between apps without annoying delays is easy with four cores at your disposal. With power comes power-efficiency as well, because the cores are utilized sensibly to ensure that there is good management of battery. Capturing Life Real-Time 13 megapixels at the back and 2 megapixels on the front ‰ÛÒ the cameras on the Titanium S4 ensure that not a moment passes by without you having the opportunity to capture it. Be it a cute animal or your delicious lunch or even a selfie to make a statement, the S4 is capable of catering to your needs. The primary camera sports flash support and comes with auto focus as well. Power and Space Management The phone sports a 1800 mAh battery to power it and comes with an expandable memory of up to 32 GB. With support for two SIM cards, the Titanium S4 lets you get the benefits of having two connections without the hassle of two phones. Sensible Sensors A plethora of sensors are built into the phone to ensure that it gives you a more intuitive performance ‰ÛÒ the proximity sensor to sense movement nearby, accelerometer for gaming and the orientation of the screen and the ambient light sensor that adjusts screen brightness according to surroundings. Connecting You Connect to the net and browse at impressive speeds with this Karbonn smartphone that comes with both 3G and Wi-Fi support, the latter can also be used to turn the phone into a hotspot via tethering.

title: Apple iPhone 6
description: The bigger the better - the Apple iPhone 6 is an exemplar of this phrase. The meticulously crafted iPhone 6 is truly an epitome of great taste and elegance. Incredibly light, the beautifully crafted iPhone 6 feels great in your hands. Thanks to its innovative design, the iPhone 6 provides an intuitive experience and is extremely easy to use. Brilliant Display Featuring the thinnest and most advanced Multi-Touch display ever made, the Apple iPhone 6 promises a high-contrast output with incredible colors and brightness on its 4.7 inch Retina HD display. A resolution of 1334x750 pixels, clear wide-angle viewing and an improved polariser - the iPhone 6 truly offers a bigger and better display. Power-Packed Performance Thanks to the all-new A8 processor with 64-bit architecture and an advanced 20 nanometre process, the iPhone 6 delivers an incredibly powerful performance while being extremely efficient. The iPhone 6's 8 MP iSight camera gets new features such as a new sensor with Focus Pixels, improved face detection and exposure control. Also, now you can take amazing 1080p HD videos with the world's most popular camera. Security Make life easier with the iPhone 6's breakthrough Touch ID technology. Now you can securely access your phone with your fingerprint - no more worries about forgetting your pass code ever again. Moreover, the iPhone 6 lets you use your fingerprint to securely make purchases on iTunes or the App Store. Operating System The iPhone 6 comes with the biggest iOS release ever - the iOS 8. Featuring new capabilities and features, the world's advanced mobile operating system - the iOS 8 - gives you an incredible experience on your iPhone 6. Connectivity Thanks to the advanced Wi-Fi support with fast wireless performance, you can keep up with the world around you easily. Moreover, the iPhone 6 comes with Bluetooth and 3G support. Battery Take advantage of all the features of your highly efficient Apple iPhone 6 which boasts of an amazing battery life with up to 14 hours of 3G talk time and up to 250 hours of standby.

title: Apple iPhone 6 Plus
description: The iPhone 6 Plus is not only bigger, it's better in every way. The iPhone 6 Plus boasts a large Retina Display on a slim, smooth metal surface. It is the perfect combination of hardware and software functions and it can be in your pocket right now. Sleek Design The best part of the iPhone 6 Plus is its innovative design. The cover glass curves around the sides to join the anodized aluminum enclosure in a modest design with no distinct edges or gaps. It's a seamless fusion of metal and glass that feels incredible in your hands. Bigger and Better Display The iPhone 6 Plus comes with a 5.5-inch Retina HD display that can produce a pixel resolution of 1920x1080 at 401 Pixels per inch. The Multi-touch Display comes with full sRGB color standards, white balance and brightness. The phone also uses UV light to rightly position the display's liquid crystals, resulting in a better viewing experience. State-of-the-Art Technology The iPhone 6 Plus comes with Apple's latest microchip - the all-new A8 Chip. This microchip's graphics and CPU performance are faster than iPhone 5's A7 chip while managing a larger display and other features. It uses an advanced 20-nanometer process that results in incredibly quick performances. M8 Coprocessor Technology and Sensors This phone comes with an M8 coprocessor that measures data from its sensors such as the accelerometer, compass, and gyroscope, allowing you to measure your steps and distance. It even measures changes in elevation. Stunning Photography The iPhone 6 Plus comes with an iSight camera that makes it easier to take pictures. With large 1.5-micron pixels and f/2.2 aperture, it is arguably the most popular camera that captures 1080p HD videos at 60 frames per second. You can also take slow motion videos in 720p resolution at 240 frames per second. Faster Connectivity The iPhone 6 comes with an ultra-fast wireless technology that allows you to connect to high-speed wireless networks wherever you go. With 802.11ac WiFi, you can connect to wireless networks up to 3 times faster than 802.11n networks. It also has Bluetooth 4.0. Touch ID Enjoy security at your fingertips thanks to the iPhone 6 Plus' fingerprint password that allows you to protect your phone from other users. It not only unlocks your phone, it can also be used to approve purchases on the App Store or iTunes. iOS 8 The iPhone 6 Plus comes with the latest operating system from Apple - iOS 8. This operating system comes with a number of incredible features that streamline your workflow wherever you go. The iPhone 6 Plus also comes with a bunch of new apps that make everyday lively, exciting and organized.

description: Crafted from glass and metal, the Samsung Galaxy S6 is a revolutionary smartphone that comes with a Quad HD Super AMOLED display, 16 MP camera and lightning-fast 64-bit, octa-core processor. Beautiful Display Watch your favorite movie or play your favorite game on this smartphone as it is equipped with a 13 cm (5.1) Quad HD Super AMOLED display, which produces a pixel resolution of 2560 x 1440 and has a pixel density of 577ppi. Its 2550 mAh battery lets you browse the net, play games and take calls for hours on end. On Ultra Power Saving mode, you can text and make calls even with 10% battery. Performance Get lightning performance on your Samsung Galaxy S6 as it comes with a 64-bit, Octa-Core processor, and 3 GB RAM, which ensures ultra-quick multitasking capabilities. It is also powered by an Android Lollipop v5.0 operating system. Finger Scan Keep your phone secure at all times with the Galaxy S6's finger scanning feature, which recognizes your unique ID and keeps unwanted users from accessing your personal information. Connectivity This smartphone is Bluetooth-enabled, which means you can transfer files, music and documents with other Bluetooth devices without any wires. The phone also connects to wireless internet networks which allow you to browse the web at a moment's notice. This phone can also connect to 4G LTE networks which result in super-fast web browsing wherever you go. Sensors This smartphone comes with a number of useful sensors such as an Accelerometer, Geo-magnetic, Gyroscope, RGB ambient light sensor, Proximity sensor, Barometer, Hall sensor, Finger Scanner and Heart Rate Monitor.

title: Apple iPhone 4S
description: Get ready to be impressed with the bold and impressive features of this Apple iPhone 4S. With a compact 8.89 cm (3.5) screen and a powerful A5 Chip this mobile phone ensures lightning speed and seamless performance at all times. With the 0.3 MP front camera, you can video chat with friends and family even when you are miles away from them. Performance This iPhone 4S runs on A5 Chip to deliver a powerful performance. It operates on iOS 8 which offers new capabilities and features for an incredible experience. Storage This smartphone from Apple offers a storage space of 8 GB so you can store apps, photos, songs, and more. Connectivity This iPhone 4S is Wi-Fi enabled and supports 3G connectivity so you can browse the Web or download a file from the e-mail wherever you are. This phone also supports Bluetooth. Qualcomm Snapdragon 800 Watch your apps perform at blazing speeds with the Optimus G2 which packs the Qualcomm Snapdragon 800 Processor with 2.26 GHz Quad Core CPUs that ensures that all functions are seamless. title: Nexus 5
description: Rounding off Android perfection and providing the experience that was truly intended by Google when they created the operating system, the Nexus 5 is a beautiful device that packs high-powered hardware with flawless software ‰ÛÒ a never-fail combination. Android v4.4 (KitKat) OS The first ever smartphone that comes with the KitKat operating system, the Nexus 5 provides a smart and simple Android 4.4 for you to work with. Personalization being the keyword, the phone allows you to customize extensively to ensure that your Nexus is uniquely yours. Go hands-free with Voice Actions that simplifies sending texts, finding photos, using maps and everything else that you can think of doing on a daily basis. A beautiful, full screen experience that is simple and immersive, KitKat allows you to multitask without compromising on accuracy or speed. The phone also collates numbers that you call frequently and searches for matches when you get a call from an unknown number. Talk about intuitive.åÊ Capturing with Clarity The device from Google comes with an 8 megapixel camera that comes armed with HDR+ technology to ensure that every picture that you click is perfect. The much-loved Photo Sphere also makes it appearance to ensure that you have a 360 degree view of that view from the window that you can relive anytime you want. The phone also sports a 1.3 megapixel secondary camera. The Nexus 5 is also capable of taking backup of your photos automatically to ensure that you never lose a precious memory while not clogging up phone space. If you are feeling loath to enhance those vacation pictures for family viewing, just run Auto Awesome to create animations, collages and panorama shots from the existing photos in your library. There is also the option of having them turned into memorable videos with music and the works. Powerhouse Processor To say powerful would be an understatement for the 2.3 GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon 800 Processor with support from 2 GB RAM ensures that you burn through apps without any lag or delay whatsoever. The smartphone comes with the necessary hardware to ensure that you take full advantage of the experience that Google strives to provide ‰ÛÒ tapping on an app and drumming your fingers on the table impatiently waiting for it to load is passÌ© with the Nexus 5. Perfection on Display With full High Definition and 445 ppi of pixel density, the Nexus 5‰Ûªs 4.95 inch LCD screen shows you the world as it is. Everything looks great on the IPS screen, from any angle, be it pictures of your vacation or even just the font of the menus ‰ÛÒ sharper, clearer and denser. Storage and Communication With NFC, LTE and Wi-Fi support, being social and in touch is a cinch with the Nexus 5. 16 GB of internal storage at your disposal for anything and everything that you can think of storing within your phone is aided and abetted by access to effective Cloud storage as well. The unit also comes with wireless charging of the 2300 mAh battery that is built-in for convenience. With the promise of being the first to latch on to further versions of the operating system, the Nexus 5 is arguably the best smartphone of its class.

title: XOLO Q1000 Opus
description: Designed to let you flaunt the slim design, the Opus Q1000 is a smartphone from brand XOLO which has established itself for putting together great hardware with advanced software and presenting you with great performing phones that are well within your reach. Performance The slim body of this XOLO device packs a powerful performer in the 1.2 GHz Quad Core processor that is assisted by 1 GB RAM to ensure that app launches, games and even browsing through the phone is easier and faster. Multitasking is made quicker as well, allowing you to do more with less and unprecedented crashes and lags are a thing of the past. What‰Ûªs more, with 312 MHz graphics, games that you play are fast, furious, crisp and very responsive. An Android device through and through, the Jelly Bean v4.2 gives you the freedom to personalize your phone while bringing small but very useful tweaks like bundled notifications, simpler interface and more accurate predictive input for a well-rounded and intuitive experience. Display The Opus Q1000 sports a 5 inch screen that is large enough to provide for immersive entertainment but small enough to still be portable. The FWVGA resolution screen comes with a color depth of 16M allowing for bright and crisp visuals and the IPS technology used ensures that there is no distortion, regardless of what angle you are viewing it from. Camera Don‰Ûªt let memories pass you by without capturing them for you to reminisce about later ‰ÛÒ carry the XOLO Opus that is armed with a 5 megapixel primary camera supported by LED flash to capture frames on the go. The device is also capable of HD video recording and sports a BSI sensor to ensure that even pictures in low-light conditions are bright and clear. The phone also has a 0.3 megapixel front camera to lend a face to your video chats. Battery and Storage A 2000 mAh battery powers this XOLO device to give you up to 11 hours of talktime on any 3G network. With 4 GB internal memory that can be extended up to 32 GB with a microSD card, the phone has enough space for all your apps, music and media without causing any restarts and crashes. Connectivity With both Wi-Fi and 3G support, you can browse the net with good speed and stream videos as well. Transferring data is a cinch with the microUSB that you can use to connect to your PC and Bluetooth to share a favorite tune or an image with a friend. Sensors The XOLO Opus Q1000 is armed with a variety of sensors to make it more intuitive to your needs ‰ÛÒ the accelerometer adjusts the screen orientation according to which way the phone is tilted, the proximity sensor detects when you are close by and dims the screen to avoid accidental touches and the ambient light sensor dulls and brightens the screen according to the surroundings to give you an optimized viewing experience.

title: Samsung Galaxy Trend
description: A smartphone crafted lovingly for those who truly love being the people that they are, the Galaxy Trend from Samsung is a device that lets you taste the effectiveness of Android and large screen entertainment. Multiple Language Support In an effort to make you feel completely at home, the S7392 from Samsung supports 9 Indian languages ‰ÛÒ Hindi, Bengali, Punjabi, Marathi, Gujarati, Kannada, Malayalam, Telugu and Tamil. You can change the global language for the phone itself, including the user interface apart from being able to text in the local language with a single swipe to toggle the keyboards. Like that‰Ûªs not enough, you can also change the way you browse the web and also find apps in the language of your choice. Truly one of its kind. Best of Both Worlds The Samsung Galaxy Trend comes with dual GSM SIM support allowing you to customize the way you use networks as well. Get the best of plans for voice and date with two connections that can help you keep your professional life away from the personal as well. Bringing together the experience of having two separate devices without the hassle, that‰Ûªs how simple this smartphone makes things for you.åÊ Larger Than Life With a 4 inch WVGA display with TFT capacitive touch, this Samsung smartphone ensures that what you see is crisp, rich and vivid. The size is just right to do justice to both productive functionalities like browsing and texting and also for fun sessions with your favorite games and music. This, complemented by the regional language support, ensures that the phone is one to reckon with. Performance The Galaxy Trend runs on an Android operating system aided by a 1GHz processor and 512 MB RAM. The latest Jelly Bean version ensures that you game with better graphics, everything is simple and easy to find apart from the interface being smoother, more functional and so much more fun to handle. Transitions are easy both on the hand and on the eye with this Android OS and more stability means less annoying crashes. With nifty functionalities like a 3 MP primary camera with zoom, 8 hours of talktime on 3G networks with the 1500 mAh battery, a 4 GB internal memory that can be extended up to 32 GB and connectivity options like GPRS, EDGE, 3G and Bluetooth, the phone packs quite a few features that you will not be able to live without. A seamless experience that will ensure that you get addicted to the way the smartphones are, the Samsung Galaxy Trend refuses to be discounted.

title: Lenovo A536
description: Say hello to the stylish Lenovo A536 which delivers a seamless, stutter-free performance. This affordable smartphone features a big screen, runs on Android KitKat and offers fast connectivity. Display Enjoy a satisfying visual experience on the big 12.7 cm (5) capacitive display. Surf the net, watch videos or play games in crystal-clear FWVGA resolution. Operating System This Lenovo device runs on Android KitKat 4.4 operating system. Enjoy the polished, beautiful design and enhanced performance of KitKat. Performance This smartphone offers a fluid performance and seamless multitasking, thanks to the quad-core processing power of the 1.3 GHz + MT6582M processor and 1 GB RAM. Camera Capture good quality photos and videos with the 5 MP rear camera. If you love to take selfies or you enjoy video chatting with friends across the globe, the 2 MP front camera is your best buddy. Fast Connectivity Instantly access your favourite social networking sites or stream a video without buffering, thanks to the fast HSPA+ connectivity and 21 Mbps download speed. You can also enjoy Wi-Fi and Bluetooth connectivity on this device. Dual SIM Whether you want to reap the benefits of different data plans or simply separate work from personal fun, the dual SIM option lets you enjoy two different numbers in one device. Lenovo Premium Apps Enjoy preloaded Lenovo DOit apps on this device. Transfer files wirelessly without Wi-Fi or network charges via SHAREit. Protect your phone from viruses and boost its performance with SECUREit. You can use SYNCit to backup or restore call logs, messages or contacts. Offline GPS Now you can use GPS even if you don't have a working internet connection, thanks to the satellite controlled GPS built-in to this device. Storage With 8 GB internal storage which is expandable up to 32 GB, you can store all your favourite music, photos and apps without worrying about running out of space. Battery A powerful 2000 mAh Li-Polymer battery powers this Lenovo smartphone.

title: Micromax Unite 3
description: Slim, compact and user-friendly, the Micromax Unite 3 is a good combination of powerful performance and nifty features for a great smartphone experience. Unite Messaging Service Chat with your friends and family without any language barrier, with this phone's Unite Messaging Service. Type your message and swipe to the right to translate your message from English to the language of your choice and vice versa. Your Phone, Your Language This smartphone comes pre-loaded with 10 regional languages, along with English. Type, chat or change the menu of your phone in the language you are the most comfortable with. Performance Powered by the 1.3 GHz Quad Core Processor and 1 GB RAM, the Micromax Unite 3 enables fast web browsing and effortless multi-tasking. Display Watch your favorite movies and videos in stunning visual clarity on the 11.93 cm (4.7) IPS display of this smartphone. Camera Heading for an unplanned road trip with friends to Gokarna and you don't have your camera with you? With the Micromax Unite 3 you will be able to capture all your special moments, thanks to its 8 MP Auto Focus primary camera. Take selfies with its 2 MP front camera and share it on Instagram and Facebook. Android Lollipop Experience the best of Android with the Lollipop 5.0 on the Micromax Unite 3. This Operating System offers several nifty features with intuitive notifications and enhanced performance. Connectivity Stream videos on Youtube, download music and upload pictures on Facebook with this phone's 3G connectivity. With USB connectivity transfer music from your laptop to this phone and share pictures with your friends via Bluetooth. Also, the phone has dual SIM slots for those who travel frequently. Storage You will always have your favorite music and important documents on you, thanks to the 32 GB expandable memory of the Micromax Unite 3. The phone has a 8 GB of internal memory that lets you download the latest apps and run them seamlessly. Smart Gestures Smart Awake allows for easy and fast access to all your favourite apps with the help of preset gestures. With the First Touch launcher in place, you can click photos, search your contacts and listen to your saved playlist directly from the home screen. Share Youtube links for the latest movie trailers by tapping the devices screen-to-screen, thanks to the Hotknot feature. Pre-Loaded Apps The Micromax Unite 3 comes pre-loaded with several Apps including Facebook and Facebook Messenger, Hotstar, MAD, Newshunt, PayTM, and Marbles, among others. Battery This Micromax smartphone has a 2000 mAh battery that offers a talktime of up to 8 hours. åÊ

title: Samsung Galaxy Note 3
description: Taking the mundane into the realms of the outstanding, Samsung presents the Galaxy Note 3, a revolution in technology set in the palm of the hand. Beauty meets utility in this device that brings big changes to the small workings of your life. Air Command The Note 3 comes with a palette of 5 useful features that you can use with the S Pen ‰ÛÒ hover over the screen and click the pen button to access Action Memo, Scrapbook, S Finder, Pen Window and Screen Write; every feature designed to make everyday actions simpler and easier to perform. Premium Design A phone designed to look every bit the performer that it is; the Note 3 sports a premium feel that is sure to garner more than just glances. But not at the cost of sturdiness - the phone is not delicate and does not get scratched easily either. Action Memo, Scrapbook, S Finder The Note 3 sports the Action Memo feature that lets you activate memos instantly. A simple search to ensure that you can locate any content on the phone, the S Finder on the Air Command lets you find specific content from anywhere on the phone, complete with filters and keyword support. The Scrapbook features lets you put together bits and pieces from the phone, including videos, images and other content into one comprehensive and organized file.åÊ Direct Pen Input Simplifying the way you use the phone, the Note 3 comes with the S Pen that you can use to write on the screen directly. With handwriting recognition on top of typing support, the phone transcribes everything you write into an action. If you need to add an alarm, all you need to do is write it on the screen of the Note 3 and the phone will set the alarm for you. Full HD Screen A quick peek just does not do justice to the 5.7 inch Super AMOLED screen to keep your eyes hooked, bringing visuals that are sharp, bright with astounding levels of clarity and upgrading everything you do to full HD resolution.

title: Honor 4X
description: With a Samsung/OV 5MP front camera, the Huawei Honor 4X captures candid moments with its 22mm wide angle lens. It also has a fully laminated black waterfall screen which ensures sharper, vivid images at a pixel resolution of 1280x720. 4G Connectivity Connect to 4G networks and enjoy strong and stable signals with a reduced chance of fallback to 3G. Experience 4G connectivity on two networks as the Honor 4X is capable of utilizing two 4G SIMs. Performance The Honor 4X is equipped with a 64-bit QuadCore CPU, an Adreno 306 GPU processor and a Qualcomm MSM 8916 processor which results in quicker responses, faster gameplay and quicker and stable connectivity to 4G networks. Camera Take a quick selfie while on vacation or video chat with your family abroad with this phone's Samsung/OV 5 MP front camera. Equipped with a 22mm wide angle lens, a sensor with 1.4 um pixel size and 4 pieces of lens, this camera offers a wide angle view of up to 88 degrees so you can include the entire family into a single frame. Display Watch shows, play games and browse the web on the Honor 4X's 14 cm HD, fully laminated IPS screen. The display produces up to 16.7 million colors, giving you brighter images that are easy on the eyes. It even uses an OTP calibration technique for a smooth viewing of HD movies and stable 3D gameplay. User Interface This phone uses EMUI 3.0, a user interface designed to create an enjoyable smartphone experience with simplicity as its overall theme. All messages, notifications and reminders are recorded on a timeline and you can access a search engine by pulling down the screen, no matter what screen you're at. Battery Get up to 72 hours of continued usage on your Honor 4X as it is powered by a 3000 mAh battery. Its energy efficient CPU is coupled with SmartPower 2.5, which increases the battery life by more than 30%. You can also get over seven days of battery life by switching the phone to ultra power saving mode. Sound Hear your favorite tracks in 5.1 channel surround sound as this smartphone comes with DTS audio processing and an integrated speaker. It has a dual silicon microphone design and uses noise reduction technology to ensure clarity in your phone calls, even in noisy places. Sensors This smartphone comes with a high-performance GPS receiving antenna and Glonass dual satellite geo-location for quick GPS searching. It has a high-precision 12-bit gravity sensor which helps with motion gaming and a light sensor which adjusts the screen's brightness according to the natural light in the environment for better viewing. Storage Store movies, videos and games on this phone's 8 GB internal memory, which can be expanded up to 32 GB using an microSD card. It also has 2 GB of RAM to multitask faster. Connectivity The Honor 4X connects to wireless internet networks and can be used as a Wi-Fi hotspot on demand. It also supports 3G networks for high-speed connectivity on-the-go and can connect to Bluetooth-enabled devices for peer-to-peer transfer.

title: Intex Aqua Life II
description: Aqua Life 2 1.2 GHz,Quad Core Processor with Android OS, 4.4.2 KitKat, Forget the need to compromise your viewing experience when you can indulge in full, life-like color display. Display Size 12.7 cm (5), Display Type FWVGA, Display Colors 16.7m, Display Resolution 480 x 854 pixels, An amazing camera that ensures you capture and carry all your moments with you. Camera ( Rear) 5 MP, Camera ( Front ) 1.3 MP Auto Focus No, Camera features Panorama Shot,face beauty, Motion Tracker, Flash Yes, Enjoy an extra energy boost with this lightweight battery that never keeps you waiting. Battery Type 2000 mAh.

title: Apple iPhone 5S
description: The iPhone 5S is a remarkable device from Apple. Featuring an all-new locking system, called Touch ID, and upgrades from the previous iPhone, the 5S has better hardware with the software and design to back it up. iSight Camera Point-and-click photographers will love the iSight 8MP camera which comes with True Tone flash. With larger sensors and a larger aperture, the camera captures clear, detailed photos. Still Photography Nifty features such as continuous burst mode, auto image stabilization, square photos, panorama and filters make this one of the world's best phone cameras. Video The iPhone 5S is also capable of capturing full HD videos. It can capture videos in slow motion and allows zooming in while recording a video. There's also a 1.2-megapixel secondary camera for FaceTime, with better illumination sensors and larger pixels to ensure you can also video chat in HD. iOS 7 With smarter multi-tasking abilities and side-swipe action, AirDrop for sharing content and a quick-access Control Centre to make frequent actions simpler, the iOS 7 makes the 5S easy to use, beautiful to look at and easy to work with. Apple's voice assistant, Siri, will help you even without having to touch the screen. Apple Apps This phone comes with pre-installed apps such as iPhoto, iMovie, GarageBand, Pages, Numbers and Keynote. With a plethora of apps on the App Store, the 5S is addictively capable of improving productivity and on-the-go entertainment. Connectivity With 13 LTE bands, 3G and WiFi support, the 5S ensures that you connect to the Net faster than ever. The device can also be connected to other iDevices via Bluetooth. For Mac and PC users, the 5S syncs up and transfers files through a USB connection, using iTunes. TouchID Doing away with tedious passcode and password locks, the 5S comes with Touch ID that scans your fingerprint through the identity sensor. The 5S can be unlocked by simply holding a finger on the Home button. The same authentication process can also work on iTunes and the App Store. You can also record multiple fingerprints for convenience. Performance With the A7 processor, this 64-bit smartphone packs enough performance power to run games and deliver rich, detailed visual effects. The M7 Co-Processor steps up the processing capability of this smartphone, aiding in managing the phone's power. Sensors With a proximity sensor, the phone's display automatically goes off in circumstances where you don't need it functioning, such as when making a call. An Ambient light sensor adjusts screen brightness. A three-axis gyro works with the accelerometer to make motion gaming an immersive experience. Signature Design The iPhone 5S retains the classic design of the previous Apple iPhone 5. Bridging the gap between usability and sophistication, the aluminium body is sturdy but surprisingly light. The round, sapphire crystal home button is a move forward from the previous square-shaped one. Retina Display A 10.16 cm (4) screen with a resolution of 1136 x 640 gives the 5S a crystal clear display. The 326 ppi display is also multi-touch capable.

title: Intex Aqua Power+
description: Carry this slim smartphone in your pocket to easily access Facebook, stream YouTube videos, pursue your passion for photography and more. Power in Slim Disguise Watch many episodes of Game of Thrones or listen to numerous Linkin Park albums at a stretch with this smartphone which has a pre-loaded super power app and a 4000 m Ah Li-ion battery. Slim Body The slender body of this smartphone allows you to slide it right into your pocket and carry it around with ease. Flaunt-worthy Display See movies in lifelike clarity on the HD IPS screen of this smartphone which comes with Full Lamination technology. Aced Global Standards Don't mistime a move when you're playing Mortal Kombat on this smartphone which has a 1.3-GHz quad-core processor and a 2 GB RAM. Pictures Speak to You You can capture mesmerizing pictures with the 13-MP rear camera of this phone with simple verbal commands. Clicking great selfies from a distance with the 5-MP front-facing camera is easy too. Selfies with Bluetooth Use the Bluetooth of this phone to take selfies from afar. Undercover At Its Best Use the smart-window flip cover of this phone to perform common functions. This cover protects the screen from dust and scratches. Playback & Recording You can record high-quality audio clips on this smartphone. You also record conversations for remembrance.
