title: Micromax Canvas Nitro A311
description: Powered by a 1.7 GHz Tru-Octacore processor, the Micromax Canvas Nitro runs all your applications and games smoothly while you view it on a clear 12.7 cm (5) HD IPS display. Performance Re-Invented This smartphone comes with a 1.7 GHz Tru-Octacore Mediatek 6592 processor and a Quad Core ARM Mali 450 GPU to run all your favorite applications smoothly. It also has 2GB of RAM which lets you multitask faster. Mesmerizing Display Watch your favorite movies and shows on this phone's 12.7 cm (5) HD IPS display from any angle up to 178 degrees, as it produces a pixel resolution of 1280 x 720 and has a pixel density of 294 pixels per inch. It also has an Oleophobic coating which prevents your screen from getting smudged by oily fingerprints. Stunning Camera Capture your special moments with the Canvas Nitro's 13 MP Auto Focus rear camera, as it comes with a Sony IMX134 CMOS sensor and Largan 5P Lens with a Schott Blue Glass filter for clearer photos. It also has a 5MP BSI fixed focus front camera with f/2.4 aperture, 22mm wide-angle lens for taking fun selfies on-the-go. Friendly User Interface Customize the way you view your social networking sites and weather updates on the Micromax Canvas Nitro as each type of notification can be color coded, allowing you to recognize missed calls, texts and Whatsapp messages quickly. Gesture Control With gesture control, you can quickly access apps with a simple flick of your finger. You can also access apps with your customized gesture such as flicking to the left or swiping to the right. Quick Look This feature lets you view social networking sites, the weather and new updates in one window for easy access. Smart Alerts Get all your notifications such as missed calls, Whatsapp messages and mail in a color coded strip on the phone's lock screen. This helps you identify the type of notification you receive so you can respond accordingly. Camera Widget The Micromax Canvas Nitro has a camera widget which lets you capture your favorite moments in an instant. It has a selfie mode for taking quick selfies, a stable mode for focused shooting, and a front and back mode for taking pictures with both cameras at the same time. Collage Feature With this feature, you can make beautiful collages of up to ten images from the gallery. You can also change the layout of the collage with a simple shake of the phone. Operating System This smartphone is powered by an Android KitKat 4.4.2 Operating System and comes with a number of convenient features such as a priority contact list, which lets you customize your contacts to your liking. You can also send texts and initiate searches by tapping the Google Bar and saying, 'Okay Google'. Storage With 16 GB of internal memory and up to 32 GB of external memory, you can store more movies, songs and photos on your Canvas Nitro. Connectivity Connect to wireless internet networks with the Canvas Nitro as it is Wi-Fi enabled. You can also share files, documents and songs with other devices using the phone's Bluetooth technology.

title: Asus Zenfone 5
description: Exquisitely crafted, the Asus Zenfone 5 is a commixture of intelligent technology and beautiful design. This slim and elegant phone features a 2x2 Intel Atom processor, HD Display, Corning Gorilla Glass 3, PixelMaster technology and the intelligent ZenUI. Uncompromising Mobile Experience Packing a 1.6 GHz Intel dual core processor, PowerVR GPU and 2 GB RAM, enjoy flawless performance and responsiveness on the Asus Zenfone 5. Multitask seamlessly, switch between apps without any lags, browse through heavy webpages effortlessly, and indulge in immersive 3D gaming on the Asus Zenfone 5. Grand Display Enjoy a splendid mobile experience on the stunning 5-inch IPS display with 1280 x 720p HD resolution and 294 ppi. Powered by Asus TruVivid technology, immerse yourself in impressive visual clarity, beautiful colors and quality pictures. The Corning Gorilla Glass 3 protects the Asus Zenfone 5 from scratches and accidental screen damages. Timeless Design The Asus Zenfone 5 flaunts a simple, ergonomic and innovative design which has undergone stringent quality testing. The design incorporates the iconic concentric circle finish with a unique fine texture which lends the phone a classic look and feel. Incredible Touch Experience Experience impressive touch responsiveness on the Asus Zenfone 5 with a quick response time of 60 ms. An anti-fingerprint coating is applied on the screen to reduce smudges. Also, the Asus Zenfone 5 has increased display sensitivity so you can use the phone even while wearing gloves. Superb Photos With PixelMaster Click excellent photos with the 8 MP rear camera infused with Asus's unique PixelMaster technology which combines five brightness-enhancing lenses to achieve perfect photos. With the various photo features that PixelMaster provides, you can be assured of clicking high quality images. Also, the phone comes with a 2 MP camera. Ultimate Sound Experience A combination of high quality hardware and software, Asus's SonicMaster technology is designed to deliver an exceptional sound experience. This unique audio optimization technology has been developed by the Asus Golden Ear Team. Dual SIM, Dual Standby Experience the power of two phones in one with the Asus Zenfone 5 which features dual SIM standby support. Separate your work account from your personal account without the hassle of carrying two different phones. Moreover, the Asus Zenfone 5 provides excellent signal reception, thanks to its advanced antenna design. Dual Carrier HSPA+ Stream HD videos or browse the web or work from anywhere with the Asus Zenfone 5 which supports network speeds up to 42 Mbps DC-HSPA+ and dual carrier. Battery Life The Asus Zenfone 5 packs a strong 2110 mAh battery that keeps it running for a long time. Moreover, the low-power Intel processor, power-efficient antenna design and the power saving mode admixture ensures that the battery lasts long without deterring the performance. Asus ZenUI Simple, intuitive, and extremely functional, the ZenUI is exclusively designed to function based on your needs. Features such as What's Next, Do It Later, Omlet Chat, PixelMaster, Zen Link, and Open Cloud provide smart options to prevent complications and ease out your life. Operating System The Asus Zenfone 5 comes with Android Jelly Bean 4.3 operating system installed in the device. The OS is upgradeable to Android KitKat v4.4 on this Asus device. Memory The Asus Zenfone 5 offers up to 16 GB of internal memory to store all your multimedia files and important documents. The memory of the device is expandable up to 64 GB via a micro SD card. Along with these memory options, Asus provides 5 GB free lifetime Asus web storage. Connectivity Enjoy endless around-the-clock connectivity with friends and family via 3G or Wi-Fi on your Asus Zenfone 5. Furthermore, the phone lets you transfer data to other devices via Bluetooth or USB connect.

title: Lenovo A6000 Plus
description: Designed for music and multimedia lovers, the Lenovo A6000 Plus is a budget smartphone with a 12.7 cm (5) HD display. It's powered by a quad-core Snapdragon processor which delivers a responsive system performance. Memory & Storage Along with excellent multi-tasking, the 2 GB RAM of this Lenovo device ensures that applications and games run lag-free. The 16 GB ROM easily accommodates all your favorite pictures, music, videos and games. Live Life in HD The Lenovo A6000 Plus comes with a 12.7 cm (5) HD display for viewing photos, browsing websites or playing games. This smartphone uses an IPS technology to deliver ultra-wide 178-degree viewing angles that are great for watching videos in large groups. Snapdragon Processor Powered by a 64-bit quad-core Qualcomm Snapdragon processor, the Lenovo A6000 Plus offers a solid performance at a reasonable price. It's 2300 m Ah battery ensures connectivity with your friends all-day. Twin Speakers Become the DJ at your friend's party with this phone's twin speakers and Dolby Digital Plus audio technology. It provides crisp audio so you can enjoy your music, games and videos. Pair this phone with some good earphones to enjoy the clarity of sound that Dolby provides. 4G LTE Get ultra-fast data transfer speeds on this phone as it supports 4G LTE networks for video streaming and online gaming. Camera This Lenovo smartphone comes with an 8 MP rear camera that clicks great pictures. The 2 MP fixed-focus front camera is good for video calls and selfies. Connectivity Enjoy the flexibility of two SIMs on one phone or choose a separate data plan to save on your phone bills. This is great for people where network coverage varies between telecom providers. Other connectivity features include 3G, Wi-Fi and Bluetooth. Android Operating System With Android KitKat 4.4, you can optimize memory and improve your touchscreen responsiveness so that it performs faster than before. This lets you listen to music while you browse a webpage with no interruptions or reduced performance. SHAREit with CLONEit This featureåÊallows for sharing of videos, photos and apps across devices without network charges or Wi-Fi. With CLONEit, you can instantly transfer all your old data to you new Lenovo phone. This phone also comes with SYNCit which provides a backup for all your contacts, logs and SMS messages.

title: Samsung Galaxy Ace NXT
description: Operating system android 4.4, form factor touch screen, CPU 1.2

title: Sony Xperia C4 Dual
description: Are you a selfie fan? If yes, then grab this exceptional Sony Xperia C4 Dual smartphone which has been designed to click the best PROselfies. Apart from an amazing front and rear camera, this Full HD smartphone offers maximum performance and speed. All You Need For PROselfies For all selfie lovers, the 5 MP front camera of this Sony device is equipped with a soft LED flash, 25 mm wide-angle lens and other features to click the best PROselfies. Exmor R sensor ensures sharp pictures with low noise. HDR balances bright background lights for clearer results. SteadyShot lets you shoot amazing selfie videos. Unique Soft LED Flash The unique soft LED flash automatically adjusts according to the lighting conditions, illuminates the scene and gives you the perfect shot. Whether there is a bright backlight or you are taking photos at night, the Superior Auto feature ensures that your selfies and group selfies are of professional quality. 25 mm Wide View Thanks to the 25 mm wide-angle lens with an 80-degree field of view, you can fit in more of your friends or more of the view in a single shot. Main Camera This Sony Xperia smartphone is equipped with a 13 MP primary shooter. Exmor RS For Mobile This image sensor technology assures sharp photos and videos with fine detailing, amazing picture clarity and rich colors, even while shooting in challenging light conditions. Superior Auto The Superior Auto feature recognizes up to 52 different scenarios such as illuminated night shots and close-up macros. This intelligent feature adjusts the settings according to the scene, so you get noteworthy photos always. HDR For Photo & Video HDR mode shoots the same image multiple times under different exposures and layers themåÊso that you get clear and bright photos and videos. This feature is extremely useful while capturing photos or videos in strong backlight or high-contrast situations. SteadyShot Thanks to SteadyShot, every video you shoot with this Xperia smartphone is smooth, steady and perfect. Sound Photo Relive you favorite moments with sound and visuals. Capture up to 10 seconds of audio with your photos using Sound Photo app and share it via PlayMemories Online. AR Mask Replace your own face or other people's faces with a different face using the AR Mask app. You can choose from the pre-loaded faces or create your own collection. Style Portrait This app lets you select from different styles to enhance your photos or add fun effects to them. These effects can be applied in real-time or after taking the photo or video. Download More Apps Apart from the pre-installed apps, you can download more camera apps directly from the camera interface of this Xperia smartphone. Display The large 13.97 cm (5.5) Full HD display and Mobile Bravia Engine 2 make the Xperia C4 an ideal device for watching movies and playing games. The IPS technology allows excellent viewing from all angles, so you and your friends can enjoy a movie on this device while chilling out in the college cafeteria. Sound Equipped with a speaker capable of up to 97 decibels and ClearAudio+ technologies for crystal clear audio, you can pump up your home get-togethers with loud music. This Xperia device delivers rich bass, thanks to the xLoud loudness enhancement engine. Design Despite the large screen size, the Xperia C4 is sleek, lightweight and easily slides into your jeans pocket or wallet. The device is 7.9 mm thin and weighs just 147 grams. Processor Play games lag-free, run multiple apps simultaneously, surf the web seamlessly and stream HD videos without glitches. The competent 1.7 GHz Octa Core processor and 2 GB RAM offers maximum performance in everything you do on your Xperia smartphone. The phone also comes with a built-in LTE/4G modem for extremely fast internet connectivity. Battery An incredibly powerful yet efficient 2600 mAh battery powers this Xperia phone. To further extend the already long battery life, this device offers four power management modes - Battery STAMINA mode, Extended standby mode, Extended usage mode and Ultra STAMINA mode.

title: Apple iPhone 6
description: The bigger the better - the Apple iPhone 6 is an example of this phrase. The meticulously crafted iPhone 6 is truly an epitome of great taste and elegance. Beautiful Unibody Design Extremely thin, the iPhone 6 flaunts a seamless design with the smooth blend of anodised aluminium, stainless steel and the curved, polished glass. Incredibly light, the beautifully crafted iPhone 6 feels great in your hands. Thanks to its innovative design, the iPhone 6 provides an intuitive experience and is extremely easy to use. Brilliant Display Featuring the thinnest and most advanced Multi-Touch display ever made, the Apple iPhone 6 promises a high-contrast output with incredible colors and brightness on its 4.7 inch Retina HD display. A resolution of 1334x750 pixels, clear wide-angle viewing and an improved polariser - the iPhone 6 truly offers a bigger and better display. Power-Packed Performance Thanks to the all-new A8 processor with 64-bit architecture and an advanced 20-nanometre process, the iPhone 6 delivers an incredibly powerful performance while being extremely efficient. Get up to 50x faster CPU performance and up to 84x faster GPU performance with the iPhone 6. M8 Motion Coprocessor & Sensors Improve your iPhone's power efficiency with the M8 Motion Coprocessor that continuously measures data from your iPhone's different sensors such as an accelerometer, compass, gyroscope and the new barometer. Camera Photos or videos - there is nothing that can beat the iPhone 6's iSight camera. The iPhone 6's 8 MP iSight camera gets new features such as a new sensor with Focus Pixels, improved face detection and exposure control. Also, now you can take amazing 1080p HD videos with the world's most popular camera. Security Make life easier with the iPhone 6's breakthrough Touch ID technology. Now you can securely access your phone with your fingerprint - no more worries about forgetting your pass code ever again. Moreover, the iPhone 6 lets you use your fingerprint to securely make purchases on iTunes or the App Store. Operating System The iPhone 6 comes with the biggest iOS release ever - the iOS 8. Featuring new capabilities and features, the world's advanced mobile operating system - the iOS 8 - gives you an incredible experience on your iPhone 6. Connectivity Thanks to the advanced Wi-Fi support with fast wireless performance, you can keep up with the world around you easily. Moreover, the iPhone 6 comes with Bluetooth and 3G support. title: Sony Xperia T2 Ultra Dual
description: Featuring a smart camera and brilliant screen, the Sony Xperia T2 Ultra is a sleek 6-inch dual SIM smartphone designed for great fun and entertainment on the go. Superior Brightness The 15.24 cms wide screen of the Xperia T2 Ultra is enriched with Sony's Triluminos‰ã¢ Display for mobile and comes with a 720p HD resolution. The screen displays superior brightness with rich colors and crystal clear images. Triluminos‰ã¢ Display Enriched with the Triluminos‰ã¢ display technology for mobiles, the Xperia T2 Ultra delivers a wide palette of natural and rich colors. Seascapes and landscapes appear more vivid and faces come in natural skin tones. Get ready for a rich and vivid color experience on the Sony Xperia T2 Ultra Dual SIM smartphone. Design The Xperia T2 Ultra comes with a screen to phone size ratio of approximately 73.7%, making it extremely light, sleek, and easily portable. For easy operation with one hand, the T2 Ultra offers an easy-toggle keyboard, centralised keypad and an easy-trigger notification tray. 13 MP Camera The Xperia device sports a 13-megapixel camera featuring the Exmos RS‰ã¢ for mobile image sensor and HDR mode. Click or record exceptional photos and videos on the Xperia T2 Ultra Dual SIM smartphone. Superior Auto. Superior Photos. With the Superior Auto feature as the default camera mode, the Xperia T2 Ultra clicks exceptional photos always. The Superior Auto can detect up to 26 scene types and adjusts the settings based on the requirements of the current scene. Also, it turns the HDR mode on or off depending on the scene being shot. HDR For Photos And Video - The HDR technology shoots the same image under varied exposures and merges them together to create the perfect picture. It is an extremely useful tool for strongly backlit scenes like when the subject is standing in front of a window or the setting sun. On the Xperia T2 Ultra, you can enjoy HDR for videos too. Exmor RS‰ã¢ For Mobile - The revolutionary Exmor RS‰ã¢ for mobile with a next generation BSI light sensor helps the Xperia T2 Ultra to shoot detailed photos with low noise under any lighting condition. You can click stunning pictures with rich reproduction of colors and details with this Xperia device. Camera Apps Make more of your pictures with Sony's camera apps. The Xperia T2 Ultra smartphone comes with a wide range of preloaded camera apps that help you make your pictures perfect. For more camera apps, you can click on the +Apps on your T2's camera viewfinder and download other available apps. Performance Featuring a 1.4 GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon quad core processor and 1 GB RAM, the Xperia T2 Ultra Dual SIM gives you lightning speed performance, improved multitasking capabilities, good battery life, and amazing graphics. Moreover, this Xperia smartphone supports LTE/4G. Battery - STAMINA Mode Battery STAMINA Mode lets you save power, especially when you are not using your phone. No more battery drain issues - the Battery STAMINA Mode automatically turns off unnecessary functions when you are not using your phone. When your phone is on standby, Wi-Fi and data are disabled by the Battery Stamina Mode. One-Touch Connectivity An active player in the consumer electronics sector, Sony has a diverse NFC enabled product portfolio. All these devices work together flawlessly and all they need is one touch to get connected to each other. Watch your smartphone photos and videos on your big screen TV or listen to music through wireless speakers. One-Touch Connection Enjoy hands free calling while driving. With just one touch, connect your smartphone to your NFC-enabled car accessories and take complete control over your car's audio functions. One-Touch Listening Play your smartphone's music through a NFC-enabled wireless Sony headset or speaker using just one touch. More Ways To Connect Your Xperia smartphone comes with a Throw smart application. You can Throw content to your Wi-Fi enabled TV using DLNA or screen mirroring, or send your phone's music content to a speaker through Bluetooth. Also, the phone offers connectivity through Bluetooth, Wi-Fi and Micro-USB, or Miracast Wireless Technology. Memory The device comes with a flash memory up to 8 GB*. Also, it features an external MicroSD slot which supports up to 32 GB (SDXC supported). * Memory comprises approximately 3.2 GB of firmware, plus 4.8 GB of internal storage for music, pictures and films, downloaded applications and their data. Sensors The Xperia T2 Ultra Dual SIM comes with an Ambient Light Sensor, Accelerometer, eCompass, Proximity Sensor, Magnetometer, and Gyroscope.

It recognizes up to 36 different scene types and automatically adjusts the camera settings to match the scene requirements. Moreover, the Auto scene recognition turns HDR on and off depending upon the scene. HDR For Photos And Video The High Dynamic Range imaging technology lets you click clear and detailed pictures and videos, even in strong backlight situations such as the subject standing in front of a setting sun. HDR takes multiple shots of the same image under different exposures and then merges them together to create the perfect click. Stunning Shots In Any Light For pictures with rich details and low noise, the Xperia M2 has adopted the Exmor RS‰ã¢ for mobile image sensor technology. On standby, the Battery Stamina mode disables Wi-Fi and data connections. However, you can still receive calls, alarms and messages. One-Touch Connectivity With NFC connectivity, it just takes one touch to connect all NFC-enabled devices to each other. You can easily connect your NFC-enabled smartphone to your NFC-enabled TV or NFC-enabled speakers with just a touch. One-Touch Connection Enjoy hands-free calling while driving. With just one touch, connect your smartphone to your NFC-enabled car accessories and take complete control over your car's audio functions. One-Touch Listening Play your smartphone's music through an NFC-enabled wireless Sony headset or speaker using just one touch. One-Touch Mirroring Activate screen mirroring by touching your smartphone to the remote of your BRAVIAå¨ TV and mirror your smartphone contents on the TV. One-Touch Sharing With a single touch, you can share music or photos between two devices or an NFC-enabled laptop. One-Touch Backup Store all the pictures from your Xperia smartphone, tablet or camera on the Sony Personal Content Station‰ã¢ - a wireless hub for all your photos and videos. For more connectivity, this Xperia smartphones is enabled with Wi-Fi support.

title: Sony Xperia C
description: Enthralling and gape-worthy, the Xperia C from Sony is a smartphone made for amazing entertainment. Capturing Clarity The Xperia C comes with an 8 megapixel camera that incorporates the Exmor R technology that stems from Sony‰Ûªs time-proven record with professional cameras. Helping you take amazing pictures even in low-light conditions, the camera employs HDR, aided by a pulsed LED, that captures at different exposure levels and layers them, ensuring that the subject looks crisp and bright. What‰Ûªs more, the phone is also capable of capturing full HD videos as well. A scaling mechanism which is intuitive about what you are searching for allows you to find specific pictures with ease. Also, the phone body comes with a dedicated camera button that lets you access it in a jiffy. Connectivity Simplified The Xperia C can also be connected with your large screen TV to watch mind-blowing content like it should be. All you need is Wi-Fi connectivity on the TV and you can throw content onto it using Bluetooth on your phone - the best way to connect to other devices without the hassle of wires. Processing with Power A 1.2 GHz MTK6589 Quad Core processor backed by 1 GB RAM gives you performance and speed that you could easily get used to. Lag is a thing of the past as you blaze through apps, the web, streaming live videos and multitasking is but a piece of cake that will not frustrate you with slow responses. Aided and abetted by the Android v4.2.2 (Jelly Bean) operating system that is both intuitive and smooth while being simple and easy to use as well, the phone packs quite a punch. 4 GB of internal storage can be extended upto 32 GB and the phone packs a 2330 mAh battery as well. A feature that comes in very handy to those who don‰Ûªt get the time to charge their phone batteries all that often, the Battery STAMINA mode that comes with the dual GSM SIM Sony Xperia C ensures that unnecessary battery drainage is curbed by cutting off display when not in use and disabling Wi-Fi and data traffic while still allowing notifications to show up on the screen, significantly improving battery life. You can also customize what kind of notifications you want to show up. A smartphone that will definitely catch the eye, the Sony Xperia C will ensure that daily tasks are made simpler.

You can expand the storage space by up to 32GB as it also supports microSD cards. Performance This XOLO smartphone is powered by a 1.5 Ghz Qualcomm Snapdragon 615 Octa-Core 64-bit processor and an LPDDR3 2 GB RAM. Apps run smoothly, games are hiccup-free and multi-tasking is seamless on this smartphone. Battery The 3200 mAh Li-Ion battery provides enough fuel for life on the move as it is optimized to consume less power. The Quick Charge 1.0 technology reduces this XOLO device's charging time to 2.5 hours. HIVE Atlas Built on Android Lollipop, the HIVE Atlas UI is easy to use and is loaded with new features. Comet browser enables 20% faster browsing and uses lesser data than other browsers. Keep your private data safe by locking private apps in the Underground feature and retrieve them with a password. The reading mode turns your display black and white for a better reading experience. Audio Love listening to music or watching videos on your smartphone? The XOLO BLACK optimises the audio for your headset, thereby delivering an enhanced audio experience. Storage Carry your favourite songs and videos with you wherever you go, thanks to the 16 GB internal storage capacity which can be expanded up to 32 GB. Connectivity Whether you are a social media addict or often transfer songs from your laptop to your phone, this XOLO device is up to the task as it comes with 4G LTE, Wi-Fi and Bluetooth. The Hybrid Dual SIM capability lets you choose the device as dual SIM or single SIM with microSD. Sensors The XOLO BLACK comes with an accelerometer, a magnetometer, an ambient light sensor, a gyroscope, a hall effect sensor and a proximity sensor.

title: BlackBerry Z3
description: Meet the latest addition to the BlackBerry smartphone range - the BlackBerry Z3. This smartphone brings the best of BlackBerry in a pocket-friendly and Android compatible avatar. Display Experience BlackBerry 10 on the large 12.7 cm (5)åÊdisplay which comes with 16:9 aspect ratio and 540 x 960 qHD resolution. The highly responsive LCD screen of the Z3 uses a GFF/CoverGlass touch panel display. Processor The BlackBerry Z3 packs a 1.2 GHz dual-core processor and 1.5 GB of RAM. So, here is a Blackberry device that processes tasks efficiently and is capable of speedy multitasking, thus delivering a complete smartphone experience. Battery Life Packing a 2500 m Ah battery, your BlackBerry Z3 has the power to stay with you throughout the day. The device is capable of up to 15.5 hours of 3G talk time and up to 10 hours of video playback. Also, it boasts of a 3G standby time of up to 16.2 days. However, the battery of the Z3 is non-removable. Camera The BlackBerry Z3 boasts a 5 MP rear-facing camera with 5x digital zoom and a 1.1 MP front-facing camera. Both the cameras are capable of recording HD videos, 1080 p for the rear camera and 720p for the front camera. BlackBerry Hub & Smart Sharing The Z3 lets you peek into the BlackBerry hub from any application and prioritize everything that matters to you with just a pinch. Also, the Z3 features the faster and more intuitive smart sharing option. With smart sharing, you can get suggestions on whom and how to share your pictures, documents, or files with just a single touch. Hinglish Flick Typing English or Hinglish - experience the new and fast BlackBerry flick typing on the Z3. So whether it is an email, a message, or a BBM, flick typing lets you type faster and more accurately by suggesting appropriate words. Operating System The BlackBerry Z3 runs on the BlackBerry 10.2.1 operating system. This new BlackBerry OS has opened the doors to Android apps. Along with this substantial addition, the new OS lets you experience faster browsing and an optimized battery life. Connectivity Your BlackBerry Z3 loves to get connected with the world around. Share files and multimedia with your loved ones via Bluetooth or just stay connected with the world through Wi-Fi or 3G connectivity. Memory With 8 GB of internal memory and a hot swappable micro SD card slot, the BlackBerry Z3 offers ample storage space for storing all your files and multimedia. Sensors Thanks to the accelerometer, proximity sensor, and the ambient light sensor, your Z3 connects better with you and the real world. The accelerometer detects the orientation of your Z3 on three axes. The proximity sensor recognizes how close your phone is to you while the ambient light sensor helps to adjust the phone's brightness by checking the intensity of light outside.

title: Asus Zenfone 2 ZE551ML
description: Beautifully crafted, the Asus Zenfone 2 ZE551ML delivers a truly remarkable performance and gets you through the day without fail. This dual SIM smartphone runs on Android Lollipop and offers up to 16 GB internal storage. Beautifully Crafted Indeed a marvel of design and ergonomics, this Asus smartphone is crafted with ultra-thin edges and flaunts the iconic Asus concentric circle design. The 3.9 mm thin edges make it comfortable to hold this device with one hand. Ergonomic Arc Design Besides making it extremely comfortable to hold this device, the ergonomic arc design with the intuitive rear controls make it easy to adjust the volume, snap selfies or retrace your steps. Display Enjoy crystal-clear picture clarity on the razor-sharp 13.97 cm (5.5) IPS display of the Asus Zenfone 2. It comes with a resolution of 1920 x 1080 Full HD and offers 178-degree viewing angles. In addition, Asus TruVivid technology ensures that colors appear natural and lifelike. Performance Apps open quickly, games run smoothly and web browsing is effortless on this Asus phone. Thanks to the 1.8 GHz 64-bit Intel Atom Super quadcore processor which enhances everyday performance up to three times better and gaming performance up to seven times faster. The 2 GB RAM adds to the flawless performance. Graphics Performance Whether you are watching an HD flick or playing Mortal Kombat X, get a smooth and immersive experience with the PowerVR-G6430 GPU built into this Asus handset. Touch Experience With a quick response time of 60 ms, experience impressive touch responsiveness on this Asus smartphone. A crystal-clear anti-fingerprint coating is applied on the screen to reduce scratches and smudges. Sound Experience Developed by the Asus Golden Ear Team, the SonicMaster technology has been designed to deliver rich and detailed audio whether you are on speakers or headphones. Amazing Camera Click amazing pictures with the 13 MP primary shooter. The 5 MP front camera comes with an 85-degree wide-angle lens that lets you take exceptional selfies or enjoy clear video calls. Super HDR Mode The Super HDR Mode helps to improve the light balance so that the pictures you click are similar to what your eyes see. Low Light Mode With 4x increased light sensitivity, reduced noise, and 4x enhanced color contrast, the Low Light Mode lets you capture clear and sharp images in low light conditions. Dual-LED Real Tone Flash Ideal for indoor shots, the dual-LED real tone flash creates natural illumination and captures the real tones of subjects in every photo. Zero Shutter Lag Capture moments in real time, even the fast fleeting ones, with the zero shutter lag capability of this Asus PixelMaster camera. Selfie Panorama This amazing Asus phone gives you the ability to take 140-degree panoramic selfies, so you can capture your entire gang of friends and even the background. Zen UI Experience The new interface design delivers a smart and intuitive user experience. Also, the Zen UI lets you customize your Asus phone the way you want. This UI comes with a variety of new features such as ZenMotion, SnapView, Trend Micro Security and ZenUI Instant Updates. Battery For long lasting usage, this Asus device packs a powerful 3000 mAh battery that keeps it alive through the day. In addition, it comes with the Asus BoostMaster Technology which charges the battery at double the normal speed. With 39 minutes of charging, your battery gets fueled up to 60%. Connectivity This phone has WiFi, Bluetooth, and NFC connectivity options.

title: Honor 4C
description: The Honor 4C is a premium smartphone that comes with an innovative design, 64-bit octa-core CPU and 13MP primary camera. With a 12.7 cm (5) 720p black waterfall fully laminated IPS screen, the Honor 4C is perfect for watching videos or playing games. Design Crafted to perfection, the Honor 4C employs a unique ID design that gives a silky smooth touch in your hand. The rear camera goes through the CNC diamond cutter million process to give the Honor 4C an elegant look. Performance With 8 cores functioning at the same time, the Honor 4C can handle multiple applications simultaneously for different scenarios, such as lower consumption or high performance. It also comes with a quad-core Mali-450 image processor which improves GPU performance, ensuring that your images and videos are crisp and clear. Strong Signal Reception This phone has a higher signal reception by 3dB when compared to other phones in its range. This results in clear conversations even when the signal is weak, such as underground garages or other marginal coverage areas. Camera Take fun selfies on this phone as it comes with a Samsung/OV 5MP front-facing camera. You can also capture memorable moments on this phone uses a BSI 13MP primary camera. It has a macro mode at the centimeter level for close up shots and a 27 mm wide angle lens for landscape shots. Display The Honor 4C comes with a fully laminated black waterfall screen which displays a resolution of 1280 x 720 pixels. The screens uses a combination of 16.7 million colors to give you sharper picture quality. User Interface This phone comes with EMUI 3.0, a unique interface designed to simplify your smartphone needs. All your messages and notifications are recorded on a timeline and you can trigger a search engine that covers your contacts, applications, and other content by pulling down the screen. Audio This phone comes with DTS audio processing and 5.1 channel surround sound effect for an immersive audio experience. It also has a dual silicon microphone design and uses noise reduction technology to give you clarity while you listen to music or attend a call, even in noisy areas. Battery The Honor 4C's CPU and other hardware components are coupled with SmartPower 2.5, a technology that increases this phone's 2550 mAh battery life by more than 30%. You can expect up to 80 hours of light usage and up to 50 hours of moderate usage with this phone.

title: Lenovo A536
description: Enjoy a seamless and stutter-free performance on this budget-friendly Lenovo A536 smartphone that runs on Android KitKat and a quad-core processor. Display Immerse yourself in rich visual clarity on the 12.7 cm (5) TFT capacitive display of this device. The twisted nematic LCD display gives a new dimension to browsing the Web, watching movies, or playing games. Operating System This smartphone runs on Android KitKat 4.4 operating system which optimizes memory and enhances touch screen experience so you can perform tasks in a fast and responsive way. Performance With a quad-core 1.3 GHz + MT6582M processor and 1 GB RAM, you can experience smooth performance and seamless multitasking. Camera Capture stunning photos and record videos with the 5 MP rear camera. In addition, it also comes with a 2 MP front camera that lets you capture selfies. Fast Connectivity Access social networking sites, listen to music, or stream videos quickly as this device supports HSPA+ connectivity and 21 Mbps download speed. You can also enjoy Wi-Fi and Bluetooth connectivity on this smartphone. Dual SIM Thanks to the dual-SIM configuration, this device frees you of the burden of carrying two phones. Lenovo Premium Apps Use the SHAREit app to transfer files wirelessly without using Wi-Fi or incurring any network charges. The Security app protects your phone from viruses and boosts its performance. Use the SYNCit app to backup or restore call logs, messages and contacts, which ensures you won't lose any personal data. Offline GPS You can easily find your way around a new town using the satellite controlled GPS which functions even without an internet connection. Storage The 8 GB internal storage capacity, expandable up to 32 GB, allows you to store all your favorite music, photos and apps without running out of space. Battery This device is powered by a 2000 m Ah Li-Polymer battery.

title: Lenovo A6000 Plus
description: Designed for music and multimedia lovers, the Lenovo A6000 Plus is a budget smartphone with a 12.7 cm (5) HD display. It's powered by a quad-core Snapdragon processor which delivers a responsive system performance. Memory & Storage Along with excellent multi-tasking, the 2 GB RAM of this Lenovo device ensures that applications and games run lag-free. The 16 GB ROM easily accommodates all your favorite pictures, music, videos and games. Live Life in HD Powered by a 64-bit quad-core Qualcomm Snapdragon processor, the Lenovo A6000 Plus offers a solid performance at a reasonable price. It's 2300 m Ah battery ensures connectivity with your friends all-day. Twin Speakers Become the DJ at your friend's party with this phone's twin speakers and Dolby Digital Plus audio technology. It provides crisp audio so you can enjoy your music, games and videos. Pair this phone with some good earphones to enjoy the clarity of sound that Dolby provides. 4G LTE Get ultra-fast data transfer speeds on this phone as it supports 4G LTE networks for video streaming and online gaming. Camera This Lenovo smartphone comes with an 8 MP rear camera that clicks great pictures. The 2 MP fixed-focus front camera is good for video calls and selfies. Connectivity Enjoy the flexibility of two SIMs on one phone or choose a separate data plan to save on your phone bills. This is great for people where network coverage varies between telecom providers. Other connectivity features include 3G, Wi-Fi and Bluetooth. Android Operating System With Android KitKat 4.4, you can optimize memory and improve your touch screen responsiveness so that it performs faster than before. This lets you listen to music while you browse a web page with no interruptions or reduced performance. SHAREit with CLONEit This featureåÊallows for sharing of videos, photos and apps across devices without network charges or Wi-Fi. With CLONEit, you can instantly transfer all your old data to you new Lenovo phone. This phone also comes with SYNCit which provides a backup for all your contacts, logs and SMS messages.

title: Apple iPhone 4S
description: Get ready to be impressed with the bold and impressive features of this Apple iPhone 4S. With a compact 8.89 cm (3.5) screen and a powerful A5 Chip this mobile phone ensures lightning speed and seamless performance at all times. Design & Display This stylish and elegant iPhone 4S feels great in your hands and is easy to use. The 8.89 cm (3.5) screen of this smartphone displays crisp and high-quality images which give a new dimension to the way you view photos, watch videos, and play games. It comes with an oleophobic coating on the front and back to resist fingerprints. Camera This phone has an 8 MP primary camera which comes with autofocus, tap to focus, face detection, panorama, geo-tagging, backside illumination sensor, and more so you can click amazing photos wherever you go. With the 0.3 MP front camera, you can video chat with friends and family even when you are miles away from them. Performance This iPhone 4S runs on A5 Chip to deliver a powerful performance. It operates on iOS 8 which offers new capabilities and features for an incredible experience. Storage This smartphone from Apple offers a storage space of 8 GB so you can store apps, photos, songs, and more. Connectivity This iPhone 4S is Wi-Fi enabled and supports 3G connectivity so you can browse the Web or download a file from the e-mail wherever you are. This phone also supports Bluetooth. Battery The built-in, rechargeable lithium-ion battery offers up to 8 hours talktime on 3G network and a standby time of up to 200 hours on 2G network.

title: Samsung Galaxy S3 Neo
description: An impressive budget-friendly smartphone for the masses, the Samsung Galaxy S3 Neo is a dual SIM offering that looks good, performs incredibly and is equipped with a variety of smart features. Display Whether you are watching Full HD videos or reading online content, the 12.19 cm (4.8) high definition display of the S3 Neo captivates you with its true-to-life color reproduction. Designed for pure visual enjoyment, the Super AMOLED display of this smartphone gives you wide viewing angles, better sunlight legibility and a smooth touch response. Performance The Samsung S3 Neo is equipped with a 1.2 GHz quad-core processor and 1.5 GB of RAM. Seamlessly open multiple apps at the same time and run demanding applications smoothly, thanks to the strong processor and the large RAM capacity of this Samsung handset. Operating System This Samsung handset comes with the user-friendly Android KitKat operating system. Enjoy a smoother, faster and enhanced experience with Android KitKat on the S3 Neo. Design The Samsung Galaxy S3 Neo has been ergonomically designed with gentle curves and a comfortable grip. Inspired by nature, this Samsung smartphone features non-linear lines and a smooth body that gives it a natural feel. Camera Satisfy all your photo and video related needs with the 8 MP rear camera and the 1.9 MP front camera of the S3 Neo. Capture your life's precious moments with the 8 MP shooter. Take beautiful selfies or video chat with loved ones using the front-facing camera. Pop Up Play Pop Up Play makes it possible for you to perform tasks simultaneously on the S3 Neo. Watch an HD video in one window, while sending an e-mail or chatting with your friend at the same time. Smart Stay Designed for your viewing pleasure, Samsung's Smart Stay feature detects when you are looking at your phone screen with the help of the front camera. This helps to maintain the display brightness for a comfortable reading experience. S Voice Take control over your Samsung Galaxy S3 Neo with S Voice. Tell your phone to wake up, answer or reject a call, adjust the volume, and even snooze the alarm. Social Tag Get quicker updates of your friends and family with the Social Tag feature. Social Tag lets you link faces in your album to their social media profiles, so you can see their current status while looking at their pictures. Storage Use a micro SD card to boost your S3 Neo's storage abilities up to 64 GB, so you can store all your music, videos and photos easily. AllShare Play Share content across devices easily with AllShare Play. This handy feature lets you remotely access content from connected devices. Buddy Photo Share Share photos easily with Buddy Photo Share. Your Galaxy S3 Neo recognizes your friends' faces and lets you share with them instantly. Connectivity Get all the necessary connectivity options on this Samsung Galaxy smartphone. It comes with Wi-Fi, Wi-Fi Direct, Bluetooth and a USB 2.0 port. Battery Get up to 14 hours of 2G talk time with the powerful 2100 mAh removable battery which ensures that your S3 Neo is available when you really need it. Sensors To connect better with the world and enhance your user experience, your Samsung handset comes with an accelerometer, a geo-magnetic sensor, a gyro sensor, a light sensor, a proximity sensor, an RGB sensor, and a hall sensor.

title: Apple iPhone 5C
description: A premium creation in the world of smartphones, Apple presents the much-awaited iPhone 5C that blends the superfine design that Apple is famous for with peppy colors and functional, versatile technology that surpasses their previous offerings. iOS 7 Operating System Beautifully redesigned to include a host of features that makes the 4-inch screen iPhone several shades easier and simpler to use, the iOS 7 is fluid and fits perfectly on the retina display screen. A new Control Centre that pops out from underneath lets you access what you use the most in a jiffy. And the notification centre ensures that all everything you need to know is bundled into one convenient place. iSight Camera With an 8 megapixel primary camera and LED flash, pamper the budding photographer in you. The phone makes available several live filters and the option to take photos in square and panorama formats as well. Record videos of your little one‰Ûªs stunts on the bike in HD and watch it on a large screen or FaceTime with your best friend via the 1.2 megapixel secondary camera that comes with backside illumination sensor that increases the quality of pictures in low light conditions. A6-Chip Processor Apple‰Ûªs very own A6 processor ensures that there is extremely fast processing of apps with great power management ensuring that you perform all tasks that you usually do without draining out your battery too quickly. Play Infinity Blade on high graphics without a single hitch of lag ‰ÛÒ that is what the chip is capable of. Apple Apps Extremely useful apps from Apple like iPhoto, iMovie and GarageBand along with Pages, Number and Keynote apart from iBooks and Podcasts are available on the iPhone 5C for free to ensure that you get maximum productivity ‰ÛÒ you won‰Ûªt be able to keep your hands off the phone with so much to do. Connectivity and Storage With 13 LTE bands which is the most number for any smartphone and AirDrop to share data and media with just a touch and a swipe, the iPhone 5C provides useful connectivity features that look, feel and work great. Browsing the internet is superfast, downloads are even faster with the 5C. The smartphone also comes with 16 GB of internal storage for all your apps and media without slowing the phone down or causing unnecessary crashes.

title: Samsung Galaxy S5
description: The Samsung Galaxy S5 lets you browse the web, play games and edit documents with ease, thanks to an Octa-core processor and 2 GB RAM. Display Watch videos in life-like picture quality with the S5's 12.7cm (5) Full HD Super AMOLED Display. It has an adaptive display that analyses incoming lights and adjusts the screen brightness accordingly. You can now see the screen clearly in sunlight as the screen reflects less light. Camera Samsung Galaxy S5's 16 MP primary camera has various modes such as Virtual Tour shot and Video Stabilisation that make your shots look good and shake-free in real time. This phone has a 2 MP camera for selfies as well. HDR (High Dynamic Range) Capture rich, vivid photos and videos with the Galaxy S5 as it comes with an HDR feature that ensures vibrant colours and a brilliant contrast. Stay Powered Up Don't worry about low battery as the Galaxy S5‰Ûªs Ultra Power Saving Mode minimises battery use by shutting down unnecessary features. OS This phone is powered by an Android v4.4.2 (KitKat) OS which supports a plethora of apps including SHealth, PayPal and YouTube. Performance The S5 uses an Adonis Prime2 Octa-core processor and 2 GB RAM for seamless multitasking. You can have multiple applications running simultaneously without any hindrance in performance. Storage With an inbuilt memory of 16 GB, this phone lets you store your favourite videos, music and games. It has a micro SD slot which lets you expand the memory by up to 128 GB. Dust & Water Resistant Carry your phone with confidence in any weather condition as its premium design ensures that no dust or water particle affects the phone's functionality. Connectivity Enjoy hassle-free browsing sessions with two internal Wi-Fi antennas that deliver fast Wi-Fi speeds. It supports 3G (HSPA 42 Mbps) networks and lets you stream music, photos or videos on the go. With the S5's Bluetooth feature, you can transfer files, music and other data instantly. Kids Mode The Galaxy S5‰Ûªs Kids Mode feature ensures that only child-friendly apps and videos can be accessed. Sensors This phone comes with inbuilt sensors such as a Gyro Sensor, Accelerometer, Proximity Sensor, Barometer, Hall Sensor, Finger Print Sensor, Compass, Gesture Sensor, RGB Ambient Light Sensor and Heart Rate Sensor.

title: Samsung Galaxy Star Pro
description: Another addition to Samsung‰Ûªs long and revered lineage of smartphones for every kind of budget, the Star Pro is here to give you a full smartphone experience, complete with top-notch performance and powerful presence. Superior PerformanceåÊ A 4 inch TFT screen that is wide enough for you to see every last detail with clarity is what the S7262 has on offer. A one GHz Cortex-A5 processor with 512 MB RAM ensures that you can switch between apps and browse through the phone without any lag or hang. Also, with the Android 4.1 (Jelly Bean) operating system, the phone is intuitive to your needs and extremely simple to operate apart from being smooth and seamless as well. Smart Experience With access to both Google Play and Samsung Apps, the phone grants you unlimited access to any kind of app you need. To top it all, the Intelligent User Interface gives you shortcuts for the regular actions that you perform, making life that much easier. Dual SIM Experience With support for two GSM microSIM cards, the phone ensures that you get the best of two network plans and also enables you to keep the business away from the personal as well. With the Always On feature, calls get transferred to SIM 2 when the first one is in use to ensure that you never miss a call. Also call functions available on both SIMs ensure that can manage simultaneous calls at the same time on the same phone.

title: LG G4
description: Listen to your favorite band and refresh your mood whenever you feel low on this LG G4 smartphone. Display The 13.97 cm (5.5) IPS quantum display makes browsing the Web, chatting with friends on WhatsApp, or watching movie trailers a treat for the eyes. The quad HD display with a resolution of 2560 x 1440 pixels ensures sharp and detailed image quality. Camera With this phone's 16 MP rear camera and 8 MP front camera, you can capture amazing photos wherever you go. Take fun photos with friends and family using the dual cameras. You can also capture photos in insufficient lighting as the rear camera comes with a flash. Performance & Operating System You can play action-packed games like Mortal Kombat X or Asphalt 8 on this smartphone as it runs on Qualcomm Snapdragon 808 processor. Thanks to the 3 GB RAM, you can multitask easily and quickly between applications without the lag. This mobile runs on Android Lollipop v5.1. Storage This smartphone offers an internal storage space of up to 32 GB. You can expand the memory by up to 2 TB via a microSD card. Store photos, songs, videos, movies and more on your smartphone without worrying about running out of space. Connectivity Book a flight ticket or order food while you are at your office or on-the-go as this mobile phone supports Wi-Fi, 3G and 4G connectivity. It also has two SIM slots which support GSM and LTE networks. Battery This phone comes with a 3000 m Ah removable battery.

title: Nokia Lumia 520
description: A Lumia that fits right into your pocket without letting go of all that is innately identifiable about Nokia, the 520 is a compact powerhouse that lies within a colourful and sturdy body. Digital Lenses The Lumia 520 comes with a 5 megapixel camera with built-in digital lenses that you can click perfect pictures with. Also, apps like Cinemagraph to add motion to images, Smart Shoot to take multiple photos and such add to the efforts that go into creating picture perfect photos.åÊ Super-sensitive Screen This Lumia sports a 4 inch screen that comes with sensitivity so effective that it can detect movement even when you are wearing gloves. You can also have long fingernails, the phone will still be responsive. Nokia Mix Radio With unlimited access to your favourite tunes, the Nokia Mix Radio gives you a wide array to choose from. You can even generate your own playlists and share them with your friends as well. HERE Maps Regardless of whether you are on foot, in publick transport or driving, HERE Maps will lead you to your destination with simple, easy to understand, step-by-step instructions ‰ÛÒ you will never get lost from now on, regardless of whether you are in your hometown or abroad. Windows 8 One of the best operating systems in the world, the Lumia 520 runs on the Windows Phone 8 which comes with Live Tiles that keep you updated of all the happenings in your life right on the homescreen while it is happening. It also has MS Office that keeps you in the loop wherever you are and with free storage space on SkyDrive there is never a question of you losing any data whatsoever.

title: Samsung Galaxy Core Prime
description: The Galaxy Core Prime is an efficient smartphone, powered by a quad-core processor and comes with a WVGA display. With a 5MP CMOS primary camera, you can take great photos of memorable events. Performance This smartphone comes is powered by a 1.2 GHz quad-core processor and 1 GB RAM for seamless multitasking. Now you can play a game in one app while listening to music using other apps simultaneously. This phone also comes with a 2000 mAh lithium-ion battery, which gives you up to 9 hours of internet browsing on 3G networks. Design & Display The 11.43 cm (4.5) Galaxy Core Prime features a simplistic design with a built-in durable frame with the exquisite feel of anodized metal. It has a thickness of 8.8 mm, which makes it fit comfortably in one hand or in your pocket. Camera This phone lets you take great photos in any light environment as it comes with a 5MP CMOS primary camera. You can also take fun selfies or video chat with your friends and family abroad using the phone's 2MP front-facing camera. Storage The Galaxy Core Prime comes with up to 8GB of storage space and it can be expanded by up to 64GB as it supports microSD cards. Connectivity Connect to wireless internet networks on your phone as it supports Wi-Fi bands. You can also browse on-the-move as the Galaxy Core Prime supports 3G networks as well. Sensors This Galaxy Core Prime has an accelerometer which controls the phone's orientation, allowing you to play motion-based games. It also has a proximity sensor capable of detecting nearby objects and adjusting the screen's brightness automatically.

title: Lenovo A7000
description: A mix of the right ingredients and an economical price tag, the Lenovo A7000 qualifies as a great device for multimedia, gaming and productivity. Dolby Atmos Considered the world's first smartphone with Dolby Atmos, this Lenovo device comes as a boon for multimedia lovers. Dolby Atmos takes mobile audio to great heights, delivering rich sound with your music, videos and games. The headphone experience is truly amazing with this device. Big HD Screen Enjoy watching videos, gaming, browsing the web or even online shopping in vibrant HD quality on the 13.97 cm (5.5) display of this Lenovo smartphone. The ultra-wide viewing angles further enhance your smartphone experience. A Total Performer The True8Core processor by MediaTek unleashes the power of all eight cores for an overall enhanced performance while consuming very less power to boost battery life. The 2 GB RAM ensures that your Lenovo phone performs without any lags. 4G LTE Are you facing too many lags while gaming online? Is a poor connection affecting the quality of your video calls? Switch to 4G LTE and experience speed and connectivity like never before - whether you are streaming videos, sharing files, video chatting or downloading multimedia. Android Lollipop This Lenovo smartphone comes loaded with Android Lollipop 5.0 operating system. Enjoy the new features and enhancements that Android offers on this device. Camera If you love to click photos and selfies, then the pair of snappers of this Lenovo device will not fail you. The 8 MP primary camera and the 5 MP front camera deliver quality photos and videos. Dual SIM Thanks to the Dual SIM Dual Standby support, you can combine work and play in one device using two phone numbers. The Dual SIM feature also lets you cut down on your phone bill by choosing separate plans for data and calls. Expandable Storage This phone offers up to 32 GB expandable storage via micro SD. Store all your favourite music, photos and videos, and take them with you wherever you go. Battery Enjoy all-day texting, play games or stream videos when bored, and stay connected to social media throughout the day. The 2900 mAh battery of the Lenovo A7000 gives up to 16 hours 3G talk time and up to 39 hours 2G talk time. Furthermore, this device supports OTG charging. Lenovo Secure Zone Enjoy two virtual phones in one device with Lenovo Secure Zone. It allows you to create a password-protected zone and lets you select the apps and accounts you want to access from this zone. Connectivity This smartphone comes with Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, and 3G support. Sensors This A7000 smartphone has a light sensor, a gravity sensor, an e-Compass, and a proximity sensor.

title: Lenovo A6000 Plus
description: Designed for music and multimedia lovers, the Lenovo A6000 Plus is a budget smartphone with a 12.7 cm (5) HD display. It's powered by a quad-core Snapdragon processor which delivers a responsive system performance. Memory & Storage Along with excellent multi-tasking, the 2 GB RAM of this Lenovo device ensures that applications and games run lag-free. The 16 GB ROM easily accommodates all your favorite pictures, music, videos and games. Live Life in HD The Lenovo A6000 Plus comes with a 12.7 cm (5) HD display for viewing photos, browsing websites or playing games. This smartphone uses an IPS technology to deliver ultra-wide 178 degree viewing angles that are great for watching videos in large groups. Snapdragon Processor Powered by a 64-bit quad-core Qualcomm Snapdragon processor, the Lenovo A6000 Plus offers a solid performance at a reasonable price. It's 2300 m Ah battery ensures connectivity with your friends all day. Twin Speakers Become the DJ at your friend's party with this phone's twin speakers and Dolby Digital Plus audio technology. It provides crisp audio so you can enjoy your music, games and videos. Pair this phone with some good earphones to enjoy the clarity of sound that Dolby provides. 4G LTE Get ultra-fast data transfer speeds on this phone as it supports 4G LTE networks for video streaming and online gaming. Camera This Lenovo smartphone comes with an 8 MP rear camera that clicks great pictures. The 2 MP fixed-focus front camera is good for video calls and selfies. Connectivity Enjoy the flexibility of two SIMs on one phone or choose a separate data plan to save on your phone bills. This is great for people where network coverage varies between telecom providers. Other connectivity features include 3G, Wi-Fi and Bluetooth. Android Operating System With Android KitKat 4.4, you can optimize memory and improve your touch screen responsiveness so that it performs faster than before. This lets you listen to music while you browse a web page with no interruptions or reduced performance. SHAREit with CLONEit This featureåÊallows for sharing of videos, photos and apps across devices without network charges or Wi-Fi. With CLONEit, you can instantly transfer all your old data to you new Lenovo phone. This phone also comes with SYNCit which provides a backup for all your contacts, logs and SMS messages.

title: Mi 4
description: The powerful new member of the Mi family is here - the Mi 4. This piece of metallic beauty is built with state-of-the-art components and performs like a bat out of hell. Performance Experience blazing-fast performance with the 2.5 GHz quad-core Snapdragon 801 processor and 3 GB RAM. With 14% more computing speed, this Mi smartphone smoothly handles multiple complex tasks at the same time. The new and improved image processor is capable of 45% faster image processing than the previous one. Graphics Play games hiccup-free with the efficient Adreno 330 GPU. With support for advanced graphics APIs, including OpenGL ES 3.0, OpenCL, Renderscript Compute and FlexRender, the Adreno 330 is capable of rendering even complex graphics as fast and efficiently as a gaming console. Display Enjoy a delightful entertainment experience on the 5" JDI high color-saturation display of the Mi 4. It produces a resolution of 1920x1080 and has a pixel density of 441 ppi. The screen is very sensitive to touch, making it easy to operate this device. 13 MP Rear Camera Thanks to the latest camera technology incorporated into this device, the 13 MP primary shooter is extremely quick to activate, focus and capture your precious moments before they pass. The Mi 4's camera takes just 0.5 seconds to launch and it does not experience any shutter lag.åÊ - Autofocus in 0.3 Seconds With the advanced close-loop focus system of this device, it can autofocus in just 0.3 seconds making it perfect for shooting on-the-go. - Shoot 4K UHD Videos Record real-time 4K videos at 30 frames per second, thanks to the 13 MP Sony IMX 214 CMOS sensor. - Intelligent High Dynamic Flash The intelligent high dynamic flash of this phone gives you flawless pictures with natural skin tones, and a clear and bright foreground and background. - Tracking Autofocus The Touch-To-Track technology lets you select and lock on to fast-moving objects for perfect shots, just like a professional camera. 8 MP Front Camera There cannot be anything better than an 8 MP front camera and a next-generation Beauty app that allows you to click amazing selfies. The Beauty app offers you 36 smart filters that can be applied to perfect your selfies. DSP Technology Thanks to the Hexagon QDSP6V5A DSP technology, you can run image and video-based applications for longer without draining out your phone's battery. Reduce Power Wastage The high-performance mobile technology and the aSMP dynamic CPU power-supply control makes thisåÊ smartphone extremely energy efficient. It is also equipped with Quick Charge 2.0 accelerated charging technology which reduces the charging time by almost 75%. Infrared Remote Control Mi 4 comes with infrared emitters that allow you to control a wide variety of home appliances such as televisions, ACs, Wi-Fi devices and more. Use the Mi remote control app to operate supported devices. As of now, this app supports 2,853 devices. MIUI V6 With MIUI V6 interface on the Android operating system, you get a variety of customization options and practical features on your Mi device. This beautiful interface is not just smart and practical, but it also improves performance and reduces power consumption. Battery This smartphone comes with a premium-quality Lithium Ion battery with a typical capacity of 3080 mAh. This powerful battery boasts of up to 280 hours of standby time. Connectivity This smart mobile supports 3G and 2G mobile networks. Stay connected with Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.0, Bluetooth HID, Wi-Fi Display and Wi-Fi Direct. Sensors The Mi 4 comes with a barometer, an electronic compass, an accelerometer, a light sensor, a gyroscope, infrared, a hall sensor and a proximity sensor. åÊ

title: Intex Aqua Power+
description: Carry this slim smartphone in your pocket to easily access Facebook, stream YouTube videos, pursue your passion for photography and more. Power in Slim Disguise Watch many episodes of Game of Thrones or listen to numerous Linkin Park albums at a stretch with this smartphone which has a pre-loaded super power app and a 4000 m Ah Li-ion battery. Slim Body The slender body of this smartphone allows you to slide it right into your pocket and carry it around with ease. Flaunt-worthy Display See movies in lifelike clarity on the HD IPS screen of this smartphone which comes with Full Lamination technology. Aced Global Standards Don't mistime a move when you're playing Mortal Kombat on this smartphone which has a 1.3-GHz quad-core processor and a 2 GB RAM. Pictures Speak to You You can capture mesmerizing pictures with the 13-MP rear camera of this phone with simple verbal commands. Clicking great selfies from a distance with the 5-MP front-facing camera is easy too. Selfies with Bluetooth Use the Bluetooth of this phone to take selfies from afar. Undercover At Its Best Use the smart-window flip cover of this phone to perform common functions. This cover protects the screen from dust and scratches. Playback & Recording You can record high-quality audio clips on this smartphone. You also record conversations for remembrance.

title: Microsoft Lumia 640 XL
description: Watch a movie on the long bus ride home with the Lumia 640 XL's large 14.48 cm (5.7) HD IPS display. Its quad-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 400 processor also ensures quicker multitasking between apps and faster Internet browsing, allowing you to do more on the go. Office 365 Get a year's subscription of Microsoft Office 365 Personal on the purchase of this Lumia phone and enjoy creating documents on MS Word, spreadsheets on Excel and store up to 30 GB of personal data with OneDrive. Camera Quality pictures are hard to come by, but with the Lumia XL's 13 MP Auto Focus rear camera with Carl Zeiss optics, that sentiment can be put to rest. Take fun selfies with your friends at a football match with this phone's 5 MP Full HD wide-angle front camera and record that sensational goal in Full HD at 30 frames per second. Performance Unleash the power of this phone's quad-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 400 processor to browse websites, play HD games and toggle between applications in the blink of an eye. Its 3000 m Ah battery lets you make 3G calls for up to 23.7 hours, helping you stay connected with your friends and family at all times. Fun Apps After a tiring day at the office, all you want to do is take your mind off work. With the Lumia 640 XL, that expectation becomes a reality. Play fun games such as Candy Crush Saga or review restaurants on TripAdvisor. Windows Operating System What makes a good phone is not the number of 'cool' features it has, but the quality it delivers. Powered by a Windows 8.1 operating system, the Lumia 640 XL adds simplicity to all your daily activities. Work on-the-go, play games and take photos in an instant as the Lumia 640 XL has an easy-to-use interface for quicker access to your apps. Dual SIM Connectivity With two SIM slots (GSM + WCDMA) that allow you to store your local number as well as an international one, your family back home can call you without making an international call while you avoid roaming charges as well.

This HD Capacitive Touchscreen makes gaming or web browsing more entertaining with crisp, clear visuals. Operating System Experience a faster, more powerful performance with Android v5 (Lollipop) OS that makes networking with your family and friends easy and hassle-free. It also has an efficient power management system. Performance This phone is gifted with a powerful 64-Bit, 1.5 GHz OctaCore processor that teams up with 2GB DDR3 RAM to make multi-tasking easier. You don't have to worry about your battery dying while you game as it has power-saving features to boost battery life. Battery This phone comes with a long lasting 2900mAh battery and efficient power-saving features that let you watch videos or take pictures all day long. Dolby Atmos Enjoy a rich, immersive sound experience while gaming or watching movies, thanks to Dolby Atmos that gives you a sound quality like no other. title: Samsung Galaxy S4
description: Samsung Galaxy S4 I9500 not only makes your life richer, simpler and fun but also monitors our health and well-being. Display S4's Full HD, super AMOLED 12.7 cm (5) screen encased in a polycarbonate body makes this light yet strong. Operating System This phone comes with an Android v4.2.2 (Jelly Bean) OS that provides a host of user-friendly, personalized features. Performance This phone comes with two Quad-Core processors that help run multiple applications simultaneously without freezing up. Dual Shot With this feature, you can simultaneously shoot with the front and rear cameras to get one perfect picture. Primary camera (13 MP) and front camera (2 MP) team up to help you capture a photo of yourself while you take a picture. Sound & Shot Now you can remember what was said or played when the photo was taken as every picture you take on Samsung Galaxy S4 comes with sound. Drama Shot This feature lets you take a series of pictures of any moving object and puts them together in a single frame, so you can see the action in detail while giving you a dynamic photo. Group Play- Share Music Need a sound system for your party? Get all the Samsung GALAXY S4 phones together and create a powerful sound system that enhances the sound quality. You can also wirelessly connect multiple Samsung Galaxy S4 phones to play games and share photos and documents. Story Album You've taken too many pictures and you don't want them to get mixed up. Samsung Galaxy S4 organizes your photos to create customized albums for every occasion choosing various layouts. Samsung Hub Now you can easily browse through any content available on the Samsung Hub whether it is videos, games or songs, and shop from one integrated store that has a stylish magazine layout. S Translator With S Translator, all you have to do is say what you want to translate and it'll read or text back the translation. It allows tourists to communicate with the locals, helps discover foreign dishes and explore hidden hangouts. Languages supported are English, German, French, Chinese, Spanish, Italian, Japanese and Korean. Air View Barely hover your finger over the screen to get a quick preview, enlarge photos or speed dial. Also, you can control your phone by just waving your hand over the screen to accept calls or to browse. Samsung Smart Pause When you look away while watching a video, this smartphone detects your moves and pauses the video so you don't miss anything. Look back at the screen again to resume your video. This phone intuitively moves along with you and scrolls up or down when you tilt the phone from one side to another. Samsung Home Sync Home Sync is your personal cloud device with 1 TB of storage capacity that can store tons of pictures, videos and games. Stream content directly on your TV and navigate with ease with Mirror Mouse, a specialized navigating feature of Samsung Galaxy S4. Samsung WatchON S4 becomes a TV remote when you connect it with your home entertainment system, so it suggests you programs that you may like, gives you program schedules and even does channel surfing for you. S Health With S Health feature, you can keep track of your workouts, daily intake and weight levels. It also shows your comfort levels based on temperature and humidity outside. Adapt Display & Sound Adapt Display adjusts your view with 7 automatic modes and 4 manual modes so as to give your eyes a rest. Adapt Sound gives you the perfect volume customized just for you by dialing music up and down and balancing left and right audio based on your hearing. Storage S4 comes with 16 GB internal memory with an expandable memory of up to 64 GB with a micro SD. Battery This phone comes with a battery of 2600 m Ah that lets you browse the net for up to 8 hours if 3G and up to 10 hours if Wi-Fi Sensors This phone has various in-built sensors to make day to day tasks easier such as Accelerometer, Geomagnetic, Gyro-sensor, Light Sensor, Pressure sensor, Proximity Sensor, Gesture Sensor, Temperature & Humidity sensor and Hall Sensor.

title: Redmi 2
description: If you're looking for a budget-friendly Android smartphone with a cool UI that does not compromise on performance, then look no further than the Redmi 2. Performance Powered by a 64-bit Cortex-A53 processor and 1 GB, the Redmi 2 delivers fast and efficient performance. You can expect up to 30% faster browsing speed and 50% higher CPU performance than the previous Cortex-A7 processor. With the Adreno 306 GPU, you get desktop-grade graphics that support DirectX and FlexRender for flawless 3D gaming. 4G Dual SIM With 4G LTE support, enjoy super fast surfing and streaming with download speeds of up to 150 Mbps. The 4G Dual SIM with standby lets you enjoy the benefits of two phones in one. Display The 11.9 cms (4.7) fully laminated display with its 178° IPS technology delivers quality 1280 x 720 resolution pictures and amazing color consistency from every angle. Camera Take great photos in different lighting conditions as the 8 MP rear camera comes with a BSI sensor for quality low light images and an infrared sensor protection for quality images in sunlight. In addition, the phone offers 18 filters, HDR, panorama, fish-eye and more. The 2 MP front camera is excellent for selfies, thanks to the built-in beauty filter. Design Flaunting rounded corners, this device is thin and light. It is 9.4 mm in width and weighs only 133g.åÊThe back cover is textured and matte-sprayed, making it very comfortable to hold. It is also fingerprint- and grease-resistant. MIUI 6 The fast and responsive Android operating system has been customized to run native applications and games flawlessly. The MIUI 6 comes embedded with excellent animations with customization options for an enhanced user experience. Moreover, the MIUI interface undergoes improvements constantly based on suggestions by millions of active MIUI users. MEMS Microphones The phone houses two noise-cancelling silicon microphones that deliver clear sound, even in extremely noisy situations. Battery The Redmi 2 comes with an efficient battery which boasts a rated capacity of 2200 mAh and typical actual capacity of 2400 mAh. Quick Charge technology speeds up charging by 40%.

title: Asus Zenfone 2 Deluxe ZE551ML
description: Beautifully crafted, the Asus Zenfone 2 delivers a truly remarkable performance and gets you through the day without fail. This dual SIM smartphone runs on Android Lollipop and offers up to 64 GB internal storage. Beautifully Crafted Indeed a marvel of design and ergonomics, this Asus smartphone is crafted with ultra-thin edges and the iconic Asus concentric circle design. The 3.9 mm thin edges make it comfortable to hold this device with one hand. Ergonomic Arc Design Besides making it extremely comfortable to hold this device, the ergonomic arc design with the intuitive rear controls make it easy to adjust the volume, snap selfies or retrace your steps. Display Enjoy crystal-clear picture clarity on the razor-sharp 13.97 cm (5.5) IPS display of the Asus Zenfone 2. It comes with a resolution of 1920 x 1080 Full HD and offers 178-degree viewing angles. In addition, Asus TruVivid technology ensures that colors appear natural and lifelike. Performance Apps open quickly, games run smoothly and web browsing is effortless on this Asus phone. Thanks to the 2.3 GHz Intel Atom Super Quad-core processor which enhances everyday performance up to three times better and gaming performance up to seven times faster. Graphics Performance Whether you are watching an HD flick or playing Mortal Kombat X, get a smooth and immersive experience with the PowerVR-G6430 GPU built into this Asus handset. 4 GB RAM The Asus Zenfone 2 boasts of being the world's first smartphone with up to 4 GB RAM. This large RAM capacity and the dual channel technology makes your Zenfone multitask seamlessly and gives up to two times data transfer speed as compared to other similar devices. Touch Experience With a quick response time of 60 ms, experience impressive touch responsiveness on this Asus smartphone. A crystal-clear anti-fingerprint coating is applied on the screen to reduce scratches and smudges. Sound Experience Developed by the Asus Golden Ear Team, the SonicMaster technology has been designed to deliver rich and detailed audio whether you are on speakers or headphones. Amazing Camera Click amazing pictures with the 13 MP primary shooter. The 5 MP front camera comes with an 85-degree wide-angle lens that lets you take exceptional selfies or enjoy clear video calls. Super HDR Mode The Super HDR Mode helps to improve the light balance, so that the pictures you click are similar to what your eyes see. Low Light Mode With 4x increased light sensitivity, reduced noise, and 4x enhanced color contrast, the Low Light Mode lets you capture clear and sharp images in low light conditions. Dual-LED Real Tone Flash Ideal for indoor shots, the dual-LED real tone flash creates natural illumination and captures the real tones of subjects in every photo. Zero Shutter Lag Capture moments in real time, even the fast fleeting ones, with the zero shutter lag capability of this Asus PixelMaster camera. Selfie Panorama This amazing Asus phone gives you the ability to take 140-degree panoramic selfies, so you can capture your entire gang of friends and even the background. Zen UI Experience The new interface design delivers a smart and intuitive user experience. Also, the Zen UI lets you customize your Asus phone the way you want. This UI comes with a variety of new features such as ZenMotion, SnapView, Trend Micro Security and ZenUI Instant Updates. Battery For long lasting usage, this Asus device packs a powerful 3000 mAh battery that keeps it alive through the day. In addition, it comes with the Asus BoostMaster Technology which charges the battery at double the normal speed. With 39 minutes of charging, your battery gets fueled up to 60%. Connectivity This Asus device comes with 4G LTE, 3G, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth and NFC. åÊ åÊ
