title: Asus Zenfone 2 Laser ZE500KL
description: An impressive performer that's adept at web surfing, gaming and streaming videos, the Asus Zenfone 2 Laser boasts a 64-bit processor, 2 GB RAM, a Corning Gorilla Glass 4 display and ZenUI with Android Lollipop. Design The Zenfone 2 Laser features thin 3.5 mm edges and the iconic ASUS concentric circles with 0.13 mm pitch at the front and rear key. A marvel of design and ergonomics, this Zenfone is crafted beautifully and is comfortable to hold. Ergonomic Arc Design The ergonomic arc design features a highly-intuitive control layout which includes a physical rear key for clicking selfies, adjusting the volume and retracing your steps. So, whether you're right- or left-handed, this phone is incredibly comfortable to hold and use. Screen To Body Ratio Asus has reduced the bezel width to achieve a remarkable 70% screen-to-body ratio in this Zenfone. Performance Powered by a powerful 64-bit 1.2 GHz Quad-Core processor and 2 GB of RAM, the Zenfone 2 Laser packs enough power for your daily activities. The Adreno 306 GPU lets you enjoy seamless gaming on this device. Corning Gorilla Glass 4 This Zenfone features a 12.7 cm (5) HD display which is ideal for playing games, watching videos and browsing. The Corning Gorilla Glass 4 display is stunningly stronger than its predecessor, thanks to its 2x drop-damage resistance, 2.5x increase in retained strength. Camera A 13 MP PixelMaster rear camera, f/2.0 aperture lens, zero shutter lag, Toshiba sensor and Dual LED Real Tone flash - this Zenfone clicks amazing, high-resolution pictures and videos. Laser Auto-Focus With the laser auto-focus technology, you get near-instant focus as fast as 0.3 seconds even in low light conditions. This technology even accelerates close-up photography. Super HDR The Super HDR mode delivers natural photos with up to 4X brightness and color contrast, even in strong backlight scenarios. Low Light Mode The Low Light Mode enables up to 4X light sensitivity and noise reduction through a combination of pixel-merging technology and advanced image-processing algorithms. With this mode, you can shoot clear and bright images in low-light situations, even without a flash. ZenUI Experience the smart and personalized ZenUI and Android Lollipop 5.0 on this Asus smartphone. The new ZenUI offers enhanced security, protection and a seamless user experience.

title: Asus Zenfone Go
description: A Quad-Core processor, 2 GB RAM, an HD display, the ZenUI and Android Lollipop. The Asus Zenfone Go is a stunning multitasker that's perfect for watching videos, playing games and browsing the web. Quad-Core Performance Whether you're handling multiple applications at a time or playing Fifa 15, the 1.3 GHz Quad-Core MediaTek processor and 2 GB RAM deliver a remarkable, glitch-free performance. Stunning Display The Zenfone Go is equipped with a 12.7 cm (5) HD IPS display for your viewing pleasure. Feast your eyes on impressive visuals with stunning clarity, brightness and vibrant colors. Gorgeous Photos Thanks to the 8 MP rear camera, you can treasure the precious moments of your life in excellent quality. This Asus device also comes with a 2 MP front camera for clicking selfies and making video calls. Dual SIM. Dual Standby. Now you can separate you personal life and work without the hassle of carrying two devices, thanks to the dual SIM capability of this Zenfone. Besides this, the advanced antenna design of this Zenfone prevents call drops even in areas with poor signal. ASUS ZenUI Experience the simple, smart and personalised ZenUI with Android Lollipop 5.1 on the Zenfone Go. The visually attractive new ASUS ZenUI comes loaded with new features such as Zen Motion, Trend Micro Dr. Safety and ZenUI Instant Updates for enhanced usability, security and a seamless experience.

title: Asus Zenfone Selfie
description: Capture the perfect you with the Asus Zenfone Selfie. It comes with a 13 MP front camera, a 13 MP rear camera and a variety of novel camera features. Front & Rear Camera The Zenfone Selfie features a PixelMaster 13 MP front camera with an f/2.2 aperture and 88-degree wide-angle lens. It also comes with an advanced 13 MP rear camera with a large f/2.0 aperture lens. Both the cameras feature five-prism Largan lenses, top-quality Toshiba sensors and dual LED Real Tone flash technology. ZenMotion For Selfies With this Asus device, snapping a selfie is as easy as drawing an S on the display. Prefer a different gesture? Create your own in just a few moments. Beautification Mode Make your selfies look even more glamorous with the Beautification mode. This mode balances your facial features, softens your complexion and removes skin blemishes to give you flawless pictures in real time. Dual LED Real Tone Flash Thanks to the Dual LED Real Tone Flash, your Asus device provides perfect illumination in any lighting conditions so you get photos with true-to-life colors always. Super HDR Technology The Super HDR technology improves light balance and captures lifelike images always. It enables up to 4x brightness in dimly-lit situations so that the resulting images look exactly like what your eyes see. Low Light Mode The innovative pixel-merging technology enables up to 4x light sensitivity, so your Zenfone Selfie can capture clear photos and videos during the night or in dark situations. The Low Light mode is applicable to the front camera as well, so you can capture beautiful selfies at night and without a flash. Selfie Panorama Enable the Selfie Panorama mode and snap panoramic selfies of up to 140 degrees. The special wide-angle mode, f/2.2 aperture front lens and 88-degree field of view enable the Zenfone Selfie to capture 140-degree panoramic selfies. Laser Auto-Focus Technology Whether you're capturing photos in low light situations or taking close-ups, the laser auto-focus technology enables near-instant focus for the fastest possible clarity. Macro Focus Capture clear close-up photos of mouth-watering dishes, thanks to the camera's ability to macro focus down to 6 cm. Design This Asus smartphone is a combination of Asus' signature concentric circle detailing, an ergonomic arc design and a stylish eggshell finish. For ease of use, the device is incredibly thin at the edges (3.9 mm) and comes with rear-mounted volume control and shutter button. title: Honor 7
description: A pure delight, the Honor 7 boasts an elegant design, smart touch sensors, two stunning cameras and delivers a smooth performance. Smart Fingertip Unlock your screen within 0.5 seconds with the sensitive and intelligent metal frame-free fingerprint reader. It is capable of 360-degree quick and accurate fingerprint recognition. You can also use the fingerprint sensor to open notification panel, dismiss notifications, take a photo, answer calls or turn off alarms. Design Sleek and compact, the Honor 7 flaunts an ergonomically-designed, full metallic body which perfectly fits in your hand. Camera The 20 MP rear camera features a durable sapphire lens, Sony IMX230 sensor and PDAF fast-focussing technology (fastest at 0.1 sec). The 8 MP front camera boasts a 26 mm wide angle lens and 10-level beauty mode. Bring out your creativity while enjoying an enhanced photo-taking experience with this Honor device. Display Whether you're streaming videos or browsing the web, enjoy bright and clear visuals on the 13.2 cm (5.2) Full HD display of this Honor device. The display has a high contrast ratio of 1500:1 and a high color saturation rate of 85%. Battery The 3100 mAh battery combined with SmartPower 3.0 lets you use your Honor smartphone for long hours. It boasts a battery life of up to 2.57 days for light users and up to 1.2 days for heavy users. Thermal Design The aluminium alloy rear cover and L-type architecture greatly improves heat dissipation and keeps your Honor 7 cool while processing arduous tasks such as gaming. Performance Enjoy a superfast performance on your Honor smartphone, thanks to its 2.2 GHz HiSilicon Kirin 935 processor, 64-bit Android Lollipop 5.0 and 3 GB RAM. Smart Key Want to quickly access apps and shortcut functions? Single or double tap the smart key. Long press the same key to access Google Search and Google Voice. Smart Voice Wakeup Use your voice to find and wake-up your Honor 7, and make calls without unlocking the screen. Smart EMUI 3.1 Experience the elegant, and efficient, 3D Dynamic UI on this Honor smartphone. Access apps fast by drawing. Take snapshots quickly by double clicking on the down volume button. The smart UI of this phone also lets you hide private apps easily. Audio Plus The sound chamber design, Smart PA and DTS sound effect ensure that the Honor 7 delivers clear, hi-fi sound. The super hands-free calling 3.0 feature reduces noise within 3 metres. The Huawei Voice+ feature lets you enhance the volume by 58% and makes calls clear. Smart Control 3.0 Control your TV, air-conditioner, DVD player or any other device with this Honor smartphone which features an IR remote chip with pre-installed IR code libraries from leading manufacturers. You don't require a network connection to use this feature.

title: Moto X Play
description: With 30 hours battery backup, an Octa-core processor and a superb 21 MP camera - the new Moto X Play lets you do so much with one gadget. Featuring an aesthetically pleasing design and nifty technical features, this handset is your perfect partner. Battery Life Now you don't have to worry about your phone running out of juice in the middle of your road trip. The Moto X Play has a 3630 m Ah battery capacity, so you can go up to 30 Hours without stopping to recharge. With Turbopower* charging, the phone gets up to 8 hours of battery life in just 15 minutes so you can quickly charge the phone before leaving home. * Turbo charger sold separately Camera This Moto phone has a 21 MP rear quick capture camera so you can capture clear, true-to-life images. Thanks to the rapid focus, auto HDR and colour balancing, dual LED flash, you can take some great shots with this phone whether it‰Ûªs day or night. Shoot videos in HD and see every detail in crisp 1080 p. This phone's 5 MP front camera ensures that you look great in selfies and while video chatting with friends. Performance Get all the processing power you need for online shopping, gaming, streaming and multitasking with the 1.7 GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon 615 Octa-core processor and 2 GB RAM of the new Moto X play. Vibrant Display Enjoy crisp and crystal-clear videos and photos in 1080 p on the remarkable 14 cm (5.5) FHD display of the new Moto X play. The Corning Gorilla Glass 3 protects the display from scratches and damages. Storage Never run out of space. Store all your favorite applications, music, videos, documents, and more on the Moto X Play. It comes with 32 GB internal memory and a microSD card slot so you can expand storage by up to 128 GB. Design Flaunting a contemporary and trendy exterior, the Moto X Play is bound to impress you with its bold style and cool features. It also comes with a water-repellent coating to protect it from accidental water spills, splashes and little rain. Best of Android The Moto X Play runs on Android 5.1.1 Lollipop for a power-packed performance. No unnecessary software means your phone runs seamlessly with enhanced battery life and new updates. Connectivity Enjoy endless connectivity with friends and family via 4G or Wi-Fi. The smartphone lets you transfer data easily to other devices via Bluetooth or USB. With Dual 4G SIM slots, you can stay connected non-stop and enjoy work-life balance. Moto Voice Moto X Play simplifies life by letting you interact with the phone, hands-free. Control your phone, ask questions and Google for information without having to hold the phone. Give your handset a nudge to preview notifications or play/pause music without unlocking your phone. Moto Assist Everyone loves an intuitive gadget. The Moto X Play learns your preferences and adapts to your situation - whether you're at work, driving, in a meeting or chilling at home - your Moto X is a delight to have around. From reading your text messages aloud while you're driving to silencing the ringer in a meeting, this phone truly makes life easy.

title: Asus Zenfone 2 Laser 5.5
description: An impressive performer that's adept at web surfing, gaming and streaming videos, the Asus Zenfone 2 Laser boasts a 64-bit processor, 3 GB RAM, a Corning Gorilla Glass 4 display and ZenUI with Android Lollipop. Beautifully Crafted The Zenfone 2 Laser features thin 3.5 mm edges and the iconic ASUS concentric circles with 0.13 mm pitch at the front and rear key. A marvel of design and ergonomics, this Zenfone is crafted beautifully and is comfortable to hold. Ergonomic Arc Design The ergonomic arc design features a highly-intuitive control layout which includes a physical rear key for clicking selfies, adjusting the volume and retracing your steps. So, whether you're right- or left-handed, this phone is incredibly comfortable to hold and use. Screen To Body Ratio Asus has reduced the bezel width to achieve a remarkable 70% screen-to-body ratio in this Zenfone. Performance Powered by a powerful 64-bit 1.7 GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon 615 processor and 3 GB of RAM, the Zenfone 2 Laser packs enough power for your daily activities. The Adreno 306 GPU lets you enjoy seamless gaming on this device. Corning Gorilla Glass 4 This Zenfone features a 13.97 cm (5.5) HD IPS display which is ideal for playing games, watching videos and browsing. The Corning Gorilla Glass 4 display is stunningly stronger than its predecessor, thanks to its 2x drop-damage resistance, 2.5x increase in retained strength. Camera A 13 MP PixelMaster rear camera, an f/2.0 aperture lens, zero shutter lag, Toshiba sensor and Dual LED Real Tone flash - this Zenfone clicks amazing, high-resolution pictures and videos. The device also comes with a 5 MP front camera. Laser Auto-Focus With the laser auto-focus technology, you get near-instant focus as fast as 0.3 seconds even in low light conditions. This technology even accelerates close-up photography. Super HDR The Super HDR mode delivers natural photos with up to 4x brightness and color contrast, even in strong backlight scenarios. Low Light Mode The Low Light Mode enables up to 4x light sensitivity and noise reduction through a combination of pixel-merging technology and advanced image-processing algorithms. With this mode, you can shoot clear and bright images in low-light situations, even without a flash. ZenUI Experience the smart and personalized ZenUI and Android Lollipop 5.0 on this Asus smartphone. The new ZenUI offers enhanced security, protection and a seamless user experience.

title: Redmi 2 Prime
description: If you're looking for a budget-friendly Android smartphone with a cool UI that does not compromise on performance, then look no further than the Redmi 2. Performance Powered by a 64-bit Cortex-A53 processor and 2 GB, the Redmi 2 delivers fast and efficient performance. You can expect up to 30% faster-browsing speed and 50% higher CPU performance than the previous Cortex-A7 processor. With the Adreno 306 GPU, you get desktop-grade graphics that support DirectX and FlexRender for flawless 3D gaming. 4G Dual SIM With 4G LTE support, enjoy super fast surfing and streaming with download speeds of up to 150 Mbps. The 4G Dual SIM with standby lets you enjoy the benefits of two phones in one. Display The 11.9 cmåÊ(4.7) fully laminated display with its 178å¡ IPS technology delivers quality 1280 x 720 resolution pictures and amazing color consistency from every angle. Camera Take great photos in different lighting conditions as the 8 MP rear camera comes with a BSI sensor for quality low light images and an infrared sensor protection for quality images in sunlight. In addition, the phone offers 18 filters, HDR, panorama, fish-eye and more. The 2 MP front camera is excellent for selfies, thanks to the built-in beauty filter. Design Flaunting rounded corners, this device is thin and light. It is 9.4 mm in width and weighs only 133 g.åÊThe back cover is textured and matte-sprayed, making it very comfortable to hold. It is also fingerprint- and grease-resistant. MIUI 6 The fast and responsive Android operating system has been customized to run native applications and games flawlessly. The MIUI 6 comes embedded with excellent animations with customization options for an enhanced user experience. Moreover, the MIUI interface undergoes improvements constantly based on suggestions by millions of active MIUI users. MEMS Microphones The phone houses two noise-cancelling silicon microphones that deliver clear sound, even in extremely noisy situations. Battery The Redmi 2 comes with an efficient battery which boasts a rated capacity of 2200 m Ah and typical actual capacity of 2400 m Ah. Quick Charge technology speeds up charging by 40%.

title: Asus Zenfone Selfie
description: Capture the perfect you with the Asus Zenfone Selfie. It comes with a 13 MP front camera, a 13 MP rear camera and a variety of novel camera features. Front & Rear Camera The Zenfone Selfie features a PixelMaster 13 MP front camera with an f/2.2 aperture and 88-degree wide-angle lens. It also comes with an advanced 13 MP rear camera with a large f/2.0 aperture lens. Both the cameras feature five-prism Largan lenses, top-quality Toshiba sensors and dual LED Real Tone flash technology. ZenMotion For Selfies With this Asus device, snapping a selfie is as easy as drawing an S on the display. Prefer a different gesture? Create your own in just a few moments. Beautification Mode Make your selfies look even more glamorous with the Beautification mode. This mode balances your facial features, softens your complexion and removes skin blemishes to give you flawless pictures in real time. Dual LED Real Tone Flash Thanks to the Dual LED Real Tone Flash, your Asus device provides perfect illumination in any lighting conditions so you get photos with true-to-life colors always. Super HDR Technology The Super HDR technology improves light balance and captures lifelike images always. It enables up to 4x brightness in dimly-lit situations so that the resulting images look exactly like what your eyes see. Low Light Mode The innovative pixel-merging technology enables up to 4x light sensitivity, so your Zenfone Selfie can capture clear photos and videos during the night or in dark situations. The Low Light mode is applicable to the front camera as well, so you can capture beautiful selfies at night and without a flash. Selfie Panorama Enable the Selfie Panorama mode and snap panoramic selfies of up to 140 degrees. The special wide-angle mode, f/2.2 aperture front lens and 88-degree field of view enable the Zenfone Selfie to capture 140-degree panoramic selfies. Laser Auto-Focus Technology Whether you're capturing photos in low light situations or taking close-ups, the laser auto-focus technology enables near-instant focus for the fastest possible clarity. Macro Focus Capture clear close-up photos of mouth-watering dishes, thanks to the camera's ability to macro focus down to 6 cm. Design This Asus smartphone is a combination of Asus' signature concentric circle detailing, an ergonomic arc design and a stylish eggshell finish. For ease of use, the device is incredibly thin at the edges (3.9 mm) and comes with rear-mounted volume control and shutter button. Display Enjoy eye-delighting picture clarity and brilliant colors on the 13.97 cm (5.5) Full HD IPS display. It comes with ASUS TruVivid technology built-in and offers a 178-degree viewing angle. Corning Gorilla Glass 4 The stronger and safer Corning Gorilla Glass 4 display guarantees up to 2x drop-damage resistance, 2.5x increase in retained strength and is 85% less likely to break on comparison to its predecessor. Performance The Zenfone Selfie is packed with a 64-bit octa-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 615 processor and 3 GB RAM that creates a perfect balance between multimedia performance and battery efficiency. It also comes with Adreno 405 graphics for enhanced gaming and 4G LTE for super-fast internet connectivity.

It also comes with an advanced 13 MP rear camera with a large f/2.0 aperture lens. Both the cameras feature five-prism Largan lenses, top-quality Toshiba sensors and dual LED Real Tone flash technology. ZenMotion For Selfies With this Asus device, snapping a selfie is as easy as drawing an S on the display. Prefer a different gesture? Create your own in just a few moments. Beautification Mode Make your selfies look even more glamorous with the Beautification mode. This mode balances your facial features, softens your complexion and removes skin blemishes to give you flawless pictures in real time. Dual LED Real Tone Flash Thanks to the Dual LED Real Tone Flash, your Asus device provides perfect illumination in any lighting conditions so you get photos with true-to-life colors always. Super HDR Technology The Super HDR technology improves light balance and captures lifelike images always. It enables up to 4x brightness in dimly-lit situations so that the resulting images look exactly like what your eyes see. Low Light Mode The innovative pixel-merging technology enables up to 4x light sensitivity, so your Zenfone Selfie can capture clear photos and videos during the night or in dark situations. The Low Light mode is applicable to the front camera as well, so you can capture beautiful selfies at night and without a flash. Selfie Panorama Enable the Selfie Panorama mode and snap panoramic selfies of up to 140 degrees. The special wide-angle mode, f/2.2 aperture front lens and 88-degree field of view enable the Zenfone Selfie to capture 140-degree panoramic selfies. Laser Auto-Focus Technology Whether you're capturing photos in low light situations or taking close-ups, the laser auto-focus technology enables near-instant focus for the fastest possible clarity. Macro Focus Capture clear close-up photos of mouth-watering dishes, thanks to the camera's ability to macro focus down to 6 cm. Design This Asus smartphone is a combination of Asus' signature concentric circle detailing, an ergonomic arc design and a stylish eggshell finish. For ease of use, the device is incredibly thin at the edges (3.9 mm) and comes with rear-mounted volume control and shutter button. Display Enjoy eye-delighting picture clarity and brilliant colors on the 13.97 cm (5.5) Full HD IPS display. It comes with ASUS TruVivid technology built-in and offers a 178-degree viewing angle. Corning Gorilla Glass 4 The stronger and safer Corning Gorilla Glass 4 display guarantees up to 2x drop-damage resistance, 2.5x increase in retained strength and is 85% less likely to break on comparison to its predecessor. Performance The Zenfone Selfie is packed with a 64-bit octa-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 615 processor and 2 GB RAM that creates a perfect balance between multimedia performance and battery efficiency. It also comes with Adreno 405 graphics for enhanced gaming and 4G LTE for super-fast internet connectivity.

title: Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge+
description: A quintessential union of technology and aesthetics, the Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge+ boasts a sleek physique, a Quad HD display, a powerful Octa Core processor and a variety of camera features. Dual-Edge Display Thanks to the beautiful 14.47 cm (5.7) Quad HD Super AMOLED dual-edge display, the S6 Edge+ adds more depth to videos and provides a real-to-life gaming experience. Enjoy an immersive and engaging viewing experience on this Samsung smartphone. Performance Whether you play a lot of 3D games or multitask heavily, the Samsung S6 Edge+ delivers a faultless performance. It is equipped with a 14 nm Exynos 7420 Octa Core processor and 4 GB of RAM. This smartphone runs on the Android Lollipop v5.1 operating system. Battery & Charging This Samsung device is powered by an efficient 3000 mAh Li-Ion battery (non-removable). You can choose to charge your S6 Edge+ either using the cable or by placing it on a compatible wireless charging pad. The device takes up to 120 minutes to fully charge when using the wireless pad and up to 90 minutes when using the cable. Camera Thanks to the 16 MP rear camera and 5 MP front camera, the S6 Edge+ captures clear photos and videos in any situation. The camera app launches in an instant, so you don't ever miss out on any fleeting moments. The front camera comes with an Advanced Selfie Technology and a variety of filters that let you click beautiful selfies. Live Broadcast Celebrating your little one's first birthday? With Live Stream, you can live stream the celebration directly from your S6 Edge+. Live Broadcast streams on YouTube. Steady Footage No more shaky videos, thanks to the combination of Video Digital Imaging Stabilization and Optical Image Stabilization. This feature is available only on the rear camera. Auto Real-Time HDR Get detailed, vivid and lifelike photos with this Samsung smartphone. The device's camera comes with auto real-time HDR feature which captures the same scene in different exposure levels and combines them into a single picture. Video Clip Modes With innovative videography modes such as Collage, Series and Slow Motion, the S6 Edge+ lets you get creative. Shoot four video clips and combine them into a video collage with the Collage Mode. Create your own short film with the Series feature. Appreciate your favorite moments better by shooting them in the Slow Motion mode. Connectivity Connect to the Web or transfer files to other devices with this Samsung smartphone which comes with 3G, 4G, Wi-Fi and Bluetooth connectivity. Access Favorites Easily This Samsung Galaxy smartphone lets you assign five favorite contacts and five favorite apps to the edge. Swipe inwards from the edge handle anytime to access these assigned favorites. OnCircle With this feature, you can send an emoji or poke your People Edge contacts. Now you can communicate in ways more than just words with the S6 Edge+. SideSync With SideSync, you can transfer photos to your laptop or PC effortlessly. What's better? You can answer calls or reply to texts from your computer at the same time.

title: Intex Aqua Sense 5.0
description: Display and ConfigurationThe Intex Aqua Sense 5.0 smartphone from Intex boasts of a superior design. The rectangular shaped phone with sharp curves around the edges is encompassed within a sleek 8mm casing and is available in black and white colour variants. The smartphone houses a 5-inch IPS LCD qHD display. It has a display resolution of 540 x 960 pixels with a pixel density of 220 ppi and renders a superior viewing experience with good clarity. The device is powered by quad-core, 1.2GHz, Cortex A7 processor which is coupled with 512MB of RAM. It runs on Android v4.4.2 (Kitkat) operating system. Camera and MemoryThe Intex Aqua Sense 5.0 has a 5MP shooter on its back which has an LED flash as well. It has a 0.3MP front camera for stunning selfies. It comes with Auto Focus, Panorama Mode, Continuous Shot, clicks picture by Volume up/down key and headphone button, and slow motion video recording etc. The phone comes with an 8GB RAM and up to 32GB of expandable memory with the help of a memory card.Connectivity and BatteryThe Intex Aqua Sense 5.0 smartphone sips its juice from a 2,000mAh, li-ion battery. A rich diversity can be spotted on the connectivity front as the device packs in options like 3G, Wi-Fi 802.11, b/g/n, Mobile Hotspot, Bluetooth v2.1, GPS with A-GPS, and USB connectivity.

title: Micromax Canvas Sliver 5
description: Aesthetically sculpted and carved to perfection, the Micromax Canvas Sliver 5 is a design marvel that you'd love to flaunt to the world. Slim & Light The Canvas Sliver 5 boasts a super slim and lightweight build, thanks to its 5.1 mm body and 97 grams weight. Fast 4G Connectivity Stream videos faster and play online games seamlessly with the super-fast 4G connectivity. It gives up to 150 Mbps download speed and up to 50 Mbps upload speed. Performance The 1.2 GHz Quad Core processor (64-bit), 2 GB RAM and Adreno 306 GPU ensure that your Micromax device delivers an amazing performance whether you're browsing, gaming or streaming videos. Design This Micromax phone is made from aircraft grade aluminium which makes it extremely strong and durable. Display Experience excellent visuals in true HD quality on the 12.19 cm (4.8) AMOLED display. It is protected by Corning Gorilla Glass 3 which keeps the screen free from scratches. Rear Camera Capture moments as they happen and in excellent picture quality with the 8 MP Sony AF rear camera. It features a wide-angle lens, a Blue Glass filter and is capable of 1080 p video recording Front Camera Whether you want to click beautiful selfies or enjoy clear video chats with friends, this Micromax device comes with a 5 MP front camera. Clear Sound Equipped with an NXP Smart Power Amplifier and Dirac HD sound, the Canvas Sliver 5 delivers rich Surround Sound with deeper bass and enhanced volume output. Battery The high density 2000 m Ah Li-Po battery boasts up to eight hours of talk time and up to 345 hours of standby time. Storage Download your favorite apps, songs and videos and store them in the 16 GB of storage space offered by this smartphone. Professional Mode Control White Balance, ISO, Exposure and Anti-Banding manually just like in a DSLR with the Professional Mode. Night Shot The in-built night mode lets you click clear pictures in low light conditions. Panorama Shot The Panorama mode lets you capture wider frames. Beauty Features The built-in Face Beauty Modes let you beautify your selfies and group pictures. Android Lollipop Enjoy a seamless and efficient smartphone experience with the Android Lollipop 5.0 operating system. Pre-Loaded Apps This Micromax device comes with a host of pre-loaded apps such as Housing, Hotstar, Quikr, Snapdeal, NewsHunt and more.

title: Intex Aqua Life III
description: Max-out With The Super Smooth OS ANDROID 5.1 Lollipop From now on multitasking would be fun. Listen to music, browse the web and chat at the same time. Nothing can slow you down. Bring Alive The Experience - AQUA Life III has a stunning display with the amazing power of colours. It‰Ûªs time to pour life into everything you do. Latest Fashion Statement AQUA Life III comes in three premium colours to suit your style. Its light body, sleek design, and premium Metal Brush finish are Something that you would love to flaunt. While you are recording the video using the rear camera, continuous tapping on the screen for about few seconds will take a picture of the screen which you are recording. Capture all that you love in slow motion and extend the joy. An exciting match or friends birthday- shoot it all and enjoy the whole action in slow motion. Want to capture the mesmerizing beauty of landscapes at one go in one picture? No worries!! With AQUA LIFE III‰Ûªs PANORAMA SHOT function you can capture the moment. AQUA LIFE III AIR SHUFFLE function allows you to operate the phone with simple hand gestures. While listening to music, now you can easily Play, Pause, or go to the Next or Previous Track without even touching the screen. Power Button to End Call, By using the power button instead of a software key to terminate calls, you don't even have to look at the phone. This could be useful when you're doing something else in parallel with talking on the phone.

title: Honor 7
description: A pure delight, the Honor 7 boasts an elegant design, smart touch sensors, two stunning cameras and delivers a smooth performance. Smart Fingertip Unlock your screen within 0.5 seconds with the extremely sensitive and intelligent metal frame-free fingerprint reader. It is capable of 360-degree quick and accurate fingerprint recognition. You can also use the fingerprint sensor to open notification panel, dismiss notifications, take a photo, answer calls or turn off alarms. Design Sleek and compact, the Honor 7 flaunts an ergonomically-designed, full metallic body which perfectly fits in your hand. Camera The 20 MP rear camera features a durable sapphire lens, Sony IMX230 sensor and PDAF fast-focussing technology (fastest at 0.1 sec). The 8 MP front camera boasts a 26 mm wide angle lens and 10-level beauty mode. Bring out your creativity while enjoying an enhanced photo-taking experience with this Honor device. Display Whether you're streaming videos or browsing the web, enjoy bright and clear visuals on the 13.2 cm (5.2) Full HD display of this Honor device. The display has a high contrast ratio of 1500:1 and a high color saturation rate of 85%. Battery The 3100 mAh battery combined with SmartPower 3.0 lets you use your Honor smartphone for long hours. It boasts a battery life of up to 2.57 days for light users and up to 1.2 days for heavy users. Thermal Design The aluminium alloy rear cover and L-type architecture greatly improves heat dissipation and keeps your Honor 7 cool while performing arduous tasks such as gaming. Performance Enjoy a superfast performance on your Honor smartphone, thanks to its 2.2 GHz HiSilicon Kirin 935 processor, 64-bit Android Lollipop 5.0 and 3 GB RAM. Smart Key Want to quickly access apps and shortcut functions? Single or double tap the smart key. Long press the same key to access Google Search and Google Voice. Smart Voice Wakeup Use your voice to find and wake-up your Honor 7, and make calls without unlocking the screen. Smart EMUI 3.1 Experience the elegant and efficient 3D Dynamic UI on this Honor smartphone. Access apps fast by drawing. Take snapshots quickly by double clicking on the down volume button. The smart UI of this phone also lets you hide private apps easily. Audio Plus The sound chamber design, smart PA and DTS sound effect ensure that the Honor 7 delivers clear hi-fi sound. The super hands-free calling 3.0 feature reduces noise within 3 metres. The Huawei Voice+ feature lets you enhance the volume by 58% and makes calls clear. Smart Control 3.0 Control your TV, air-conditioner, DVD player or any other device with this Honor smartphone which features an IR remote chip with pre-installed IR code libraries from leading manufacturers. You don't require a network connection to use this feature.

title: Sony Xperia C5 Ultra Dual
description: Love taking photos and selfies? Hone your photography skills with the Sony Xperia C5 Ultra Dual that features two 13 MP cameras and a wide variety of camera apps. Camera Capture impressive photos, videos and selfies with the 13 MP rear camera and 13 MP front camera. Both the cameras are equipped with an Exmor RS sensor and a soft LED flash. They come with features such as auto focus, superior auto, HDR and SteadyShot. Superior Auto Click clear photos and selfies whether there is a bright backlight or you are taking photos at night, thanks to the Superior Auto feature. The Xperia C5 Ultra comes with Superior Auto for front and back cameras. A Selfie Flash The front camera is equipped with a soft LED Selfie Flash so that you get perfect selfies in any lighting condition. The square shape of the flash lights up more of the frame. 22 MM Wide View Fit in more of the view in every shot with the wide 22 mm lens and 88-degree field of view. Low Light Technology Capture perfect pictures indoors and at night with this Xperia smartphone that comes with Sony's renowned low light technology. The Exmor RS for mobile sensor and HDR technology ensure that your pictures are clear and sharp, irrespective of the situation. Selfie Camera Apps Apply the different selfie apps such as AR Mask, Style Portrait and Face in to enhance your selfies and add fun effects to them. These can be applied either in real-time or after taking the shot. Display The 15.24 cm (6) Full HD display with Mobile BRAVIA Engine 2 and IPS technology is perfect for watching videos, viewing photos and browsing the Web. Activate the Super vivid mode to further enhance your entertainment experience. Design Sleek and slim, this Xperia smartphone flaunts a premium aluminium frame, a curved back and a super-thin bezel. Activate mini mode and shrink the screen size to 10.16 cm whenever you're using your device to text. This lets you use this Xperia smartphone with just one hand easily. Battery Life This Sony device packs a 2930 m Ah battery which is incredibly powerful and delivers a long battery life. It boasts up to 7 hours of continuous HD video streaming and up to 74 hours of music playback. Battery Modes Extend your Xperia's battery life by activating one of the three power saving modes. The Extended Standby mode makes standby last up to four times longer. The Extended Usage mode disables functions when the battery is low, extending the usage time up to 14%. The Ultra STAMINA mode extends the battery life by keeping only basic functions on. Performance The Xperia C5 delivers a super-fast performance, thanks to the 1.7 GHz Octa-core processor and 2 GB RAM. Stream videos lag-free, multitask seamlessly and run games without any glitches on this Xperia device. This device also comes with a built-in LTE/4G modem for fast Internet connections. Sound Thanks to the speaker which is capable of up to 95 decibels and the ClearAudio+ technologies - Clear Stereo, Clear Bass and Clear Phase, you can experience loud, crystal-clear sound on this device. The xLOUD loudness enhancement engine ensures a deep, rich bass performance.

title: Sony Xperia M5 Dual
description: Capture amazing photos at the right moment, just like professional photographers who plan and coordinate each picture, with this Sony Xperia M5 Dual Smartphone. Camera Now you can click beautiful, vivid photos like a pro with this phone. The camera's 0.25-second Hybrid Autofocus, 21.5 megapixels, 5x clear image zoom, and 4K video capture features will transform the way you capture videos and photos. Hybrid Autofocus Bid goodbye to blurry and shaky photos as this phone uses advanced Hybrid AF that combines two technologies - phase detection AF for a quick response and contrast detection AF for added precision - for rich and clear photos even when the subject is in motion. Clear Image Zoom Now you can capture even the sharp and fine details of cutlery on this phone as it offers 5x Clear Image Zoom. Superior Auto Clicking the perfect shot is now an easy task, thanks to the Superior Auto that is tuned to recognise up to 52 scenarios. It can automatically adjust the settings, including HDR, so you can capture some amazing pictures that will speak a thousand words. Capture life in 4K Thanks to this phone, you don't need to buy a compact digital camera as it is capable of capturing videos in 4K with similar quality and performance. 13 MP Front Cam Take your love for selfies to the next level with this phone that features a 13-Megapixel front camera. The sharp autofocus with a host of Sony camera tech makes it a delight to click selfies, wherever you go. Stunning Shots In Any Light This Xperia M5 features the Exmor RS‰ã¢ for the front camera so you can click selfies in vivid details and low noise, even in challenging light conditions. HDR for selfie With the High Dynamic Range (HDR) imaging technology, you can now click clear and detailed pictures, even when the subject is in front of a strong backlight. Durability Don't worry if your phone gets dirty when you are lazing on the beach or get caught in a sudden downpour as this phone, with an IP rating of IP65/68, can easily resist water up to a depth of 1.5 m. You can even rinse your phone under the tap to get rid of the dirt. Long Lasting Battery Go on a long drive without having to use a power bank to charge your phone or go in search of a power socket for a recharge. This smartphone has a 2600 m Ah battery which can easily run up to 2 days on a single charge. Stunning Display This smartphone has a stunning 12.7 cm (5) Full HD display which makes everything come alive on the screen - from videos to games. The Mobile BRAVIAå¨ Engine 2 adds sharpness and contrast to the images on the 1920 x 1080 pixel screen. The IPS technology ensures a clear view from any angle and accurate color reproduction from edge to edge. Sturdy Design The amalgamation of pure beauty and perfection - this Xperia M5 is formed with the classic Sony Omnibalance‰ã¢ design language to stand apart from the rest. The durable body features stainless steel corners that offer protection from bumps and a frame, extending just a touch over the screen, to absorb drop impacts. Fast Connectivity Featuring an inbuilt Cat4 4G/LTE modem, this smartphone allows you to browse the internet literally at lightning fast speeds. It offers download speeds up to 150 Mbit/s and upload speeds up to 50 Mbit/s. Lightning-Fast Performance This smartphone comes with 2 GHz MediaTek Helio X10 64-bit octa-core processor and 3 GB RAM so you can run multiple apps, stream lag-free videos, and play games seamlessly. This device operates on Android 5.0 OS for a smooth and user-friendly interface. Dual SIM This Xperia M5 gives you the freedom to separately maintain work and personal contacts, thanks to its Dual SIM capability.

title: Samsung Galaxy Alpha 32GB
description: Display and Build The Samsung Galaxy Alpha features a 4.7-inch HD Super AMOLED display with a resolution of 1,280 x 720 pixels and a pixel density of 312 ppi which is delivers vibrant and crisp visuals. The smartphone is built to carry a sophisticated outlook without compromising on the functionality. The pimpled panel on the back carries a soft matte finish which feels comfortable in the palm. The metal frame grabs attention by reflecting light. Being just 6.7mm thick, it is surely the most slender Galaxy smartphone till date. Its length and breadth of 132.4mm and 65.5mm respectively and weight of115g makes it easy to be held and carried around. Processor and OS The smartphone is powered by a 1.3GHz Cortex A7 quad-core CPU plus 1.8GHz Cortex A15 quad-core CPU loaded on Exynos 5 Octa 5430 chipset. It is aided by 2GB RAM and manages rich graphics with the Mali T628 MP6 GPU. The handset runs the latest Android v4.4.4 KitKat OS. Camera, Storage and Other Features The Samsung Galaxy Alpha flaunts a 12MP rear autofocus snapper which has a resolution of 4,128 x 3,096 pixels and is capable of producing UHD videos at 30fps. It supports features like LED flash, HDR, smile and face detection, geo-tagging, touch focus and panorama. On the front, you can find a 2.1MP shooter. It has an inbuilt memory of 32GB without any microSD slot. The home button carries the fingerprint sensor and there is a heart rate monitor beside the camera at the back. The Private Mode feature lets you keep files hidden from spying eyes and the ultra power saving mode lets you capitalize on the battery fuel completely. Battery and Connectivity The Samsung Galaxy Alpha is powered by an 1,860mAh Li-ion battery and can be connected using LTE, 3G, GPS, USB port, NFC, Bluetooth v4.0 and Wi-Fi 802.11 a/ac/b/g/n.VerdictThe Samsung Galaxy Alpha looks intriguing and tough with its all new body and extremely sleek design. The device has ample power under the hood to deliver a seamless performance even while playing high-end games and multitasking. It could be an interesting product for those tired of Samsung's plastic phones.

title: Intex Aqua Star II

It has a 1.2GHz quad-core processor coupled with 1GB of RAM and runs on Android v4.4 Kitkat operating system. Camera and StorageThe device is packed with an 8MP rear camera with LED flash, and digital zooming . It also has a 5MP secondary camera to take good quality selfies which are a rage among everyone these days. It has an internal memory of 16GB which can be further expanded up to 32GB to store ample songs, videos, photos etc.Battery and ConnectivityThe Intex Aqua Star 2 16GB has connectivity options such as GPRS, 3G, Wi-Fi, and GPS for those who are reliant on the internet majorly. It has Bluetooth and USB support to connect it to other devices. To ensure that the users have access to uninterrupted entertainment, it is powered by a 2,000 mAh, li-po battery.VerdictThe Intex Aqua Star 2 has elegant looks coupled with a good configuration. It's affordable and has plenty of internal storage. The front camera is also good, making it ideal for all purpose selfies. title: Intex Cloud 4G Star
description: Intex's 4G smartphone, the Cloud 4G Star comes with Android's v5 Lollipop operating system. It comes with a 1.3GHz Quad-Core processor and 2GB RAM to handle your smartphone needs, be it web browsing, gaming or watching videos on the 12.7cm (5) HD display. Android Operating System Preloaded with Android Lollipop 5.0, this smartphone is your key to multitasking, playing games and managing your daily tasks with apps such as Google Keep. Create widgets, personalize your wallpaper with custom pictures or even set ringtones for your contacts! Performance What's that? Play the latest Spider-Man game while listening to songs on Google Play? No Problem! Handle multiple applications simultaneously with this phone's 1.3GHz Quad-Core processor and 2GB RAM. Display The Cloud 4G Star's 12.7cm (5) HD display has been engineered to treat your eyes to dazzling visuals and rich details. With a resolution of 1280 x 720 pixels, you'll be able to enjoy HD videos with impeccable clarity. If you're bored while waiting for friend, pop out your phone and watch that video your mom sent on WhatsApp. Why, mom? More Room This phone's display has an 80% screen ratio which is great for watching videos. Rear Camera Capture your favorite moments with the Cloud 4G Star's 13MP rear camera as it has an in-built autofocus and digital zoom. Front Camera How about "Livin' with my ladies, #LIVE". I only got 10 likes in the last 5 minutes. Do you think I should take it down? Let me take another selfie with my Intex Cloud 4G Star smartphone's 5MP front camera. With a zero shutter delay and face beauty features, you always look good when you take selfie with this phone. Slow Motion Let your inner Wachowski take over as you can record slow-motion videos with this smartphone. Panorama Shot As the Cloud 4G Star has a wide panorama feature, you can use the joke, "Yo' momma so fat, she had to use my phone's panorama shot feature to take a selfie," on your friends. Picture Modes With the Picture-in-Picture mode, you'll be able to take snaps from both cameras simultaneously. It also has a Video-in-Video mode which lets you take videos with both cameras, so you can be part of your own videos. Wide Angle Camera This phone comes with an 88 degree wide angle camera that's perfect for taking candid shots on-the-go. Gesture Control Control your using simple gestures, such as drawing a C on the sleeping screen to go from sleep to camera mode in a flash. You can also draw an M and W to go to the Music app and File Manager app respectively. Battery Get up to 8 hours of talktime with this smartphone as it comes with a 2300mAh lithium-polymer battery. It also has a standby time of 210 hours. Power Saving Mode This phone has a power saving mode which switches the display from LCD to black and white with a single key. Storage Store your favorite apps, games and videos on this phone's 16GB internal memory. You can expand the memory by up to 32GB as this phone supports microSD cards. Curved Design Carry a smile wherever you go as this phone's curved design adds life to all your activities. Scratch-Free Display The screen is protected by a Dragon Trail Glass is resistant to both scratches and abrasions. Connectivity This phone connects to 4G LTE and 3G networks to download files and stream videos at high speeds. It also connects Wi-Fi networks so you can browse the web or used web-based apps. Send songs or files to other devices with the phone's Bluetooth feature. GPS Tracker Need to find the fastest route to the restaurant? Switch on your phone's location and navigate your way through the city with Google Maps. FM Radio Get the latest traffic and news updates by tuning your phone to your favorite radio stations. Supported Video/Audio formats This smartphone supports a number of video and audio formats such as 3GP, MP4, AVI, WAV, MP3, AAC, AMR and MIDI. Light Sensor Fitted with a light sensor, this smartphone adjusts its screen brightness by detecting the light intensity of the environment. Gravity Sensor This sensor detects the direction of your phone and how you're holding it, so that it smartly turns the screen. Auto Call Record "Yes, darling. Yes, darling. Of course, darling." *click*. "Oh no! I wasn't even listening to my wife! What did she say?" With the Cloud 4G Star, every call is recorded automatically, allowing you to replay the call incase you missed out on some important information.

title: Asus Zenfone 2 Deluxe ZE551ML
description: Beautifully crafted, the Asus Zenfone 2 delivers a truly remarkable performance and gets you through the day without fail. This dual SIM smartphone runs on Android Lollipop and offers up to 64 GB internal storage. Beautifully Crafted Indeed a marvel of design and ergonomics, this Asus smartphone is crafted with ultra-thin edges and the iconic Asus concentric circle design. The 3.9 mm thin edges make it comfortable to hold this device with one hand. Ergonomic Arc Design Besides making it extremely comfortable to hold this device, the ergonomic arc design with the intuitive rear controls make it easy to adjust the volume, snap selfies or retrace your steps. Display Enjoy crystal-clear picture clarity on the razor-sharp 13.97 cm (5.5) IPS display of the Asus Zenfone 2. It comes with a resolution of 1920 x 1080 Full HD and offers 178-degree viewing angles. In addition, Asus TruVivid technology ensures that colors appear natural and lifelike. Performance Apps open quickly, games run smoothly and web browsing is effortless on this Asus phone. Thanks to the 2.3 GHz Intel Atom Super Quad-core processor which enhances everyday performance up to three times better and gaming performance up to seven times faster. Graphics Performance Whether you are watching an HD flick or playing Mortal Kombat X, get a smooth and immersive experience with the PowerVR-G6430 GPU built into this Asus handset. 4 GB RAM The Asus Zenfone 2 boasts of being the world's first smartphone with up to 4 GB RAM. This large RAM capacity and the dual channel technology makes your Zenfone multitask seamlessly and gives up to two times data transfer speed as compared to other similar devices. Touch Experience With a quick response time of 60 ms, experience impressive touch responsiveness on this Asus smartphone. A crystal-clear anti-fingerprint coating is applied on the screen to reduce scratches and smudges. Sound Experience Developed by the Asus Golden Ear Team, the SonicMaster technology has been designed to deliver rich and detailed audio whether you are on speakers or headphones. Amazing Camera Click amazing pictures with the 13 MP primary shooter. The 5 MP front camera comes with an 85-degree wide-angle lens that lets you take exceptional selfies or enjoy clear video calls. Super HDR Mode The Super HDR Mode helps to improve the light balanceåÊso that the pictures you click are similar to what your eyes see. Low Light Mode With 4x increased light sensitivity, reduced noise, and 4x enhanced color contrast, the Low Light Mode lets you capture clear and sharp images in low light conditions. Dual-LED Real Tone Flash Ideal for indoor shots, the dual-LED real tone flash creates natural illumination and captures the real tones of subjects in every photo. Zero Shutter Lag Capture moments in real time, even the fast fleeting ones, with the zero shutter lag capability of this Asus PixelMaster camera. Selfie Panorama This amazing Asus phone gives you the ability to take 140-degree panoramic selfies, so you can capture your entire gang of friends and even the background. Zen UI Experience The new interface design delivers a smart and intuitive user experience. Also, the Zen UI lets you customize your Asus phone the way you want. This UI comes with a variety of new features such as ZenMotion, SnapView, Trend Micro Security and ZenUI Instant Updates. Battery For long-lasting usage, this Asus device packs a powerful 3000 mAh battery that keeps it alive through the day. In addition, it comes with the Asus BoostMaster Technology which charges the battery at double the normal speed. With 39 minutes of charging, your battery gets fueled up to 60%. Connectivity This Asus device comes with 4G LTE, 3G, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth and NFC.

title: Acer Liquid Z530
description: If you love to click photos with your phone, then the ergonomically designed Acer Z530 will be an ideal partner. Camera The Acer Z530 features an 8 MP rear camera as well as an 8 MP front camera. -åÊInnovative Hybrid UI A brand new hybrid camera UI lets you control the camera and shoot photos. It also lets you choose any mode, scene and color at one time. -åÊVoice Camera Control your phone's camera using your voice. Say 'Selfie' to open the front camera and click a selfie in 3 seconds. Say 'Cheese' to snap a picture. You can also switch modes by saying the mode out loud. - Bright Magic Want to click clear low-light photos? Turn on Bright Magic feature and click bright pictures even when the lighting is extremely dim. You can also click bright selfies in low-light situations by turning on Bright Magic in selfie mode. -åÊPhoto With Sound Capture photos with a 10-second voice recording with this feature of the Acer Z530. Also, you can swipe V for call, Z for launching the music player or play, and O to pause.
